# TODO: Translation updated at 2026-07-09 15:26

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4
translate spanish d13a_9669528e:

    # "Later..."
    "Más tarde..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:10
translate spanish d13a_7f3231f4:

    # St "{i}*sigh*{/i} I don't think the queen knew how large this place really is, when she gave me her task."
    St "{i}*suspiro*{/i} No creo que la reina supiera lo grande que es realmente este lugar, cuando me encomendó su tarea."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:11
translate spanish d13a_af011095:

    # St "I should start searching the buildings near the street."
    St "Debería empezar a registrar los edificios cercanos a la calle."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:14
translate spanish d13a_a0a0622b:

    # St "I've been here long enough. If I don't find him quickly, I'll just have to call it and leave."
    St "Ya llevo aquí demasiado tiempo. Si no doy con él pronto, tendré que dejarlo y largarme."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:15
translate spanish d13a_36bb86e5:

    # St "This whole place feels like a potential trap..."
    St "Todo este lugar parece una trampa en potencia..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:18
translate spanish d13a_0e81721e:

    # St "I'll do a quick scan of the area and see if I find any signs of life. If I don't, she'll just have to make her peace with it."
    St "Haré una rápida exploración de la zona y veré si encuentro señales de vida. Si no encuentro ninguna, ella simplemente tendrá que aceptarlo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:19
translate spanish d13a_dff8952c:

    # St "I can always come back another time, if she's really hung up on finding this guy."
    St "Siempre puedo volver en otro momento, si está realmente empeñada en encontrar a ese tipo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:22
translate spanish d13a_4aa6ea29:

    # St "...And now my compass is acting like a spinning top."
    St "... Y ahora mi brújula se comporta como una peonza."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:23
translate spanish d13a_62272d2e:

    # St "Useless junk! How is this even possible? The North should still be the North, even here..."
    St "¡Un trasto inútil! ¿Cómo es posible? El Norte debería seguir siendo el Norte, incluso aquí..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:26
translate spanish d13a_2c4b63fa:

    # St "...gonna scout this place without it, I guess."
    St "... voy a explorar este lugar sin ella, supongo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:29
translate spanish d13a_abb123c2:

    # S "{i}*sigh*{/i}"
    S "{i}*suspiro*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:30
translate spanish d13a_4400b575:

    # St "Let's see what I can find."
    St "Veamos qué puedo encontrar."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:33
translate spanish d13a_cc5cbace:

    # "The gloom of the approaching dusk, the sand of the surrounding desert and the dust of time seem to settle in, coating the surroundings with a sense of abandonment."
    "La penumbra del crepúsculo que se aproxima, la arena del desierto circundante y el polvo del tiempo parecen asentarse, cubriendo el entorno con una sensación de abandono."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:34
translate spanish d13a_ef6be5a6:

    # St "Some scavenger would have a field day mining this place for scraps. The wires alone, broken as they are... there's a lot good raw materials to be found here."
    St "Algún carroñero se lo pasaría en grande buscando restos en este lugar. Sólo los cables, rotos como están... hay mucha materia prima buena que encontrar aquí."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:35
translate spanish d13a_993927ee:

    # "The streets appear dead, and silence is only broken by soft footsteps crunching sand and pebbles underfoot..."
    "Las calles parecen muertas, y el silencio sólo se rompe por las suaves pisadas que hacen crujir la arena y los guijarros bajo los pies..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:36
translate spanish d13a_81b75077:

    # "After a while, something changes in the monotony of travelling in the area, as distant sound of conversation clearly indicates a presence."
    "Al cabo de un rato, algo cambia en la monotonía del viaje por la zona, pues el sonido lejano de una conversación indica claramente una presencia."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:37
translate spanish d13a_78253a7b:

    # "Approaching slowly, it seems to be a group of adventurers... or could it be something worse?"
    "Acercándose lentamente, parece tratarse de un grupo de aventureros... ¿o podría ser algo peor?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:40
translate spanish d13a_193179c5:

    # C "You realise there's no going back for me, right?"
    C "Te das cuenta de que no hay vuelta atrás para mí, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:41
translate spanish d13a_10e2dd3f:

    # C2 "Why do you say that?"
    C2 "¿Por qué lo dices?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:42
translate spanish d13a_383b5c38:

    # C "I've been away without permission for days now. I really don't want to be whipped or put in a cell for missing out a few roll calls."
    C "Llevo días fuera sin permiso. No quiero que me azoten o me metan en una celda por perderme unas cuantas pasadas de lista."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:45
translate spanish d13a_86b50b3c:

    # C "I've been keeping a low profile for ages, trying to get in the good graces of that bitch."
    C "He pasado desapercibido durante mucho tiempo, intentando caerle en gracia a esa zorra."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:46
translate spanish d13a_d07bb985:

    # C "But it's done now. The Queen knows I am here, and she knows I should've been back by now."
    C "Pero ya está hecho. La Reina sabe que estoy aquí, y sabe que ya debería haber vuelto."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:47
translate spanish d13a_60774684:

    # C3 "Do you think they'll send people after you?"
    C3 "¿Crees que enviarán gente a por ti?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:48
translate spanish d13a_bde4acfa:

    # C "As long as we stay here, on the edges of the Zone, they won't dare. None of those guards are paid enough to risk that."
    C "Mientras permanezcamos aquí, en los límites de la Zona, no se atreverán. Ninguno de esos guardias cobra lo suficiente como para arriesgarse."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:49
translate spanish d13a_91c74a9a:

    # C3 "There's more than just guards..."
    C3 "Hay algo más que guardias..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:52
translate spanish d13a_eabb9359:

    # St "..."
    St "..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:53
translate spanish d13a_823b35af:

    # C "Either way, I am done working for them. And it's not like I left the place empty handed. She might be a bitch, but she pays well."
    C "En cualquier caso, he terminado de trabajar para ellos. Y no es que me haya ido con las manos vacías. Puede que sea una zorra, pero paga bien."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:59
translate spanish d13a_426785cc:

    # C2 "Remember when father said access to the palace would be a good thing for our tribe, Narg? This is what he was talking about. You should have waited."
    C2 "¿Recuerdas cuando padre dijo que el acceso al palacio sería algo bueno para nuestra tribu, Narg? A esto se refería. Deberías haber esperado."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:60
translate spanish d13a_b2eb37bc:

    # Narg "..."
    Narg "..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:63
translate spanish d13a_fef5c465:

    # C4 "So what do we do now, huh? We could scout this place further and sell whatever we can grab. We already got some from that kid you sniped."
    C4 "¿Y ahora qué hacemos? Podríamos explorar más este lugar y vender todo lo que podamos coger. Ya hemos conseguido algo de ese chico al que mataste."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:64
translate spanish d13a_88feea18:

    # St "So it was them..."
    St "Así que fueron ellos..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:67
translate spanish d13a_1f8c9bd3:

    # C4 "I'm getting hungry for more than jerky and stale bread, Hakunin."
    C4 "Me está entrando hambre de algo más que cecina y pan duro, Hakunin."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:68
translate spanish d13a_6ef863c5:

    # Hak "We have to decide what to do with this thing, first."
    Hak "Primero tenemos que decidir qué hacer con esta cosa."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:71
translate spanish d13a_138db5e6:

    # Narg "Well, from what little I understood of the text, it's an old document... like, very old. Goes back right to the beginning of Zeta."
    Narg "Bueno, por lo poco que he entendido del texto, es un documento antiguo... muy antiguo. Se remonta a los inicios de Zeta."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:72
translate spanish d13a_c2d861b8:

    # Narg "I can't read most of it though. The language is... we should find someone who can tell us more about it."
    Narg "Sin embargo, no puedo leer la mayor parte. El idioma es... Deberíamos encontrar a alguien que pueda contarnos más al respecto."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:73
translate spanish d13a_231a006a:

    # Hak "Father will know who to ask."
    Hak "Papá sabrá a quién preguntar."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:76
translate spanish d13a_21084fd4:

    # Narg "You keep talking about father. He wasn't the one who infiltrated the palace."
    Narg "Sigues hablando de padre. No fue él quien se infiltró en el palacio."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:77
translate spanish d13a_296b1f5f:

    # Hak "Yes, well... fine."
    Hak "Sí, bueno... bien."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:80
translate spanish d13a_8ce4ab93:

    # Hak "Do you know anybody else who this could be valuable for?"
    Hak "¿Conoces a alguien más para quien esto pueda ser valioso?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:83
translate spanish d13a_78f7d765:

    # Hak "It should be interesting to people who trade antiques... if anything."
    Hak "Debería ser interesante para la gente que comercia con antigüedades... en todo caso."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:86
translate spanish d13a_af636c64:

    # Narg "That depends on the exact content, brother. It could potentially be very embarrassing for some powerful people in the city."
    Narg "Eso depende del contenido exacto, hermano. Podría ser muy embarazoso para algunas personas poderosas de la ciudad."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:87
translate spanish d13a_a5a772ea:

    # Narg "Or maybe it's just the ramblings of some old grouch."
    Narg "O quizá sólo sean las divagaciones de un viejo cascarrabias."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:90
translate spanish d13a_d6d6654a:

    # C3 "I think that we should have looted the boy and moved on."
    C3 "Creo que deberíamos haber saqueado al chico y seguir adelante."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:91
translate spanish d13a_4f1cd4f4:

    # C3 "You two keep playing with things we know nothing about, when this place has tons of shit we could make a good profit off."
    C3 "Vosotros dos seguís jugando con cosas de las que no sabemos nada, cuando este lugar tiene toneladas de mierda de la que podríamos sacar un buen provecho."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:94
translate spanish d13a_57b059c4:

    # C4 "Listen to her, there's a reason why those guards don't risk setting foot in places like this."
    C4 "Escúchala, hay una razón por la que esos guardias no se arriesgan a poner un pie en lugares como éste."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:95
translate spanish d13a_9a7cbd0e:

    # Hak "You are free to leave, if you can't keep your nerves in check."
    Hak "Eres libre de irte, si no puedes controlar tus nervios."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:98
translate spanish d13a_635492f0:

    # C3 "The fuck is that supposed to mean?! Father wouldn't like to hear you speak like this."
    C3 "¿Qué coño significa eso? A Padre no le gustaría oírte hablar así."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:99
translate spanish d13a_6ff4176b:

    # C3 "Anyway, we better make sure we're not surrounded by feral dogs before we call it a day."
    C3 "En fin, será mejor que nos aseguremos de que no estamos rodeados de perros salvajes antes de dar por terminado el día."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:102
translate spanish d13a_8c762d3b:

    # C4 "Yeah, well, I would feel safer too if we scouted around a bit."
    C4 "Sí, bueno, yo también me sentiría más seguro si exploráramos un poco los alrededores."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:105
translate spanish d13a_60edf75d:

    # C4 "I've heard stories, and I want to make sure we're not going to be attacked during the night."
    C4 "He oído historias y quiero asegurarme de que no nos atacarán durante la noche."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:108
translate spanish d13a_d3abd950:

    # Hak "Fine... let's take a look around before you piss your pants. Just to be sure."
    Hak "Bien... Echemos un vistazo antes de que te mees en los pantalones. Sólo para estar seguros."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:111
translate spanish d13a_2838150d:

    # Hak "Let's go get the rides. Stay here brother."
    Hak "Vamos a por los vehículos. Quédate aquí, hermano."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:112
translate spanish d13a_d74f4e9e:

    # Narg "Fine. I'll try to make more sense of the texts... after taking a nap."
    Narg "Bien Intentaré darle más sentido a los textos... después de echarme una siesta."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:115
translate spanish d13a_ea867ccd:

    # "Three of the people [S] can see from her hideout get up and leave to scout the immediate surroundings."
    "Tres de las personas que [S] puede ver desde su escondite se levantan y salen a explorar los alrededores inmediatos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:118
translate spanish d13a_b36a28e9:

    # "The man who appears to be the guy [S] was told to find, lies down, staring at the dusty sky for a while, before closing his eyes."
    "El hombre que parece ser el que [S] debía encontrar, se tumba, mirando fijamente al cielo polvoriento durante un rato, antes de cerrar los ojos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:121
translate spanish d13a_ee284d7d:

    # St "This must be the man the Queen told me to look for. That's... lucky, I guess."
    St "Ése debe de ser el hombre que la Reina me dijo que buscara. Esto es... suerte, supongo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:122
translate spanish d13a_b30f87af:

    # St "I wish I had caught this conversation from the start. The bit I did hear doesn't mean much to me."
    St "Ojalá hubiera escuchado esa conversación desde el principio. La parte que oí no significa mucho para mí."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:123
translate spanish d13a_d72cd4a1:

    # St "There's more going on here than the Queen told us. I wonder if she knew and chose not to share, or if she actually has no idea."
    St "Aquí ocurren más cosas de las que nos contó la Reina. Me pregunto si lo sabía y decidió no compartirlo, o si en realidad no tiene ni idea."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:126
translate spanish d13a_661fc31b:

    # St "I should wait a bit so I can check it out."
    St "Debería esperar un poco para poder comprobarlo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:131
translate spanish d13a_4d71714e:

    # St "I can't hear their steps anymore, and this other guy seems to be sleeping. This is my best shot at sneaking in."
    St "Ya no oigo sus pasos, y el otro parece estar durmiendo. Esta es mi mejor oportunidad para colarme."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:134
translate spanish d13a_eb2c4b52:

    # St "Oof... concentrate, girl. Not the time to get sleepy!"
    St "Uf... Concéntrate, chica. ¡No es momento de dormirse!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:137
translate spanish d13a_94c7f812:

    # St "Damn... how long have I been awake, anyway?"
    St "Joder... ¿cuánto tiempo llevo despierta?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:140
translate spanish d13a_de10ca9b:

    # St "I..."
    St "Yo..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:143
translate spanish d13a_9583940f:

    # St "Wake up, [S]..."
    St "Despierta, [S]..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:146
translate spanish d13a_df867066:

    # St "...and go!"
    St "... y ¡ya!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:149
translate spanish d13a_11a57533:

    # "The surroundings look dilapidated just like most of the scenery [S] has passed through on her way."
    "Los alrededores tienen un aspecto ruinoso, como la mayoría de los paisajes que [S] ha atravesado en su camino."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:150
translate spanish d13a_e4a8a899:

    # "If not for the traces of recent and frequent passage, the low building would not stand out from the others."
    "Si no fuera por las huellas del paso reciente y frecuente, el edificio bajo no destacaría entre los demás."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:156
translate spanish d13a_37db4902:

    # St "There we are..."
    St "Ya estamos aquí..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:159
translate spanish d13a_46e3ceed:

    # "A book and a single annotated page lie on the dusty table. Around it, a few pots and pans that look a bit too clean to be part of the scenery."
    "Sobre la polvorienta mesa hay un libro y una sola página anotada. A su alrededor, unos cuantos cacharros que parecen demasiado limpios para formar parte del paisaje."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:160
translate spanish d13a_730de6f9:

    # "The bandits seem to have made this place their refuge, however temporary."
    "Los bandidos parecen haber hecho de este lugar su refugio, aunque sea temporal."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:163
translate spanish d13a_1f9197ef:

    # St "Let's see..."
    St "Veamos..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:164
translate spanish d13a_e5ddd0e3:

    # "That guy wasn't wrong. This looks like an ancient text, and this page bears the marks of the royal archive."
    "Ese tipo no se equivocaba. Parece un texto antiguo, y esta página lleva las marcas del archivo real."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:167
translate spanish d13a_875085fd:

    # St "So that means..."
    St "Así que eso significa..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:170
translate spanish d13a_23a4bbf8:

    # "Whatever the content, this must be what the Queen is really after."
    "Sea cual sea el contenido, esto debe ser lo que realmente busca la Reina."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:172
translate spanish d13a_c51f4cb5:

    # Narg "Tsk, you made a mistake, girl..."
    Narg "Tsk, te has equivocado, chica..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:176
translate spanish d13a_4d8db2ea:

    # Narg "Hands where I can see them!"
    Narg "¡Las manos donde pueda verlas!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:177
translate spanish d13a_023625ff:

    # St "Well, shit..."
    St "Bueno, mierda..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:180
translate spanish d13a_5c9b5c27:

    # Narg "I'm not telling you twice, girl."
    Narg "No te lo voy a decir dos veces, chica."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:183
translate spanish d13a_8051ac77:

    # Narg "Drop the parchment. So much as scratch it and I'll leave your body to the scavenger beasts."
    Narg "Suelta el pergamino. Si tan solo le haces un rasguño, dejaré tu cuerpo a las bestias carroñeras."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:186
translate spanish d13a_239af7f9:

    # Narg "Didn't you hear me? Put your hands up, bitch!"
    Narg "¿No me has oído? ¡Levanta las manos, zorra!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:189
translate spanish d13a_4fd8d5df:

    # Narg "Go on, try me..."
    Narg "Vamos, pruébame..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:192
translate spanish d13a_5536983c:

    # Narg "Put your weapons on the table. And I mean all of them."
    Narg "Pon tus armas sobre la mesa. Y me refiero a todas."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:195
translate spanish d13a_14c0f194:

    # Narg "{i}*laughs*{/i} I'll be damned. A fucking crossbow."
    Narg "{i}*risas*{/i} Que me maten. Una maldita ballesta."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:198
translate spanish d13a_4eac67ee:

    # Narg "Take off that coat. Now!"
    Narg "Quítate ese abrigo. ¡Ya!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:199
translate spanish d13a_971a98df:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:202
translate spanish d13a_ddfcd81e:

    # "As he comes closer, the scout confidently places his bow on the table..."
    "Al acercarse, el explorador coloca con confianza su arco sobre la mesa..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:205
translate spanish d13a_0905fdb8:

    # St "Damn it... what do I do now..."
    St "Joder... qué hago ahora..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:206
translate spanish d13a_1c0d85b6:

    # "The man moves in closer, his breathing muffled by his scarf, as he stares [S] up and down, probably looking for more weapons."
    "El hombre se acerca, con la respiración ahogada por la bufanda, mientras mira a [S] de arriba abajo, probablemente en busca de más armas."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:209
translate spanish d13a_b2eb37bc_1:

    # Narg "..."
    Narg "..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:210
translate spanish d13a_47dbd517:

    # "His eyes linger on [S]'s body..."
    "Sus ojos se detienen en el cuerpo de [S]..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:213
translate spanish d13a_cc0ff497:

    # Narg "You shouldn't have tried this, girl."
    Narg "No deberías haberlo intentado, muchacha."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:214
translate spanish d13a_d96a5903:

    # Narg "You look quite young..."
    Narg "Pareces muy joven..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:217
translate spanish d13a_a8ec9ef9:

    # Narg "Didn't your mother teach you to stay out of trouble?"
    Narg "¿No te enseñó tu madre a no meterte en líos?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:218
translate spanish d13a_16134393:

    # Narg "Didn't she tell you what happens to thieves?"
    Narg "¿No te contó lo que les pasa a los ladrones?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:221
translate spanish d13a_c1afff88:

    # "The tip of the man's dagger grazes gently on the fabric covering [S], as the man continues to talk, his voice hoarse and menacing."
    "La punta de la daga del hombre roza suavemente la tela que cubre a [S], mientras el hombre sigue hablando, con voz ronca y amenazadora."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:224
translate spanish d13a_eec055fd:

    # "In her mind, [S] can almost picture the man. The sound of his voice giving her a fair indication of his stance."
    "En su mente, [S] casi puede imaginarse al hombre. El sonido de su voz le da una buena indicación de su postura."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:225
translate spanish d13a_e33c89fc:

    # "Her eyes dart towards her belongings, assessing her options."
    "Sus ojos se dirigen hacia sus pertenencias, evaluando sus opciones."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:228
translate spanish d13a_69874688:

    # Narg "I am going to enjoy this."
    Narg "Voy a disfrutar de esto."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:229
translate spanish d13a_ed6265a9:

    # "[S] senses that the bandit is about to take advantage of the situation..."
    "[S] presiente que el bandido está a punto de aprovecharse de la situación..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:230
translate spanish d13a_971a98df_1:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:240
translate spanish d13a95_230be378:

    # St "That's close enough!"
    St "Ya está bien."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:250
translate spanish d13a95_fcc978da:

    # Narg "Agh-"
    Narg "Agh-"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:253
translate spanish d13a95_e4d67727:

    # St "He's stumbling...!"
    St "¡Está dando tumbos... !"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:267
translate spanish d13a95_0798a4ab:

