translate spanish d13a95_b2eb37bc:

    # Narg "..."
    Narg "..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:504
translate spanish d13a95_4905057b:

    # "The bandit's death rattle and the adrenaline-fuelled breathing of his killer are the only sounds that break the eerie silence that descends on the scene."
    "El estertor de muerte del bandido y la respiración cargada de adrenalina de su asesino son los únicos sonidos que rompen el silencio escalofriante que desciende sobre la escena."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:512
translate spanish d13a116_c6fe294b:

    # "I have what I came for. I should get out of here."
    "Tengo lo que he venido a buscar. Debo salir de aquí."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:518
translate spanish d13a116_03c3c262:

    # "This is the way out of here."
    "Ésta es la forma de salir de aquí."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:519
translate spanish d13a116_5bfbbeca:

    # "The faster the Zone is traversed, the more the climate around [S] changes."
    "Cuanto más rápido se atraviesa la Zona, más cambia el clima alrededor de [S]."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:520
translate spanish d13a116_d0accab9:

    # "The broken main road departing from this residential area leads to the ruins of a bridge."
    "La carretera principal rota que sale de esta zona residencial conduce a las ruinas de un puente."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:524
translate spanish d13a116_9bb8d461:

    # "How much time has passed since the last cars were driving on this road?"
    "¿Cuánto tiempo ha pasado desde que los últimos coches circularon por esta carretera?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:525
translate spanish d13a116_ac3f2705:

    # "As the desolate urban landscape unfolds, time seems to shift in odd ways."
    "A medida que se despliega el desolado paisaje urbano, el tiempo parece cambiar de forma extraña."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:526
translate spanish d13a116_c12cfd33:

    # "The light illuminating the sky turns pale and yellowish, swallowing the red hues that darkened the road until then."
    "La luz que ilumina el cielo se vuelve pálida y amarillenta, tragándose los tonos rojizos que oscurecían el camino hasta entonces."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:531
translate spanish d13a116_424d8d85:

    # "A storm is approaching."
    "Se acerca una tormenta."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:536
translate spanish d13a116_4d4dec6a:

    # "Abandoning the buildings and navigating the ever more barren landscape, finally a wall crosses the chosen path, standing tall and unbroken, stretching out into the distance on both sides."
    "Abandonando los edificios y navegando por el paisaje cada vez más árido, finalmente un muro cruza el camino elegido, erguido e ininterrumpido, extendiéndose a lo lejos a ambos lados."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:537
translate spanish d13a116_8bbc52d6:

    # "This is not [S]'s original entry point into the Zone, but it just could be a way out."
    "Éste no es el punto de entrada original de [S] en la Zona, pero podría ser una salida."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:540
translate spanish d13a116_13393492:

    # St "...I figured I would have to climb the wall. This passage will save me at least that hassle."
    St "... Supuse que tendría que escalar la pared. Este pasadizo me ahorrará al menos esa molestia."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:541
translate spanish d13a116_50570cab:

    # S "I can almost feel it... this is where I leave the Zone. It must be."
    S "Casi puedo sentirlo... aquí es donde abandono la Zona. Así debe ser."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:544
translate spanish d13a116_f39ad8dd:

    # St "The compass is still screwed up. If it stays that way once I am out of here, I guess I'll just have to dump it."
    St "La brújula sigue estropeada. Si sigue así cuando salga de aquí, supongo que tendré que deshacerme de ella."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:545
translate spanish d13a116_863b220e:

    # St "Then again, if it isn't, I'll know I am definitely out of the Zone."
    St "Aunque si no lo es, sabré que definitivamente estoy fuera de la Zona."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:549
translate spanish d13a116_971a98df:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:550
translate spanish d13a116_11cc1509:

    # "The sound of sputtering engines announces the approaching vehicles, as [S] observes them coming to a halt not far from her."
    "El sonido de los motores chisporroteando anuncia la aproximación de los vehículos, mientras [S] los observa detenerse no lejos de ella."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:565
translate spanish d13a116_585fe97f:

    # C3 "Hey... you!"
    C3 "Eh... ¡tú!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:568
translate spanish d13a116_647c7f76:

    # "Dismounting from a motorbike, the woman [S] spied on before stands tall, brandishing a menacing looking axe."
    "Desmontada de una moto, la mujer a quien [S] había observado previamente se alza con imponente presencia, sosteniendo un hacha de apariencia intimidante."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:571
translate spanish d13a116_5d154928:

    # C3 "Don't you know this is a dangerous place? What are you doing here?"
    C3 "¿No sabes que éste es un lugar peligroso? ¿Qué haces aquí?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:572
translate spanish d13a116_a25c9963:

    # C4 "Um... [Rey]... you sure she knows?"
    C4 "Um... [Rey]... ¿estás segura de que lo sabe?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:575
translate spanish d13a116_50492d54:

    # "Standing next to the bike, she waits for her companions to dismount their vehicle."
    "De pie junto a la moto, ella espera a que sus compañeros desmonten del vehículo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:576
translate spanish d13a116_65b325bb:

    # Rey "Hey... you! No need to be worried. We just have a couple questions!"
    Rey "Oye... ¡tú! No tienes por qué preocuparte. ¡Solo tenemos un par de preguntas!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:577
translate spanish d13a116_971a98df_1:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:580
translate spanish d13a116_9b54d854:

    # Rey "Don't run, ok girl? I'm coming over, don't worry..."
    Rey "No salgas corriendo, ¿vale, guapa? Voy para allá, no te preocupes..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:583
translate spanish d13a116_9dd978d8:

    # Rey "We don't want to have to hurt you, right Mynoc?"
    Rey "No queremos tener que hacerte daño, ¿verdad Mynoc?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:586
translate spanish d13a116_ca2e31ce:

    # Hak "Her tracks come from the right direction..."
    Hak "Sus huellas vienen de la dirección correcta..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:589
translate spanish d13a116_f0f62872:

    # Hak "Be careful."
    Hak "Ten cuidado."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:592
translate spanish d13a116_f4234af4:

    # Myn "Not that I mind killing, but... she's just a girl?"
    Myn "No es que me importe matar, pero... ¿Es sólo una chica?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:593
translate spanish d13a116_76805d1b:

    # Rey "{i}*sigh*{/i}"
    Rey "{i}*suspiro*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:594
translate spanish d13a116_fafb1e82:

    # Rey "Getting soft now, [Myn]?"
    Rey "¿Te estás ablandando, [Myn]?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:597
translate spanish d13a116_d98c3fae:

    # Rey "Can't you talk, girl?!"
    Rey "¡¿No puedes hablar, chica?!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:598
translate spanish d13a116_8814b6ed:

    # "The woman's voice echoes as she shouts more than she'd need to cover the distance. There's an unhinged quality to her voice that for a second sends a shiver down [S]'s back."
    "La voz de la mujer resuena mientras grita más de lo que necesitaría para cubrir la distancia. Hay una cualidad desquiciada en su voz que por un segundo hace que un escalofrío recorra la espalda de [S]."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:601
translate spanish d13a116_971a98df_2:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:602
translate spanish d13a116_205989a4:

    # Rey "Playing dumb, huh? You shouldn't have come here if you didn't want trouble, girl!"
    Rey "Haciéndote la tonta, ¿eh? ¡No deberías haber venido aquí si no querías problemas, chica!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:605
translate spanish d13a116_5201edf1:

    # "With the bandit stepping closer and the looming threat rising, [S] leans the crossbow to the wall..."
    "Con la bandida cada vez más cerca y la amenaza inminente en aumento, [S] apoya la ballesta en la pared..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:608
translate spanish d13a116_f77fb8c5:

    # S "What do you want from me?!"
    S "¿Qué quieres de mí?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:610
translate spanish d13a116_6da5dd33:

    # Rey "Oh, look at that! She talks!"
    Rey "¡Oh, mira eso! ¡Ella habla!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:611
translate spanish d13a116_f2fbf67f:

    # Rey "Listen, girl. We don't want to hurt an innocent bystander, so let me just look into your eyes as I ask you a question..."
    Rey "Escucha, muchacha. No queremos herir a un transeúnte inocente, así que déjame mirarte a los ojos mientras te hago una pregunta..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:614
translate spanish d13a116_5201edf1_1:

    # "With the bandit stepping closer and the looming threat rising, [S] leans the crossbow to the wall..."
    "Con la bandida cada vez más cerca y la amenaza inminente en aumento, [S] apoya la ballesta en la pared..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:618
translate spanish d13a116_1d3aae36:

    # "As she moves forward, the woman seems to be murmurring something to herself, a melody somewhat dimmed by the cloth covering her mouth."
    "Mientras avanza, la mujer parece murmurar algo para sí misma, una melodía algo atenuada por la tela que le cubre la boca."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:621
translate spanish d13a116_9b8828e6:

    # Rey "So... girl... here's the deal. Someone in this big and wide place just killed my friend's brother, you see?"
    Rey "Así que... chica... éste es el trato. Alguien en este lugar grande y ancho acaba de matar al hermano de mi amigo, ¿lo entiendes?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:622
translate spanish d13a116_0741a679:

    # Rey "And now we're looking for the bastard who did it, so we can skin him alive."
    Rey "Y ahora buscamos al bastardo que lo hizo, para despellejarlo vivo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:625
translate spanish d13a116_a5e5c496:

    # Rey "So why don't you help us on the right path?"
    Rey "¿Por qué no nos ayudas a seguir el camino correcto?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:626
translate spanish d13a116_44a38b1c:

    # Rey "You wouldn't know who could have done such an evil thing, would you?"
    Rey "No sabes quién podría haber hecho algo tan malvado, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:629
translate spanish d13a116_7fc7bdf8:

    # "The pleading, almost innocent tone of Reyna's last remark is belied by her actions, as she lifts the hook of the axe towards [S]'s face."
    "El tono suplicante, casi inocente, del último comentario de Reyna queda desmentido por sus acciones, cuando levanta el gancho del hacha hacia la cara de [S]."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:630
translate spanish d13a116_c799cf80:

    # Rey "You see, one of my buddies can't imagine that someone as... cute as you, would ever be involved in such an act..."
    Rey "Verás, uno de mis compañeros no puede imaginar que alguien tan... mona como tú, se involucre en un acto así..."

