    # A "[S]! You're back!!"
    A "¡[S]! ¡¡Has vuelto!!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1177
translate spanish d13b_f6144000:

    # A "Big sis!!!"
    A "¡¡¡Hermana mayor!!!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1178
translate spanish d13b_b2bef177:

    # S "Help-"
    S "Ayuda..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1181
translate spanish d13b_25757204:

    # A "Tell me everything! How was it? Was it dangerous? What did you see in there?"
    A "¡Cuéntamelo todo! ¿Cómo era? ¿Era peligroso? ¿Qué viste allí dentro?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1182
translate spanish d13b_5bded4e9:

    # A "I was so worried! You {i}have{/i} to tell me all about it!"
    A "¡Estaba tan preocupada! {i}¡Tienes{/i} que contármelo todo!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1185
translate spanish d13b_20476ba3:

    # W "{i}*sigh*{/i} [A]..."
    W "{i}*suspiro*{/i} [A]..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1186
translate spanish d13b_c5ae822b:

    # S "Easy, easy. There's plenty of time..."
    S "Tranquila, tranquila. Hay tiempo de sobra..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1189
translate spanish d13b_3ad01866:

    # S "I'm fine, really..."
    S "Estoy bien, de verdad..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1192
translate spanish d13b_a4c14ec3:

    # S "...I missed you too, [A]."
    S "... Yo también te eché de menos, [A]."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1195
translate spanish d13b_a3b96541:

    # W "Well look at that. I haven't seen you this close for years."
    W "Pues fíjate. Hacía años que no os veía tan cerca."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1198
translate spanish d13b_3b96d183:

    # A "[persistent.mom!c]... come on."
    A "[persistent.mom!c]... vamos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1199
translate spanish d13b_c5ca747a:

    # A "[S]? What is that? Are you hurt? What happened?"
    A "¿[S]? ¿Qué es eso? ¿Te has hecho daño? ¿Qué ha pasado?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1200
translate spanish d13b_249b1f94:

    # S "Ouch, that hurts! Don't press there!"
    S "¡Ay, eso duele! ¡No aprietes ahí!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1201
translate spanish d13b_dbf8694e:

    # A "Sorry..."
    A "Lo siento..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1204
translate spanish d13b_ab9a7b73:

    # Z "Come on [W]. I think we're done here. Let's leave these two alone for tonight."
    Z "Vamos, [W]. Creo que ya hemos terminado. Dejemos a estas dos solas por esta noche."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1207
translate spanish d13b_b3e927df:

    # W "You're probably right."
    W "Probablemente tengas razón."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1208
translate spanish d13b_5ff779ef:

    # W "She's all yours [A]. But don't keep her up too late, she needs to rest."
    W "Es toda tuya, [A]. Pero no la mantengas despierta hasta muy tarde, ella necesita descansar."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1209
translate spanish d13b_677b8ca4:

    # W "We'll have a proper celebration, but not in the middle of the night."
    W "Lo celebraremos como es debido, pero no en mitad de la noche."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1212
translate spanish d13b_4ff61cd2:

    # Z "You heard your [persistent.mom]. Don't bug her too much. She'll tell us everything when she's ready."
    Z "Ya has oído a tu [persistent.mom]. No la molestes demasiado. Nos lo contará todo cuando esté lista."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1213
translate spanish d13b_7eac13a7:

    # Z "Anyway, goodnight girls."
    Z "En fin, buenas noches, chicas."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1214
translate spanish d13b_ed9830b9:

    # Zw "I almost feel sorry for [S]. Maybe we should drag [A] out of there."
    Zw "Casi me da pena [S]. Quizá deberíamos sacar a [A] de ahí."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1217
translate spanish d13b_569b5262:

    # Ww "{i}*laughs*{/i} She survived the Zone, she'll survive her little sister."
    Ww "{i}*risas*{/i} Sobrevivió a la Zona, sobrevivirá a su hermanita."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1228
translate spanish d13b_2d629715:

    # "You leave them be and go back to bed."
    "Las dejas solas y vuelves a la cama."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1238
translate spanish d13c_ebd60bdd:

    # "In the great hall of your mansion, you sit enjoying the last morsels of a festive dinner, surrounded by the women of your family."
    "En el gran salón de tu mansión, estás sentado disfrutando de los últimos bocados de una cena festiva, rodeado de las mujeres de tu familia."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1239
translate spanish d13c_7c1f90fd:

    # "The attention of everybody however, is on [S]."
    "Sin embargo, la atención de todos está puesta en [S]."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1240
translate spanish d13c_a9e1edf0:

    # "Both [A] and [W] look at her with a mixture of relief and trepidation."
    "Tanto [A] como [W] la miran con una mezcla de alivio y temor."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1241
translate spanish d13c_7133ef3f:

    # "You lay back in the comfortable knowledge of the affection and genuine joy your family members feel for one another."
    "Te recuestas en el cómodo conocimiento del afecto y la alegría genuina que sienten los miembros de tu familia unos por otros."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1242
translate spanish d13c_ae43c8d7:

    # S "Well, this was all pretty great. I missed your cooking, [persistent.mom]."
    S "¡Bueno, esto ha sido realmente genial! Extrañaba tu cocina, [persistent.mom]."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1243
translate spanish d13c_91ffdb94:

    # W "I did go all out this time. I'm happy you liked it."
    W "Esta vez sí que me he esforzado. Me alegro de que te haya gustado."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1244
translate spanish d13c_390cd1e5:

    # A "Yes, yes, the food was wonderful as always, but..."
    A "Sí, sí, la comida fue maravillosa como siempre, pero..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1245
translate spanish d13c_1bcc331e:

    # A "How was the Zone? Was it as dangerous as they say? Were you in danger?"
    A "¿Cómo era la Zona? ¿Era tan peligrosa como dicen? ¿Estuviste en peligro?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1246
translate spanish d13c_a94a277f:

    # A "Did you meet anybody?"
    A "¿Conociste a alguien?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1247
translate spanish d13c_08570947:

    # W "[A], let her breathe, girl... give her a chance to reply."
    W "[A], déjala respirar, chica... Dale la oportunidad de responder."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1250
translate spanish d13c_219cafac:

    # "[S] smiles quietly, before replying."
    "[S] sonríe en silencio, antes de responder."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1253
translate spanish d13c_79ef0fa3:

    # S "It's ok, [persistent.mom], I get it. I didn't really tell her much, so far."
    S "Está bien, [persistent.mom], lo entiendo. La verdad es que no le he contado mucho, hasta ahora."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1256
translate spanish d13c_ea6ebdc2:

    # "Turning towards her sister, she continues..."
    "Volviéndose hacia su hermana, ella continúa..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1259
translate spanish d13c_4c26c2f2:

    # S "It was... an experience, for sure; and yeah, I was in danger multiple times. But I am back. I made it."
    S "Fue... una experiencia, seguro; y sí, estuve en peligro varias veces. Pero he vuelto. Lo he conseguido."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1262
translate spanish d13c_bb7e7cc8:

    # A "And you got a nice ride out of it too! Those are rare!"
    A "¡Y además conseguiste un buen vehículo! ¡Esos son difíciles de encontrar!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1265
translate spanish d13c_d113319d:

    # W "I reckon you didn't just find it lying in the dunes..."
    W "Sospecho que no la encontraste simplemente tirada en las dunas..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1268
translate spanish d13c_b5574aa3:

    # "An awkward silence follows the apprehensive words, as [S]'s face turns serious for a second, hardened and battle weary. She looks downcast."
    "Un silencio incómodo sigue a las palabras aprensivas, mientras el rostro de [S] se vuelve serio durante un segundo, endurecido y cansado de la batalla. Parece abatida."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1271
translate spanish d13c_ac7918f6:

    # S "Yeah... no... I didn't..."
    S "Sí... no... Yo no..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1274
translate spanish d13c_90fe0fca:

    # S "Anyway, it's mine now."
    S "En fin, ahora es mía."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1277
translate spanish d13c_c0aaa4c4:

    # "The conversation has a momentary lull, before [A] starts talking again."
    "La conversación tiene una pausa momentánea, antes de que [A] empiece a hablar de nuevo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1278
translate spanish d13c_324214b4:

    # A "So you're officially a Stalker now?"
    A "¿Así que ahora eres oficialmente una Acechadora?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1279
translate spanish d13c_6c5b7343:

    # Z "I guess..."
    Z "Supongo..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1280
translate spanish d13c_5e65dce6:

    # A "Are you proud, [persistent.dad]?"
    A "¿Estás orgulloso, [persistent.dad]?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1283
translate spanish d13c_741f8894:

    # "You take a second to answer, looking [S] straight in the eyes."
    "Te tomas un segundo para responder, mirando a [S] directamente a los ojos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1286
translate spanish d13c_75571737:

    # Z "I am very proud, yes. Proud and relieved."
    Z "Estoy muy orgulloso, sí. Orgulloso y aliviado."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1287
translate spanish d13c_d51f7b88:

    # "[S] doesn't say anything, but you can see a barely contained joy cross her face for a few seconds."
    "[S] no dice nada, pero puedes ver cómo una alegría apenas contenida cruza su rostro durante unos segundos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1291
translate spanish d13c_ededd2ad:

    # A "Does that mean you'll finally stop dancing around each other like a pair of virgins?"
    A "¿Significa eso que por fin dejaréis de bailar el uno alrededor del otro como un par de vírgenes?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1294
translate spanish d13c_3db5aefc:

    # "A burst of laughter escapes your wife, as she looks you up and down, a mischievous glint in her eyes."
    "Una risa repentina se le escapa a tu esposa, mientras te mira de arriba abajo con un brillo travieso en los ojos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1297
translate spanish d13c_ee1e2595:

    # W "Yes, husband, is that what that means?"
    W "Sí, marido, ¿es eso lo que significa?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1300
translate spanish d13c_6c99a5ce:

    # "She looks at you, waiting for a response, until [S] speaks up..."
    "Ella te mira, esperando una respuesta, hasta que [S] habla..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1301
translate spanish d13c_aa589a35:

    # S "Well... actually..."
    S "Bueno... en realidad..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1304
translate spanish d13c_b1b55eea:

    # S "Ehm..."
    S "Ejem..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1305
translate spanish d13c_a1177bb7:

    # "[S] has the good grace to look embarrassed for a second, before continuing."
    "[S] tiene la delicadeza de parecer avergonzada durante un segundo, antes de continuar."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1308
translate spanish d13c_5cc217d4:

    # S "We actually have..."
    S "En realidad hemos..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1311
translate spanish d13c_3dcdc837:

    # "She looks at you, not with regret, but a hint of embarrassment, revealing an unexpected shyness..."
    "Te mira, no con pesar, sino con una pizca de vergüenza, revelando una timidez inesperada..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1314
translate spanish d13c_a8b3b585:

    # A "No way!"
    A "¡De ninguna manera!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1317
translate spanish d13c_1f67b7c2:

    # A "You and [persistent.dad] finally did it?!"
    A "¡¿Tú y [persistent.dad] por fin lo habéis hecho?!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1320
translate spanish d13c_bdb809bf:

    # A "Heeee...."
    A "Jeeee..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1323
translate spanish d13c_8c0c9005:

    # A "But wait... when though?"
    A "Pero espera... ¿Pero cuándo?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1326
translate spanish d13c_b045b6e8:

    # W "Yes, [persistent.player_name], would you care to tell me why I'm only finding out about it now?"
    W "Sí, [persistent.player_name], ¿te importaría decirme por qué me estoy enterando de esto ahora?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1329
translate spanish d13c_db574596:

    # Z "I just didn't think that I should tell you without [S] being present and part of the conversation... and I figured it was her story to tell, not mine."
    Z "Simplemente pensé que no debía contártelo sin que [S] estuviera presente y formara parte de la conversación... y supuse que era su historia la que tenía que contar, no la mía."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1332
translate spanish d13c_73d2a117:

    # W "Mmmh... I see, that makes sense."
    W "Mmmh... Ya veo, eso tiene sentido."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1337
translate spanish d13c_1eac0a7c:

    # "Ignoring the exchange between you and your wife, [A] is still drowning [S] in questions, the Zone completely forgotten as she fishes for juicy details."
    "Ignorando el intercambio entre tu mujer y tú, [A] sigue ahogando a [S] en preguntas, la Zona completamente olvidada mientras ella pesca jugosos detalles."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1338
translate spanish d13c_f3dbf597:

    # "You look at the women of your family, as [W] and [A] both turn to [S]."
    "Miras a las mujeres de tu familia, mientras [W] y [A] se vuelven hacia [S]."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1339
translate spanish d13c_4ac97d72:

    # "As [S] recoils back somewhat defensive, the two other women manifest the basic questions, such as how, when and where things happened between the two of you."
    "Mientras [S] retrocede un tanto a la defensiva, las otras dos mujeres manifiestan las preguntas básicas, tales como cómo, cuándo y dónde ocurrieron las cosas entre vosotros dos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1340
translate spanish d13c_e0b96274:

    # S "It happened before the Zone actually. There's this really romantic place not too far from it, where we met these travellers..."
    S "De hecho, ocurrió antes de la Zona. Hay un lugar muy romántico no muy lejos de ella, donde conocimos a esos viajeros..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1341
translate spanish d13c_187fb99d:

    # "As [S] tells the story of her first time with you, you scour the faces of the women. Both [A] and [W] seem to take the news well."
    "Mientras [S] te cuenta la historia de su primera vez contigo, recorres los rostros de las mujeres. Tanto [A] como [W] parecen tomarse bien la noticia."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1342
translate spanish d13c_29c8db35:

    # "[A] looks genuinely happy for her sister, and behind [W]'s eyes you almost see a glimpse of anticipation."
    "[A] parece realmente feliz por su hermana, y detrás de los ojos de [W] casi ves un atisbo de anticipación."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1345
translate spanish d13c_38d5a023:

    # "Still, there's going to be a long discussion tonight, that's for sure."
    "Sin embargo, seguramente habrá una larga discusión esta noche, eso es seguro."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1346
translate spanish d13c_4e57b114:

    # S "So, yeah... I guess [persistent.dad] understood the moment..."
    S "Entonces, sí... Supongo que [persistent.dad] entendió el momento..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1347
translate spanish d13c_8bc037d2:

    # A "Yes, but how was it!?"
    A "Sí, pero ¿cómo fue?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1348
translate spanish d13c_a3cb52d4:

    # "Undeterred, [A] nags her sister for more details, this time joined playfully by your wife."
    "Sin desanimarse, [A] insiste a su hermana por más detalles, esta vez acompañada de forma juguetona por tu esposa."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1349
translate spanish d13c_3c8da6a1:

    # "When their curiosity is sated and [S] refuses to answer the more... intimate questions [A] ends up asking, the conversation shifts to the events of the house."
    "Cuando su curiosidad se sacia y [S] se niega a responder a las preguntas más... íntimas que [A] acaba formulando, la conversación se desplaza hacia los acontecimientos de la casa."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1350
translate spanish d13c_bf6ab40d:

    # S "Enough about that now. I am not going to tell you that, [A], so just drop it."
    S "Ya está bien de hablar de eso. No voy a decírtelo, [A], así que déjalo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1354
translate spanish d13c_c1acffd1:

    # S "So... why don't you tell me what's been happening here instead? I've been away for days."
    S "Entonces... ¿por qué no me cuentas qué ha estado sucediendo aquí en lugar de eso? He estado fuera durante días."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1355
translate spanish d13c_927930e3:

    # A "Well, you remember our cousin Nadia...?"
    A "Bueno, ¿te acuerdas de nuestra prima Nadia...?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1358
translate spanish d13c_7f805622:

    # "As they keep chatting about everything that happened in the meantime, you start drifting into thought..."
    "Mientras siguen charlando sobre todo lo que ha pasado desde entonces, tú empiezas a sumirte en tus pensamientos..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1359
translate spanish d13c_062e5c3a:

    # "...and your attention shifts away from a conversation you know you play no part in."
    "... y tu atención se desvía de una conversación en la que sabes que no participas."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1367
translate spanish d13d_9669528e:

    # "Later..."
    "Más tarde..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1371
translate spanish d13d_5565d488:

    # Z "This is our thing now, isn't it?"
    Z "Esto es lo nuestro ahora, ¿no?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1372
translate spanish d13d_c86a0909:

    # S "Heh... yeah... I like sundowns, I guess..."
    S "Je... sí... me gustan los atardeceres, supongo..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1375
translate spanish d13d_8cceeb41:

    # Z "How's your wound?"
    Z "¿Cómo está tu herida?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1376
translate spanish d13d_99b12d41:

    # S "It's getting better... I was lucky."
    S "Está mejorando... He tenido suerte."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1377
translate spanish d13d_283a112d:

    # Z "I'm happy you made it back safe and mostly sound."
    Z "Me alegro de que hayas vuelto sana y salva."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1378
translate spanish d13d_bbbe99d4:

    # S "I guess you trained me well."
    S "Supongo que me entrenaste bien."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1379
translate spanish d13d_8dcc935e:

    # Z "Don't sell yourself short, [S]."
    Z "No te subestimes, [S]."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1380
translate spanish d13d_549f5125:

    # Z "I am proud of you, girl."
    Z "Estoy orgulloso de ti, chica."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1381
translate spanish d13d_368776fd:

    # S "Thank you [persistent.dad]."
    S "Gracias [persistent.dad]."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1383
translate spanish d13d_e1c1af61:

    # Z "So... how was it, really?"
    Z "Entonces... ¿cómo fue, en realidad?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1384
translate spanish d13d_90e10335:

    # Z "Anything like you imagined?"
    Z "¿Algo como lo que habías imaginado?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1387
translate spanish d13d_e21dd7f1:

    # "[S] contemplates her words for a few seconds, before replying."
    "[S] contempla sus palabras durante unos segundos, antes de responder."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1390
translate spanish d13d_eed099bd:

    # S "I think I understand you better, now."
    S "Creo que ahora te entiendo mejor."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1391
translate spanish d13d_d091f6ed:

    # S "You were right when you were telling me that traveling through those places is... different."
    S "Tenías razón cuando me decías que viajar por esos lugares es... diferente."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1394
translate spanish d13d_6e4484ca:

    # "You wait for her to continue, not wanting to interrupt her train of thought."
    "Esperas a que continúe, sin querer interrumpir su hilo de pensamientos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1397
translate spanish d13d_9caa8465:

    # S "I've seen places that don't really exist..."
    S "He visto lugares que en realidad no existen..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1398
translate spanish d13d_bc44e214:

    # S "...talked to a woman long dead..."
    S "... hablar con una mujer muerta hace tiempo..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1399
translate spanish d13d_d5be21e4:

    # S "...I've seen a young man die for nothing..."
    S "... he visto morir a un joven por nada..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1400
translate spanish d13d_e5cc25f8:

    # S "...and after all that..."
    S "... y después de todo eso..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1403
translate spanish d13d_7e624a41:

    # "[S] shivers for a second, seeking comfort in your embrace."
    "[S] tiembla durante un segundo, buscando consuelo en tu abrazo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1404
translate spanish d13d_d97acf9d:

    # S "I've killed people... over a stupid piece of paper..."
    S "He matado a gente... por un estúpido trozo de papel..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1405
translate spanish d13d_3cd2b435:

    # "You hold on to your [persistent.da], giving her the time to grieve for her actions and thoughts."
    "Te aferras a tu [persistent.da], dándole tiempo para que se aflija por sus acciones y pensamientos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1406
translate spanish d13d_9aef7ade:

    # S "There was this tree, [persistent.dad]... such a beautiful one too. I wish I could describe it to you in more than words."
    S "Había un árbol, [persistent.dad]... tan hermoso también. Ojalá pudiera describírtelo con algo más que palabras."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1407
translate spanish d13d_62eca10b:

    # S "Have you ever encountered something like that?"
    S "¿Te has encontrado alguna vez con algo así?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1408
translate spanish d13d_e99028a0:

    # Z "I have had my own experiences in those places... sometimes it seems that nature overcomes the devastation of the end of days in those pockets of... I am not sure how to call them."
    Z "He tenido mis propias experiencias en esos lugares... a veces parece que la naturaleza supera la devastación del fin de los días en esos focos de... No estoy seguro de cómo llamarlos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1409
translate spanish d13d_256d3a49:

    # S "I thought I might have dreamed it, but it's so hard to tell the difference when every tool you are trained to use just..."
    S "Pensé que podría haberlo soñado, pero es tan difícil notar la diferencia cuando todas las herramientas que te han enseñado a utilizar..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1410
translate spanish d13d_0b89cb77:

    # Z "The compass?"
    Z "¿La brújula?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1413
translate spanish d13d_13056ac7:

    # "[S] reacts with a surprised motion."
    "[S] reacciona con un movimiento de sorpresa."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1416
translate spanish d13d_222aced9:

    # S "How do you know?"
    S "¿Cómo lo sabes?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1419
translate spanish d13d_6b7b55e1:

    # Z "It happens, sometimes."
    Z "A veces ocurre."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1422
translate spanish d13d_68a0464f:

    # "A few more minutes of silence pass, as [S] mulls over your words, nodding occasionally."
    "Pasan unos minutos más de silencio, mientras [S] reflexiona sobre tus palabras, asintiendo de vez en cuando."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1423
translate spanish d13d_6ff15415:

    # S "Have you looked at that motorbike?"
    S "¿Te has fijado en esa moto?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1424
translate spanish d13d_72d70cc6:

    # Z "I have. It's a nice find. I have only ever seen wasteland travellers or nomad tribes ride these things."
    Z "Lo hice. Es un buen hallazgo. Sólo he visto a viajeros del páramo o a tribus nómadas montar esas cosas."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1425
translate spanish d13d_16844fc2:

    # Z "How did you get it?"
    Z "¿Cómo la has conseguido?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1426
translate spanish d13d_bde4fcb8:

    # S "I took it from one of the bandits who attacked me."
    S "Se la quité a uno de los bandidos que me atacaron."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1427
translate spanish d13d_971a98df:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1428
translate spanish d13d_51a3e8f6:

    # Z "What happened?"
    Z "¿Qué ha pasado?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1430
translate spanish d13d_919fec3b:

    # S "She was down on the ground, helpless. She looked at me... and I struck her down, before taking what was hers."
    S "Ella estaba en el suelo, indefensa. Me miró... y la golpeé, antes de tomar lo que era suyo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1431
translate spanish d13d_b3932c14:

    # Z "You struck down a surrendering enemy?"
    Z "¿Has abatido a un enemigo que se rendía?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1432
translate spanish d13d_d667f6d8:

    # S "She deserved it, [persistent.dad]. She was a murderer and a bandit. It was my decision."
    S "Se lo merecía, [persistent.dad]. Era una asesina y una bandida. Fue decisión mía."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1433
translate spanish d13d_06aa9063:

    # "You are taken aback by the edge in her tone, as you realise that the little girl that grew up swinging a wooden stick under your watchful eyes truly has grown into her own self."
    "Te sorprende el filo de su tono, al darte cuenta de que la niña que creció blandiendo un palo de madera bajo tu atenta mirada se ha convertido en ella misma."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1434
translate spanish d13d_45f9dd80:

    # Z "You are right, [S]."
    Z "Tienes razón, [S]."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1436
translate spanish d13d_642791f0:

    # S "She was down on the ground, helpless. She looked up at me... so I stepped past her, leaving her there."
    S "Estaba en el suelo, indefensa. Me miró... y pasé a su lado, dejándola allí."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1437
translate spanish d13d_abb123c2:

    # S "{i}*sigh*{/i}"
    S "{i}*suspiro*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1438
translate spanish d13d_89691232:

    # S "And then I took what was hers..."
    S "Y entonces tomé lo que era suyo..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1439
translate spanish d13d_d037551e:

    # S "I can't imagine she made it out alive."
    S "No puedo imaginar que haya salido con vida."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1440
translate spanish d13d_806b8eec:

    # "You sense that the idea of looting a defeated foe is still uneasy for her, so you let the moment pass."
    "Percibes que la idea de saquear a un enemigo derrotado aún le resulta incómoda, así que dejas pasar el momento."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1443
translate spanish d13d_a72224b0:

    # Z "How do you feel, now that you're back?"
    Z "¿Cómo te sientes, ahora que has vuelto?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1444
translate spanish d13d_af351f4c:

    # S "I'm fine, I guess. I wasn't gone for too long, even if at times it felt like it..."
    S "Estoy bien, supongo. No he estado fuera demasiado tiempo, aunque a veces lo pareciera..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1445
translate spanish d13d_94373ef0:

    # S "But... anyways... let's start over. I bet you have questions. I can tell you everything."
    S "Pero... en fin... empecemos de nuevo. Seguro que tienes preguntas. Puedo contártelo todo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1454
translate spanish d13d_menu_a6c19138:

    # Z "Tell me about the young man you mentioned."
    Z "Háblame del joven que mencionaste."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1457
translate spanish d13d_menu_777f1f3f:

    # S "It's such a sad thing, [persistent.dad]... I don't think he was older than me. He was looking for his father..."
    S "Es tan triste, [persistent.dad]... No creo que fuera mayor que yo. Buscaba a su padre..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1460
translate spanish d13d_menu_86924c7e:

    # Z "What happened to him?"
    Z "¿Qué le pasó?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1463
translate spanish d13d_menu_ff20aadf:

    # S "He was shot right in front of my eyes. An arrow through the head. Never saw it coming."
    S "Le dispararon delante de mis ojos. Una flecha en la cabeza. Nunca lo vi venir."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1464
translate spanish d13d_menu_bd915253:

    # S "I guess the only reason why I wasn't hit is that I was hiding behind a wall, out of sight."
    S "Supongo que la única razón por la que no me alcanzaron es que estaba escondida detrás de una pared, fuera de la vista."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1465
translate spanish d13d_menu_0a559bfb:

    # S "I managed to run away, only to encounter them again later."
    S "Conseguí huir, sólo para volver a encontrarme con ellos más tarde."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1468
translate spanish d13d_menu_461723e5:

    # Z "How did you know about his reason for being there... his father?"
    Z "¿Cómo sabías el motivo por el que estaba allí... su padre?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1471
translate spanish d13d_menu_3cc22e97:

    # S "He was just telling me about it when it happened. Also, I did find his father too, what remained of him. I looted his crossbow and a letter he wrote to his family."
    S "Me lo estaba contando cuando ocurrió. Además, también encontré a su padre, lo que quedaba de él. Saqueé su ballesta y una carta que escribió a su familia."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1474
translate spanish d13d_menu_3510e3bb:

    # S "You will have to show me how to use the crossbow."
    S "Tendrás que enseñarme a utilizar la ballesta."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1477
translate spanish d13d_menu_2f9d6280:

    # Z "That's... interesting. I am not sure I am the best person for that. Maybe Mandisa..."
    Z "Eso es... interesante. No estoy seguro de ser la persona más indicada para ello. Quizá Mandisa..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1484
translate spanish d13d_menu_d89b72f4:

    # Z "You mentioned a girl with elven ears?"
    Z "¿Mencionaste a una chica con orejas élficas?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1487
translate spanish d13d_menu_25506ca5:

    # S "Yeah... I was on the road towards the industrial area, but I made a mistake."
    S "Sí... Estaba en el camino hacia la zona industrial, pero cometí un error."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1488
translate spanish d13d_menu_2cf42595:

    # S "Another emission was approaching, and I wasn't prepared."
    S "Se acercaba otra emisión, y yo no estaba preparada."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1489
translate spanish d13d_menu_59063fdc:

    # S "I don't think I would've found a way out... but then this girl appeared, in one of the apartment buildings."
    S "No creo que hubiera encontrado una salida... pero entonces apareció esta chica, en uno de los edificios de apartamentos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1490
translate spanish d13d_menu_dd8c95e0:

    # S "She put a ladder down for me, shortly before the first wave hit."
    S "Bajó una escalera para mí, poco antes de que llegara la primera ola."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1491
translate spanish d13d_menu_9b352649:

    # S "When I stepped inside, she was looking at old notes... or a book? Maybe some writings? I couldn't see."
    S "Cuando entré, estaba mirando unas viejas notas... ¿o un libro? ¿Quizá algún escrito? No pude verlo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1492
translate spanish d13d_menu_b5e58eb1:

    # S "Her eyes were big, and her expression sad. We exchanged some words, but..."
    S "Sus ojos eran grandes y su expresión triste. Intercambiamos algunas palabras, pero..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1494
translate spanish d13d_menu_89d520c4:

    # S "...I don't know. When I came back later, she was gone."
    S "... no lo sé. Cuando volví más tarde, ya se había ido."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1496
translate spanish d13d_menu_825622e0:

    # S "...when I came back, she was hanging from the ceiling."
    S "... cuando volví, estaba colgada del techo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1497
translate spanish d13d_menu_159cd9e8:

    # S "She said something about not having anyone left for her. It's sad..."
    S "Dijo algo de que no le quedaba nadie. Es triste..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1498
translate spanish d13d_menu_37251171:

    # Z "People come to die in the Zone. They make it their grave. A silent grave, as we will never find out why."
    Z "La gente viene a morir a la Zona. La convierten en su tumba. Una tumba silenciosa, pues nunca sabremos por qué."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1500
translate spanish d13d_menu_0115a082:

    # "You remember what you read in [I]'s notes, about her friend who went to the Zone."
    "Recuerdas lo que leíste en las notas de [I], sobre su amiga que fue a la Zona."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1501
translate spanish d13d_menu_881acdab:

    # "Undoubtedly, this must've been her."
    "Sin duda, debe de haber sido ella."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1504
translate spanish d13d_menu_bf4e7852:

    # Z "Did she mention anything about a friend of hers?"
    Z "¿Mencionó algo sobre una amiga suya?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1507
translate spanish d13d_menu_e14f2c5c:

    # S "Huh? Why do you ask that? I don't... think she did."
    S "¿Eh? ¿Por qué preguntas eso? No... creo que lo hiciera."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1510
translate spanish d13d_menu_e9eb5925:

    # Z "Hm... I might have an idea who that girl was."
    Z "Hm... Puede que tenga una idea de quién era esa chica."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1513
translate spanish d13d_menu_a4e1ff5e:

    # S "How so?"
    S "¿Cómo es eso?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1516
translate spanish d13d_menu_e0dcc0a6:

    # Z "Do you remember that elf girl that visited us?"
    Z "¿Te acuerdas de aquella chica elfa que nos visitó?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1519
translate spanish d13d_menu_abb03d53:

    # S "I don't..."
    S "Yo no..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1522
translate spanish d13d_menu_5507706a:

    # S "Oh, I remember!"
    S "Oh, ¡me acuerdo!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1525
translate spanish d13d_menu_d56403e8:

    # Z "It's a long story. I will tell you more another time."
    Z "Es una larga historia. Te la contaré en otra ocasión."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1532
translate spanish d13d_menu_9f31366d:

    # Z "Tell me more about the lone woman in the house."
    Z "Cuéntame más sobre la mujer solitaria de la casa."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1533
translate spanish d13d_menu_354b1c72:

    # S "Her name was Julia..."
    S "Se llamaba Julia..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1536
translate spanish d13d_menu_ad864e67:

    # "As [S] tells you about her encounter with this apparition, she paints a vivid picture of the time spent in her company, under the blossoming tree."
    "Mientras [S] te cuenta su encuentro con esta aparición, te pinta una vívida imagen del tiempo que pasó en su compañía, bajo el árbol en flor."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1539
translate spanish d13d_menu_3ded8a60:

    # "A house, out in the open, and a woman, kind and welcoming."
    "Una casa, en medio de la nada, y una mujer amable y acogedora."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1540
translate spanish d13d_menu_2571395a:

    # "Her past, her hesitation to keep going. How she could not let go."
    "Su pasado, su duda para seguir adelante. Cómo no podía soltar lastre."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1541
translate spanish d13d_menu_134770c0:

    # "It sounded like one of the stories you read about when the bombs were falling... stories of two souls being ripped apart, from one moment to another."
    "Sonaba a esas historias que lees sobre cuando empezaron a caer las bombas... historias de dos almas destrozadas, de un momento a otro."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1542
translate spanish d13d_menu_d8805d53:

    # "What happens to those who don't know that they died? Are they still looking out for their loved ones? Are they still waiting in place of their death?"
    "¿Qué les ocurre a los que no saben que han muerto? ¿Siguen buscando a sus seres queridos? ¿Siguen esperando en el lugar de su muerte?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1544
translate spanish d13d_menu_1a5366dc:

    # "Is it hope that makes them linger here? Is it sadness? Is it pain?"
    "¿Es la esperanza lo que les hace quedarse aquí? ¿Es la tristeza? ¿Es el dolor?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1547
translate spanish d13d_menu_fa4ee072:

    # S "You know... Julia wasn't the only person like that in there..."
    S "Sabes... Julia no era la única persona así ahí dentro..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1548
translate spanish d13d_menu_955f480e:

    # Z "There were more people like her?"
    Z "¿Había más gente como ella?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1549
translate spanish d13d_menu_1c0dedb8:

    # S "Those that are not living under us... or have lived... I don't know."
    S "Los que no viven bajo nosotros... o han vivido... no lo sé."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1552
translate spanish d13d_menu_b22dda78:

    # S "But yes, there was this one apartment building... heard some knocking from the outside."
    S "Pero sí, había un edificio de apartamentos... oí unos golpes desde fuera."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1553
translate spanish d13d_menu_e71a7bb6:

    # S "I was trapped in there... and had to go through what seemed like a family's last moments..."
    S "Estaba atrapada allí... y tuve que presenciar lo que parecían los últimos momentos de una familia..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1554
translate spanish d13d_menu_3c77ebdf:

    # S "I found a diary, and I saw a... man I suppose? Who was coming home to see his wife."
    S "Encontré un diario y vi a un... ¿hombre, supongo? Que volvía a casa para ver a su mujer."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1555
translate spanish d13d_menu_9d8f4ed8:

    # S "It was scary, and I panicked... I would have never gone inside that apartment if I knew what I would experience."
    S "Daba miedo y entré en pánico... Nunca habría entrado en aquel apartamento si hubiera sabido lo que iba a experimentar."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1556
translate spanish d13d_menu_e36688e6:

    # S "...but now, I just feel pity for them..."
    S "... pero ahora, sólo siento lástima por ellos..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1558
translate spanish d13d_menu_c98a3cdb:

    # Z "There are some things that you don't want to do and you pledge to yourself that you won't do, you forbid yourself, and then suddenly they happen all by themselves."
    Z "Hay cosas que no quieres hacer y te prometes a ti mismo que no las harás, te lo prohíbes, y de repente ocurren solas."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1559
translate spanish d13d_menu_db05707d:

    # Z "You don't even have time to think about them, and they don't make it to the cognitive centres of the brain."
    Z "Ni siquiera tienes tiempo de pensar en ellas, y no llegan a los centros cognitivos del cerebro."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1560
translate spanish d13d_menu_2a611898:

    # Z "They just happen and that's it, and you're left just watching yourself with surprise, and convincing yourself that it wasn't your fault, it just happened all by itself."
    Z "Ocurren y ya está, y te quedas mirándote con sorpresa, y convenciéndote de que no ha sido culpa tuya, que ha ocurrido por sí solo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1563
translate spanish d13d_menu_9fee2412:

    # S "That is... true. Where did you get that?"
    S "Esto es... cierto. ¿De dónde lo has sacado?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1564
translate spanish d13d_menu_a03acab7:

    # Z "From some old prewar author... I think it was written in 2033? Back when they counted time differently..."
    Z "De algún viejo autor de antes de la guerra... ¿Creo que fue escrito en 2033? En la época en que se contaba el tiempo de otra manera..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1565
translate spanish d13d_menu_2d21c140:

    # Z "I don't remember, but it stuck with me."
    Z "No lo recuerdo, pero se me quedó grabado."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1567
translate spanish d13d_menu_1624c8cc:

    # "While telling you about her adventure, [S] seems to ask herself the same questions. And you know you can't give her an answer."
    "Mientras te cuenta su aventura, [S] parece hacerse las mismas preguntas. Y sabes que no puedes darle una respuesta."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1568
translate spanish d13d_menu_217e67ce:

    # "You sense that a little corner of her heart will forever remember the impression this experience left on her, and for a minute you wonder if it's a good thing."
    "Sientes que un pequeño rincón de su corazón recordará para siempre la impresión que le causó esta experiencia, y por un momento te preguntas si es algo bueno."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1569
translate spanish d13d_menu_3a054367:

    # "Then you realise that it's not something for you to solve, or confront. This is your [persistent.da]'s life and it would diminish her achievement if you tried to intervene."
    "Entonces te das cuenta de que no es algo que debas resolver o afrontar. Se trata de la vida de tu [persistent.da] y disminuiría su logro si intentaras intervenir."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1576
translate spanish d13d_menu_02726ee6:

    # Z "Did you find something in the industrial area?"
    Z "¿Encontraste algo en la zona industrial?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1579
translate spanish d13d_menu_3b19d782:

    # S "Yeah... I was looking for that thing your old mentor talked about. It was the first thing on my list as I entered the place."
    S "Sí... Estaba buscando eso de lo que me habló tu antiguo mentor. Era lo primero en mi lista al entrar en el lugar."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1580
translate spanish d13d_menu_0e81f939:

    # S "I was following the map closely. When I got there, the air was so dirty and thick, not much sunlight could pass through."
    S "Seguía el mapa de cerca. Cuando llegué allí, el aire estaba tan sucio y espeso que no podía pasar mucha luz solar."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1583
translate spanish d13d_menu_09ea4fbd:

    # S "There wasn't anything growing there, the place was truly dead."
    S "Allí no crecía nada, el lugar estaba verdaderamente muerto."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1586
translate spanish d13d_menu_9ed1e53f:

    # S "Anyway... I didn't know where to start looking, but I managed to find some notes and text that guided me along; stuck in the remains of people who worked there."
    S "En fin... No sabía por dónde empezar a buscar, pero conseguí encontrar algunas notas y textos que me guiaron; pegados en los restos de personas que trabajaban allí."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1589
translate spanish d13d_menu_e560114b:

    # S "It led me down into a bunker, at least that's what I thought it was, because of those huge fans."
    S "Me llevó a un búnker, al menos eso es lo que pensé que era, debido a esos enormes ventiladores."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1592
translate spanish d13d_menu_105cb855:

    # S "I found this thing there..."
    S "Encontré esto allí..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1593
translate spanish d13d_menu_2da38b63:

    # S "It's glowing, like some of these ancient street lights you showed me in pictures. It looks... pretty, in its own way."
    S "Está brillando, como algunas de esas antiguas farolas que me enseñaste en fotos. Parece... bonita, a su manera."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1596
translate spanish d13d_menu_a29cd6c5:

    # S "The people that died in this bunker had some notes about it lying next to them. We can read them together later."
    S "Las personas que murieron en este búnker tenían algunas notas al respecto junto a ellos. Podemos leerlas juntos más tarde."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1599
translate spanish d13d_menu_22f2b5fa:

    # S "I... don't know if that is what your old Master wanted me to get. But if anything stuck out in that area, it was this."
    S "Yo... no sé si eso es lo que tu antiguo Maestro quería que consiguiera. Pero si algo destacaba en esa zona, era esto."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1602
translate spanish d13d_menu_9dcafbc0:

    # S "Even centuries later, it's all glowy and buzzing with energy!"
    S "¡Incluso siglos después, está toda resplandeciente y zumbando de energía!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1605
translate spanish d13d_menu_f8588624:

    # Z "If nothing else, it's a lamp that has been shedding light for centuries, that alone makes it valuable."
    Z "Aunque sólo sea porque es una lámpara que lleva siglos arrojando luz, eso ya la hace valiosa."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1606
translate spanish d13d_menu_4d1fb1c8:

    # Z "You did great! Ancient technology that is still working and doesn't need to be fixed is very rare."
    Z "¡Lo has hecho muy bien! La tecnología antigua que aún funciona y no necesita ser reparada es muy rara."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1607
translate spanish d13d_menu_3488c591:

    # Z "You'll have to show me later, for sure."
    Z "Tendrás que enseñármelo más tarde, seguro."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1610
translate spanish d13d_menu_058f15f3:

    # "As [S] smiles, you notice that despite her enthusiastic response, she is still very tired from her adventure."
    "Mientras [S] sonríe, notas que, a pesar de su respuesta entusiasta, sigue muy cansada de su aventura."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1616
translate spanish d13d_end_5cb770aa:

    # Z "So... tell me how you got into that fight again?"
    Z "Entonces... ¿cómo fue que te metiste en esa pelea otra vez?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1617
translate spanish d13d_end_6555ebbe:

    # S "Well... do you remember the Queen told you I should find someone for her?"
    S "Bueno... ¿Recuerdas que la Reina te dijo que debía encontrar a alguien para ella?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1618
translate spanish d13d_end_fb7c6ac2:

    # Z "I was going to ask you about that too, but continue."
    Z "También iba a preguntarte por eso, pero continúa."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1621
translate spanish d13d_end_edc05daf:

    # S "It turns out she really hasn't told you everything."
    S "Resultó que en realidad ella no te lo había contado todo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1622
translate spanish d13d_end_02024870:

    # S "I actually stumbled on the man almost by chance, on my way out of the Zone."
    S "En realidad me tropecé con el hombre casi por casualidad, al salir de la Zona."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1625
translate spanish d13d_end_e1fddebb:

    # S "But he wasn't alone. In fact, there were 3 more people with him."
    S "Pero no estaba solo. De hecho, había 3 personas más con él."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1628
translate spanish d13d_end_7d07a632:

    # Z "{i}*sigh*{/i} This girl..."
    Z "{i}*suspiro*{/i} Esta chica..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1629
translate spanish d13d_end_5ee835f5:

    # Z "If she knowingly sent you into a trap..."
    Z "Si ella te envió a sabiendas a una trampa..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1632
translate spanish d13d_end_42349262:

    # "Half amused by your display of frustration, [S] continues to talk."
    "Medio divertido por tu muestra de frustración, [S] continúa hablando."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1635
translate spanish d13d_end_ed3d88b5:

    # S "I don't know if she had all the elements. It turns out the guy she sent me after had infiltrated her court and stolen some papers."
    S "No sé si tenía todos los elementos. Resulta que el tipo tras el que me envió se había infiltrado en su corte y había robado unos papeles."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1636
translate spanish d13d_end_1f677d7f:

    # S "I have recovered those as well."
    S "También los he recuperado."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1639
translate spanish d13d_end_0d32df53:

    # S "He wasn't working alone, but I don't think his friends ever set foot in the city; at least not with him. Maybe that's why she didn't know."
    S "No trabajaba solo, pero no creo que sus amigos pisaran nunca la ciudad; al menos, no con él. Quizá por eso no lo sabía."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1642
translate spanish d13d_end_7962e3b7:

    # S "Long story short, he caught me stealing his treasures... we fought, and I had to kill him."
    S "Resumiendo, me pilló robando sus tesoros... nos peleamos y tuve que matarle."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1643
translate spanish d13d_end_9e82ad43:

    # S "Later, when I was finding my way out of the Zone, his mates caught up..."
    S "Más tarde, cuando estaba buscando la manera de salir de la Zona, sus compañeros me alcanzaron..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1644
translate spanish d13d_end_971a98df:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1646
translate spanish d13d_end_b316068e:

    # S "They caught up with me right on the edge of the Zone. They were asking me what happened to their buddy, pretending they only wanted information."
    S "Me alcanzaron justo al borde de la Zona. Me preguntaban qué le había pasado a su compañero, fingiendo que sólo querían información."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1647
translate spanish d13d_end_458d2971:

    # S "But I knew they were going to kill me regardless."
    S "Pero yo sabía que iban a matarme a pesar de todo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1648
translate spanish d13d_end_107e679f:

    # S "So I had to act first..."
    S "Así que tuve que actuar primero..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1649
translate spanish d13d_end_5e0bc2bb:

    # S "There was this woman. She was getting in my face... quite literally. With an axe."
    S "Había una mujer. Se metió en mi cara... literalmente. Con un hacha."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1650
translate spanish d13d_end_97386615:

    # S "I... had to make sure she wasn't a threat anymore... and then, the other two came for me."
    S "Yo... tenía que asegurarme de que ya no fuera una amenaza... y entonces, los otros dos vinieron a por mí."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1652
translate spanish d13d_end_6cc3dbc9:

    # S "...it was very close, [persistent.dad]..."
    S "... estuvo muy cerca, [persistent.dad]..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1653
translate spanish d13d_end_40c494d7:

    # "You take in what she just said, and let the moment pass..."
    "Asimilas lo que acaba de decir y dejas pasar el momento..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1656
translate spanish d13d_end_93f5477b:

    # Z "You made it out, [S], and that's what matters. That's always, the only thing that matters."
    Z "Has salido, [S], y eso es lo que importa. Eso es siempre, lo único que importa."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1657
translate spanish d13d_end_87bd6a1d:

    # Z "It can become easier, you know? At least mentally. Experience builds up and turns into talent."
    Z "Puede llegar a ser más fácil, ¿sabes? Al menos mentalmente. La experiencia se acumula y se convierte en talento."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1658
translate spanish d13d_end_8c03aa17:

    # Z "I am proud of you."
    Z "Estoy orgulloso de ti."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1661
translate spanish d13d_end_c19ac202:

    # "She smiles..."
    "Ella sonríe..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1664
translate spanish d13d_end_1730dc33:

    # S "[persistent.dad!c]... can we go on an adventure together again?"
    S "¿[persistent.dad!c]... podemos volver a vivir una aventura juntos?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1665
translate spanish d13d_end_8989d427:

    # S "I understand why I had to go in alone. But it has been only a few times of us going out together, before the Zone appeared."
    S "Entiendo por qué tuve que entrar sola. Pero han sido pocas las veces que hemos salido juntos, antes de que apareciera la Zona."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1668
translate spanish d13d_end_844140ed:

    # S "I miss that time. Would you like to?"
    S "Echo de menos esa época. ¿Te gustaría?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1673
translate spanish d13d_end_6abe333a:

    # Z "Of course."
    Z "Por supuesto."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1674
translate spanish d13d_end_a5817479:

    # Z "I might get older, but I am still ready to show you how it's done."
    Z "Puede que me haga mayor, pero sigo dispuesto a enseñarte cómo se hace."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1677
translate spanish d13d_end_e406baea:

    # Z "Hell yes."
    Z "Diablos sí."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1678
translate spanish d13d_end_81a69d39:

    # Z "We make a great team."
    Z "Formamos un gran equipo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1681
translate spanish d13d_end_4f4fe6d7:

    # Z "Fuck yeah."
    Z "Joder, sí."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1685
translate spanish d13d_end_58ce198f:

    # S "I guess that too... {i}*giggles*{/i}"
    S "Supongo que también... {i}*risitas*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1688
translate spanish d13d_end_7edbaa62:

    # Z "{i}*laughs*{/i}"
    Z "{i}*risas*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1689
translate spanish d13d_end_3044a043:

    # Z "Having you at my side during tomb raids has been fun. I bet it will be again."
    Z "Tenerte a mi lado durante las incursiones en las tumbas fue divertido. Apuesto a que volverá a serlo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1693
translate spanish d13d_end_8e3913a7:

    # Z "In fact, maybe I know where you can accompany me next time."
    Z "De hecho, tal vez sepa dónde puedes acompañarme la próxima vez."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1694
translate spanish d13d_end_8455834d:

    # S "Really? Where?"
    S "¿Ah, sí? ¿Adónde?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1695
translate spanish d13d_end_fa51f79b:

    # Z "You will find out."
    Z "Lo descubrirás."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1696
translate spanish d13d_end_0bd080f6:

    # S "Awww.... [persistent.dad]!"
    S "¡Ayyy... [persistent.dad]!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1708
translate spanish d13e_ec028a85:

    # "You sit with [S] in your library, the flickering candlelight competing with the cold, glowing, undeniable presence of an artifact of days long past..."
    "Te sientas con [S] en tu biblioteca, la parpadeante luz de las velas compitiendo con la fría, resplandeciente e innegable presencia de un artefacto de días pasados..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1710
translate spanish d13e_e30b2414:

    # Z "That is... I have seen a lot of things over the years. But this..."
    Z "Eso es... He visto muchas cosas a lo largo de los años. Pero esto..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1711
translate spanish d13e_db9263b5:

    # S "It was actually lighting up the whole section of the bunker..."
    S "En realidad estaba iluminando toda la sección del búnker..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1712
translate spanish d13e_bed16d87:

    # Z "I believe you."
    Z "Te creo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1715
translate spanish d13e_bf4ce2ba:

    # "The glowing object lies in front of you. Its light is continuous, almost mesmerising."
    "El objeto resplandeciente está delante de ti. Su luz es continua, casi hipnotizadora."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1718
translate spanish d13e_e85a0c47:

    # S "Also... the Queen and her scout; you want to go over that as well, right?"
    S "También... La Reina y su explorador; también quieres repasar eso, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1721
translate spanish d13e_dd22b14e:

    # Z "Yes... we need to know what we're dealing with, and how we present the facts."
    Z "Sí... tenemos que saber a qué nos enfrentamos y cómo presentamos los hechos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1724
translate spanish d13e_f91aac50:

    # S "So... what do you want to go over first?"
    S "Entonces... ¿qué quieres revisar primero?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1733
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_f0770d3e:

    # Z "Let's talk about that scout..."
    Z "Hablemos de ese explorador..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1736
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_73f0e354:

    # "[S] puts aside the object and takes out the papers she found in the bandit's hideout, laying them in front of you..."
    "[S] deja a un lado el objeto y saca los papeles que encontró en el escondite del bandido, poniéndolos delante de ti..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1739
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_efa2fecb:

    # Z "{i}*sigh*{/i}"
    Z "{i}*suspiro*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1740
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_23ac075e:

    # Z "I'm still furious that she pretty much sent you into a trap. If you weren't so skilled with the sword, who knows what could've happened."
    Z "Sigo furioso porque prácticamente te envió a una trampa. Si no fueras tan hábil con la espada, quién sabe lo que podría haber ocurrido."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1743
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_a480559c:

    # S "Well, we don't know how well informed she was, if at all."
    S "Bueno, no sabemos lo bien informada que ella estaba, si es que lo estaba."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1744
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_a0136bf8:

    # S "I don't think she knew about the scout's tribe affiliations."
    S "No creo que ella conociera las afiliaciones tribales del explorador."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1747
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_9d4c48a4:

    # Z "Tribe?"
    Z "¿Tribales?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1750
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_7d1b31f2:

    # S "I was spying on them before I snuck into their hiding place, and they were talking about how the document they looted might benefit their tribe."
    S "Les estaba espiando antes de colarme en su escondite, y hablaban de cómo el documento que saquearon podría beneficiar a su tribu."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1751
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_9043a970:

    # S "They weren't just a bunch of thieves. The scout she had me look for had a brother. And there were two more."
    S "No eran sólo un puñado de ladrones. El explorador que me hizo buscar tenía un hermano. Y había dos más."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1752
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_3464d7db:

    # S "Anyways... we should read what the note says. I only skimmed it...and... I think you will like it."
    S "De todos modos... deberíamos leer lo que dice la nota. Yo que sólo la he hojeado... y... creo que te gustará."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1755
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_ede3167f:

    # Z "Let's see..."
    Z "Veamos..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1756
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_4276db24:

    # "As you go over the text, the faded ink gives you the clear idea that you're handling something very old."
    "Al repasar el texto, la tinta descolorida te da la clara idea de que estás manejando algo muy antiguo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1758
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_7965f399:

    # nvl clear
    # Nar "{i}My name is Paris, and I am one of the founding Elders of the New City of revisionist Egypt. I write this in the 32nd year since the founding.\nIf you find this text and you do not know who I might be, then know this: everything you think you know about Zeta, is a lie.{/i}"
    nvl clear
    Nar "{i}Mi nombre es Paris, y soy uno de los Ancianos fundadores de la Nueva Ciudad del Egipto revisionista. Escribo esto en el año 32 desde la fundación.\nSi encuentras este texto y no sabes quién soy, ten esto en cuenta: todo lo que crees saber sobre Zeta es mentira.{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1760
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_a0181f37:

    # Nar "{i}I know this because I have participated first hand in laying the foundation of our new society, and I am personally responsible for some of the biggest lies that it's built upon.{/i}"
    Nar "{i} Lo sé porque he participado de primera mano en el establecimiento de los cimientos de nuestra nueva sociedad, y soy personalmente responsable de algunas de las mayores mentiras sobre las que se construye.{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1761
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_ea0fcd3f:

    # Nar "{i}I still stand by my actions and believe that they were necessary.\nI still am loyal to the city of Zeta and the ideals that it is built upon.\nThose lies were necessary, and they will benefit us in the long run. Please understand that I truly believe this.{/i}"
    Nar "{i}Sigo siendo leal a la ciudad de Zeta y a los ideales sobre los que se construyó.\nEsas mentiras eran necesarias y nos beneficiarán a largo plazo.\nPor favor, comprende que lo creo de verdad.{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1762
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_c756d79e:

    # Nar "{i}However, I am a man of History, and it has been my life's work to preserve and uncover the lives and laws that governed our ancestors. When we set out to build Zeta, we agreed to create a legend for it, much like the tale of Romulus and Remus.{/i}"
    Nar "{i}Sin embargo, soy un hombre de Historia, y el trabajo de mi vida ha sido preservar y descubrir las vidas y leyes que gobernaron a nuestros antepasados. Cuando nos propusimos construir Zeta, acordamos crear una leyenda para ella, muy parecida a la historia de Rómulo y Remo.{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1763
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_4f9432ec:

    # Nar "{i}We needed to anchor the newborn structure of our society to an ancestral identity, a creation myth, a divine right. We collectively agreed to bury this knowledge and protect the new generations from it, so that they would buy into it and be true believers of this new world.{/i}"
    Nar "{i}Necesitábamos anclar la estructura recién nacida de nuestra sociedad a una identidad ancestral, a un mito de la creación, a un derecho divino. Acordamos colectivamente enterrar este conocimiento y proteger a las nuevas generaciones de él, para que lo aceptaran y se convirtieran en verdaderos creyentes de este nuevo mundo...{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1764
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_8c4508f2:

    # Nar "{i}They would be liberated from the nostalgia of modernism or the hankering towards the ruined civilisation we left behind. This was necessary, and still is. However, there was always, amongst us Elders, a covenant, an understanding that the real story would be preserved.{/i}"
    Nar "{i}Se liberarían de la nostalgia del modernismo o de la añoranza de la civilización en ruinas que dejamos atrás. Esto era necesario, y sigue siéndolo. Sin embargo, siempre hubo, entre nosotros, los Ancianos, un pacto, un entendimiento de que se preservaría la verdadera historia.{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1765
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_d14d8b13:

    # nvl clear
    # Nar "{i}That at least a few chosen individuals in every generation would be educated in the old ways, and informed about what really happened. The understanding was that this was necessary to prevent the newborn society from repeating the same mistakes that History proposes over and over.{/i}"
    nvl clear
    Nar "{i}Que al menos algunos individuos elegidos en cada generación fueran educados en las viejas costumbres e informados sobre lo que realmente ocurrió. Se entendía que esto era necesario para evitar que la nueva sociedad repitiera los mismos errores que la Historia propone una y otra vez.{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1767
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_b020f420:

    # Nar "{i}If the power over the city is to be wielded by the Queen and the Elders, both parties should share in the knowledge of the city's origins. Let the populace believe in the myths we have concocted for them.{/i}"
    Nar "{i}Si el poder sobre la ciudad debe ser ejercido por la Reina y los Ancianos, ambas partes deben compartir el conocimiento de los orígenes de la ciudad. Dejemos que la población crea en los mitos que hemos inventado para ella.{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1768
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_e312a88c:

    # Nar "{i}But if those of us who really should know better also fall for those same fables, then we are open to the whims of fate and one political plot away from falling into complete ignorance. As times went by however, this understanding came undone.{/i}"
    Nar "{i}Pero si los que realmente deberíamos saberlo mejor también caemos en esas mismas fábulas, entonces estamos expuestos a los caprichos del destino y a un complot político de caer en la ignorancia total. Sin embargo, con el paso del tiempo, esta comprensión se fue deshaciendo.{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1769
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_057387a5:

    # Nar "{i}As the original Elders started to die out and be replaced by new men and women, the preservation of the real knowledge has become an afterthought. The Queen is dead, all hail the new Queen... as is the natural order of things. The same should not be true for the truth.{/i}"
    Nar "{i}A medida que los Ancianos originales empezaron a extinguirse y a ser sustituidos por nuevos hombres y mujeres, la preservación del verdadero conocimiento se ha convertido en algo secundario. La Reina ha muerto, todos aclaman a la nueva Reina... como es el orden natural de las cosas. No debería ocurrir lo mismo con la verdad.{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1770
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_c205b39c:

    # Nar "{i}\nThe Truth is dead, all hail the new Truth, should not be a thing. I figured this was only going to be a momentary lapse of judgement, but I was wrong.{/i}"
    Nar "{i}\nLa Verdad ha muerto, viva la nueva Verdad, no debería existir. Supuse que sólo sería un lapsus momentáneo, pero me equivoqué.{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1771
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_e8f1d53d:

    # Nar "{i}The documents, the diaries that we have written and the computers in which we have stockpiled the knowledge of our entire civilisation are being discarded, burned, destroyed, forgotten.{/i}"
    Nar "{i}Los documentos, los diarios que hemos escrito y los ordenadores en los que hemos almacenado el conocimiento de toda nuestra civilización están siendo desechados, quemados, destruidos, olvidados.{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1772
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_10474013:

    # nvl clear
    # Nar "{i}As I see what were once our excavations bloom into new palaces and temples, I believe we have made the right choices initially. I just hope they won't be forgotten.{/i}"
    nvl clear
    Nar "{i}Mientras veo cómo lo que fueron nuestras excavaciones florecen en nuevos palacios y templos, creo que tomamos las decisiones correctas al principio. Solo espero que no se olviden.{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1774
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_e89a7328:

    # Nar "{i}I have sought refuge in this cave, in deprivation, to meditate on how to proceed from here. I am under no illusion that my time will soon come. As life ebbs away from me, it is my last wish to not let the truth become undone. May it also be my last act.{/i}"
    Nar "{i}He buscado refugio en esta cueva, en la privación, para meditar sobre cómo proceder a partir de aquí. No me hago ilusiones de que mi hora llegue pronto. A medida que la vida se aleja de mí, es mi último deseo no dejar que la verdad se deshaga. Que sea también mi último acto.{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1775
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_0c8e71ec:

    # Nar "{i}I am what remains of the original Elders. Soon only my private records will be tangible proof of how the city of Zeta truly came to be. I ransacked my own library, took my records of the last decades to my private study and had my apprentice seal it off to preserve its secrets.{/i}"
    Nar "{i}Soy lo que queda de los Ancianos originales. Pronto sólo mis registros privados serán una prueba tangible de cómo surgió realmente la ciudad de Zeta. Saqueé mi propia biblioteca, llevé mis registros de las últimas décadas a mi estudio privado e hice que mi aprendiz lo sellara para preservar sus secretos.{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1776
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_6c086b55:

    # Nar "{i}Killing my trusted apprentice with poison was the most reprehensible act of my long life, one for which I am surely damned, but it was necessary to preserve the secrecy.{/i}"
    Nar "{i}Matar a mi aprendiz de confianza con veneno fue el acto más reprobable de mi larga vida, por el que seguramente estoy condenado, pero era necesario preservar el secreto.{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1777
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_9fa4bf3c:

    # Nar "{i}I can only hope that one day my writings will be discovered anew, and brought to a ruler wiser than we are today, one who sees the value of real knowledge.\n\nThis is my word.{/i}"
    Nar "{i}Sólo puedo esperar que algún día mis escritos sean descubiertos de nuevo, y llevados ante un gobernante más sabio que nosotros hoy, que vea el valor del verdadero conocimiento.\n\nEsta es mi palabra.{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1780
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_b7d3c208:

    # "You think about what you have just read. This goes further than any other documents you have found about your place of home, about your heritage."
    "Reflexionas sobre lo que acabas de leer. Esto va más allá que cualquier otro documento que hayas encontrado sobre tu lugar de origen, sobre tu herencia."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1781
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_28ccfa17:

    # Z "These words... they carry weight."
    Z "Estas palabras... tienen peso."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1782
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_f6fef549:

    # Z "The Temple would call it heresy, I guess. But if enough people trusted its truthfulness, it could really cause some unrest."
    Z "El Templo lo llamaría herejía, supongo. Pero si un número suficiente de personas confiara en su veracidad, podría causar algunos disturbios."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1783
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_e83b9b14:

    # Z "It would be interesting to know if they ever found his private study..."
    Z "Sería interesante saber si alguna vez encontraron su estudio privado..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1786
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_606360ac:

    # S "Yeah, I figured. The question is, did the Queen know about this?"
    S "Sí, me lo imaginaba. La pregunta es, ¿lo sabía la Reina?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1789
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_252af9cc:

    # Z "Hard to say... she never mentioned it. Maybe she was truly just looking for the scout?"
    Z "Es difícil de decir... Ella nunca lo mencionó. ¿Quizá sólo buscaba al explorador?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1790
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_d2a933c0:

    # Z "Wait... when you listened to that thief, did he mention if he stole it from the palace, or found it someplace else?"
    Z "Espera... Cuando escuchaste a ese ladrón, ¿mencionó si lo robó del palacio o lo encontró en otro lugar?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1793
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_02c3523a:

    # S "He said that he found it, and that he can't go back to the palace with it."
    S "Dijo que lo había encontrado y que no podía volver al palacio con él."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1794
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_d27d7f87:

    # S "He really seemed to have enlisted just to get access to anything that could benefit his tribe. They were talking about bringing the documents to someone they called \"father\"."
    S "Realmente parecía haberse alistado sólo para tener acceso a cualquier cosa que pudiera beneficiar a su tribu. Hablaban de llevar los documentos a alguien a quien llamaban \"padre\"."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1797
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_39566ab5:

    # S "Maybe one of the tribe's leaders?"
    S "¿Quizá uno de los líderes de la tribu?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1800
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_d7c5e0d7:

    # Z "Could be. Or maybe just their father. I guess speaking to the girl on the throne is our only way to learn more."
    Z "Podría ser. O quizá sólo su padre. Supongo que hablar con la chica del trono es la única forma de saber más."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1803
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_971a98df:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1806
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_a6fdff43:

    # S "If what he's saying is true, that the palace has started burning its own history... do you think she will want to burn this paper, too?"
    S "Si lo que dice es cierto, que el palacio ha empezado a quemar su propia historia... ¿crees que ella también querrá quemar este papel?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1809
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_f9187092:

    # Z "Well, he is talking about events that go back centuries. Who knows how the court looks on these things today?"
    Z "Habla de acontecimientos que se remontan a siglos atrás. ¿Quién sabe cómo ve el tribunal estas cosas hoy en día?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1812
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_e86d8885:

    # S "I mean, it does make sense, doesn't it..."
    S "Tiene sentido, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1813
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_5536e8a3:

    # S "The only things we see in the city's library are documents of past events, but the old weapons, technologies and everything else are said to be kept hidden by the Palace."
    S "Lo único que vemos en la biblioteca de la ciudad son documentos de acontecimientos pasados, pero se dice que el Palacio mantiene ocultas las armas antiguas, las tecnologías y todo lo demás."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1816
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_495c7c54:

    # S "I've seen one of those weapons myself, when I was with her."
    S "Yo misma he visto una de esas armas, cuando estaba con ella."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1819
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_08056f58:

    # Z "You saw her use ancient technology?"
    Z "¿La viste utilizar tecnología antigua?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1822
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_b3cd5573:

    # S "Yeah... you've heard of her \"dragon\"?"
    S "Sí... ¿has oído hablar de su \"dragón\"?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1825
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_94ea952d:

    # Z "Oh... don't tell me..."
    Z "Oh... no me digas..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1828
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_1daf19dd:

    # S "Flaming hot, it was. Smelled of fuel too."
    S "Estaba ardiendo. También olía a combustible."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1831
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1834
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_7158ab01:

    # "You look at the notes again..."
    "Vuelves a mirar las notas..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1835
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_9acd1564:

    # Z "Whatever she's going to want to do with these notes, we should keep a copy here."
    Z "Sea lo que sea lo que ella quiera hacer con estas notas, debemos guardar una copia aquí."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1836
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_03acbbf9:

    # Z "Before our meeting with the Queen, please make sure you make a copy of everything and archive it here."
    Z "Antes de nuestra reunión con la Reina, asegúrate de hacer una copia de todo y archivarla aquí."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1837
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_e8b1f579:

    # Z "The original, of course, goes to the Queen."
    Z "El original, por supuesto, se dirige a la Reina."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1838
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_44481d73:

    # Z "I guess that compiling copies and registering events isn't as exciting a part of being a Stalker, but I have always believed that it adds to the preparation and helps absorb information."
    Z "Supongo que recopilar copias y registrar acontecimientos no es una parte tan emocionante de ser un Acechador, pero siempre he creído que contribuye a la preparación y ayuda a absorber la información."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1841
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_d68304eb:

    # S "I've had enough excitement for a little while, that's for sure. I don't mind the task"
    S "Ya he tenido suficientes emociones por un tiempo, eso seguro. No me importa la tarea"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1844
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_7efcd373:

    # Z "I don't doubt that."
    Z "No lo pongo en duda."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1845
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_900f0148:

    # Z "Hm..."
    Z "Hm..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1846
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_7c1a8fdd:

    # Z "I think I understand this Elder. I do see the value in knowing the truth of things, however dangerous."
    Z "Creo que entiendo a este Anciano. Veo el valor de conocer la verdad de las cosas, por peligrosa que sea."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1851
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_4f7890ba:

    # S "[persistent.dad!c]? Do you trust the Queen?"
    S "¿[persistent.dad!c]? ¿Confías en la Reina?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1854
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_fa586b16:

    # S "If you... we, really... if we keep working for her directly; do you trust her intentions? With us?"
    S "Si tú... nosotros, realmente... Si seguimos trabajando para ella directamente; ¿confías en sus intenciones? ¿Con nosotros?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1860
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_8e058553:

    # Z "She may still be a young Queen, but she seems passionate about leading this city."
    Z "Puede que aún sea una Reina joven, pero parece apasionada por dirigir esta ciudad."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1861
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_7d5d6509:

    # Z "And from the encounters I had with her personally, she seems to be honest about her intentions, and her reasons for calling on our services."
    Z "Y por los encuentros que tuve con ella personalmente, parece ser sincera sobre sus intenciones y sus razones para recurrir a nuestros servicios."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1864
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_b9e3cedc:

    # Z "So I tend to trust her."
    Z "Así que tiendo a confiar en ella."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1865
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_f3a433d1:

    # Z "What do you think? You've had your experience with her, too."
    Z "¿Qué te parece? Tú también has tenido tu experiencia con ella."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1869
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_8bbbc8a4:

    # S "Uff... well, she seems like a tough leader... and I think she has a thing for causing pain, physical pain..."
    S "Uff... bueno, parece una líder dura... y creo que le gusta causar dolor, dolor físico..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1870
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_820cb1fb:

    # S "But from what I have seen, she seems to care to do things the right way."
    S "Pero por lo que he visto, parece que se preocupa por hacer las cosas bien."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1873
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_cd8a6acf:

    # S "Maybe it's also that... she's trying to do what is expected of her? She didn't choose to be a Queen after all."
    S "Quizás también sea eso... ella está tratando de hacer lo que se espera de ella. Después de todo, no eligió ser una Reina."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1879
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_663e80a1:

    # S "Hmm... I don't know her too well. But... she is a Queen, above all."
    S "Hmm... No la conozco demasiado bien. Pero... es una Reina, por encima de todo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1880
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_17fa0ac2:

    # S "Working with her can only benefit us, maybe we will even gain more prominence?"
    S "Trabajar con ella sólo puede beneficiarnos, tal vez incluso ganemos más protagonismo?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1883
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_9fb0462e:

    # S "As long as we don't get too involved into the politics, we should be fine, right?"
    S "Mientras no nos involucremos demasiado en la política, todo irá bien, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1886
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_f055c5e7:

    # Z "I agree. Let's bring this document to her and see what she does with the information it holds."
    Z "Estoy de acuerdo. Llevémosle este documento y veamos qué hace con la información que contiene."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1892
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_97f4f5b0:

    # Z "I trust myself, first and foremost."
    Z "Ante todo, confío en mí mismo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1893
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_5e945f11:

    # Z "I do think she tries her best, but I also know that she is dealing in power struggles every day."
    Z "Creo que se esfuerza al máximo, pero también sé que cada día tiene que lidiar con luchas de poder."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1894
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_674d913f:

    # Z "And that means she has to look out for herself, first."
    Z "Y eso significa que ella tiene que cuidar de sí misma, primero."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1897
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_f3a433d1_1:

    # Z "What do you think? You've had your experience with her, too."
    Z "¿Qué te parece? Tú también has tenido tu experiencia con ella."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1901
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_8bbbc8a4_1:

    # S "Uff... well, she seems like a tough leader... and I think she has a thing for causing pain, physical pain..."
    S "Uff... bueno, parece una líder dura... y creo que le gusta causar dolor, dolor físico..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1902
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_820cb1fb_1:

    # S "But from what I have seen, she seems to care to do things the right way."
    S "Pero por lo que he visto, parece que se preocupa por hacer las cosas bien."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1905
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_cd8a6acf_1:

    # S "Maybe it's also that... she's trying to do what is expected of her? She didn't choose to be a Queen after all."
    S "Quizás también sea eso... ella está tratando de hacer lo que se espera de ella. Después de todo, no eligió ser una Reina."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1911
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_663e80a1_1:

    # S "Hmm... I don't know her too well. But... she is a Queen, above all."
    S "Hmm... No la conozco demasiado bien. Pero... es una Reina, por encima de todo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1912
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_17fa0ac2_1:

    # S "Working with her can only benefit us, maybe we will even gain more prominence?"
    S "Trabajar con ella sólo puede beneficiarnos, tal vez incluso ganemos más protagonismo?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1915
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_9fb0462e_1:

    # S "As long as we don't get too involved into the politics, we should be fine, right?"
    S "Mientras no nos involucremos demasiado en la política, todo irá bien, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1918
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_3790b6d2:

    # Z "I agree with that. Let's bring this document to her and see what she does with the information it holds."
    Z "Estoy de acuerdo. Llevémosle este documento y veamos qué hace con la información que contiene."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1924
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_3ffce912:

    # Z "I have done plenty of jobs for the palace since long before this Queen rose to power, and I benefitted greatly from it."
    Z "He hecho muchos trabajos para el palacio desde mucho antes de que esta reina ascendiera al poder, y me he beneficiado mucho de ello."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1925
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_cfd21b8b:

    # Z "But I never fully trust the palace, or its officials."
    Z "Pero nunca confío plenamente en el palacio ni en sus funcionarios."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1928
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_6d7f1381:

    # Z "Leaders should be acting in their population's interest, but... instead they tend to put their own interests first."
    Z "Los líderes deberían actuar en interés de su población, pero... en lugar de eso tienden a anteponer sus propios intereses."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1929
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_3fe96154:

    # Z "Seeing how she almost sent you to your death makes me trust her even less."
    Z "Ver cómo casi te envía a la muerte hace que confíe aún menos en ella."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1930
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_f3a433d1_2:

    # Z "What do you think? You've had your experience with her, too."
    Z "¿Qué te parece? Tú también has tenido tu experiencia con ella."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1934
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_8bbbc8a4_2:

    # S "Uff... well, she seems like a tough leader... and I think she has a thing for causing pain, physical pain..."
    S "Uff... bueno, parece una líder dura... y creo que le gusta causar dolor, dolor físico..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1935
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_820cb1fb_2:

    # S "But from what I have seen, she seems to care to do things the right way."
    S "Pero por lo que he visto, parece que se preocupa por hacer las cosas bien."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1938
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_cd8a6acf_2:

    # S "Maybe it's also that... she's trying to do what is expected of her? She didn't choose to be a Queen after all."
    S "Quizás también sea eso... ella está tratando de hacer lo que se espera de ella. Después de todo, no eligió ser una Reina."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1944
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_663e80a1_2:

    # S "Hmm... I don't know her too well. But... she is a Queen, above all."
    S "Hmm... No la conozco demasiado bien. Pero... es una Reina, por encima de todo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1945
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_17fa0ac2_2:

    # S "Working with her can only benefit us, maybe we will even gain more prominence?"
    S "Trabajar con ella sólo puede beneficiarnos, tal vez incluso ganemos más protagonismo?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1948
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_9fb0462e_2:

    # S "As long as we don't get too involved into the politics, we should be fine, right?"
    S "Mientras no nos involucremos demasiado en la política, todo irá bien, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1951
translate spanish d13e_discussion_menu_9616a61d:

    # Z "I guess. I will reserve my judgement for another day. Let's bring this document to her and see what she does with the information."
    Z "Supongo. Me reservaré mi juicio para otro día. Llevémosle este documento y veamos qué hace con la información."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1957
translate spanish d13e2_167b2a36:

    # Z "On its own, this paper won't change anything. Hardly anyone in the city, let alone the palace, would take it seriously over the recorded and oral traditions."
    Z "Por sí solo, este documento no cambiará nada. Casi nadie en la ciudad, y mucho menos en palacio, lo tomaría en serio por encima de las tradiciones grabadas y orales."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1958
translate spanish d13e2_31d0894a:

    # Z "Common knowledge tends to beat obscure texts, in the eye of the average person."
    Z "El conocimiento común tiende a vencer a los textos oscuros, a los ojos de la gente corriente."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1959
translate spanish d13e2_5e0b993c:

    # S "I see... but how do we approach her, then?"
    S "Ya veo... ¿pero cómo nos acercamos a ella?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1960
translate spanish d13e2_a4139cca:

    # S "How did you handle her in the past?"
    S "¿Cómo la trataste en el pasado?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1963
translate spanish d13e2_b6f54052:

    # Z "I have seen how she treats her subordinates. She demands respect, but she also can't stand them lying to her."
    Z "He visto cómo trata a sus subordinados. Exige respeto, pero tampoco soporta que le mientan."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1964
translate spanish d13e2_632155ee:

    # Z "Especially if it makes them look weak. She hates weakness."
    Z "Sobre todo si les hace parecer débiles. Odia la debilidad."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1966
translate spanish d13e2_145adfdf:

    # Z "So when I approach her, I treat her with the necessary respect, without being a pushover."
    Z "Así que cuando me acerco a ella, la trato con el respeto necesario, sin dejarme dominar."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1967
translate spanish d13e2_46453f60:

    # Z "I am convinced she respects me for holding my ground."
    Z "Estoy convencido de que me respeta por mantenerme firme."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1971
translate spanish d13e2_4a33162b:

    # Z "Not only that. I see the way she looks at me, sometimes. And I don't mind that in the slightest..."
    Z "Y no sólo eso. A veces veo cómo me mira. Y eso no me importa lo más mínimo..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1974
translate spanish d13e2_56c827dc:

    # S "{i}*giggles*{/i}"
    S "{i}*risitas*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1977
translate spanish d13e2_8f7a5116:

    # S "Like what? What happened between you two that made you say that?"
    S "¿Cómo qué? ¿Qué ha pasado entre vosotros para que digas eso?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1980
translate spanish d13e2_e285aecf:

    # Z "Let's just say our holy Queen doesn't mind watching, if you put up a little show. That's what happened in the Thermae, at least."
    Z "Digamos que a nuestra santa Reina no le importa mirar, si montas un pequeño espectáculo. Eso es lo que ocurrió en las Termas, al menos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1981
translate spanish d13e2_3bf34113:

    # Z "When I visited her later for another mission, she came up to me, much closer than her station or even an innocent conversation would warrant."
    Z "Cuando la visité más tarde para otra misión, se acercó a mí, mucho más de lo que su puesto o incluso una conversación inocente justificarían."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1984
translate spanish d13e2_5d961c2c:

    # S "What a cat..."
    S "Qué astuta..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1986
translate spanish d13e2_c21670b2:

    # S "I think she might have a thing for me as well... or maybe that was just the adrenaline of the moment..."
    S "Creo que ella también podría sentir algo por mí... o quizá sólo fuera la adrenalina del momento..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1989
translate spanish d13e2_e38e6cbf:

    # S "Inflicting pain definitely seems to cause some strong emotions in her, as well."
    S "Definitivamente, infligir dolor también parece provocar emociones fuertes en ella."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:1993
translate spanish d13e2_a79728e0:

    # S "But that kiss... I felt like there could've been more to it."
    S "Pero ese beso... Sentí que podría haber habido algo más."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2000
translate spanish d13e2_d52abf3c:

    # Z "I suppose it is not easy to deal with people when you're supposed to be above them, keep a distance, rule over them."
    Z "Supongo que no es fácil tratar con la gente cuando se supone que debes estar por encima de ellos, mantener una distancia, gobernarlos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2001
translate spanish d13e2_11ceed79:

    # Z "Who do you trust, in such a situation?"
    Z "¿En quién confías, en una situación así?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2004
translate spanish d13e2_5e299fe5:

    # S "That's true. She must be lonely."
    S "Eso es verdad. Debe de sentirse sola."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2007
translate spanish d13e2_03e13664:

    # Z "Be that as it may, she has shown to be capable of standing her ground and make her desires known."
    Z "Sea como fuere, ha demostrado ser capaz de mantenerse firme y dar a conocer sus deseos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2010
translate spanish d13e2_28ebfb18:

    # S "Now that sounds just like [A], don't you think?"
    S "Eso suena igual que [A], ¿no crees?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2013
translate spanish d13e2_cc98e841:

    # Z "That's a scary thought. Don't let your sister hear that."
    Z "Eso es una idea aterradora. No dejes que tu hermana escuche eso."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2016
translate spanish d13e2_65953b99:

    # S "{i}*giggles*{/i} Why? I think she'd make a fine Queen, no?"
    S "{i}*risitas*{/i} ¿Por qué? Creo que sería una buena Reina, ¿no?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2019
translate spanish d13e2_e91a53f4:

    # Z "[A] with the power to rule over Zeta? Downright scary, if you ask me."
    Z "¿[A] con el poder de gobernar Zeta? Realmente aterrador, si me lo preguntas."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2020
translate spanish d13e2_141ee192:

    # Z "No, Merneith is impulsive, maybe, but she is grown into her role."
    Z "No, Merneith es impulsiva, tal vez, pero ha crecido en su papel."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2023
translate spanish d13e2_23581d02:

    # Z "Trained for it and everything."
    Z "Entrenado específicamente para eso y preparado en todo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2027
translate spanish d13e2_8234817d:

    # Z "So when she gives me an audience, I make a point of showing that her station doesn't mean much to me."
    Z "Así que cuando me concede audiencia, le hago ver que su puesto no significa mucho para mí."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2028
translate spanish d13e2_0b63ff4c:

    # Z "I am not taking anything from her, and she recognises that."
    Z "No acepto nada de ella, y ella lo reconoce."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2030
translate spanish d13e2_1861bc07:

    # Z "There were some instances where I had to show her how I treat bratty girls."
    Z "Hubo algunos casos en los que tuve que enseñarle cómo trato a las niñas malcriadas."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2033
translate spanish d13e2_a8bc04a2:

    # S "Oh my... what happened between my [persistent.dad] and the young Queen?"
    S "Oh cielos... ¿qué ha pasado entre mi [persistent.dad] y la joven Reina?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2036
translate spanish d13e2_fa601453:

    # Z "Oh... there were a couple of situations."
    Z "Oh... hubo un par de situaciones."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2038
translate spanish d13e2_2f19ae81:

    # Z "One time, she roped me into acting as a tool for her, to inflict a punishment on a prisoner of hers, like I was a common guard for her to command."
    Z "Una vez, me engañó para que le sirviera de instrumento para infligir un castigo a un prisionero suyo, como si yo fuera un vulgar guardia a sus órdenes."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2039
translate spanish d13e2_8988fdc7:

    # Z "Her arrogance got the best of me, so I pushed her against the wall and manhandled her, feeling her up."
    Z "Su arrogancia pudo conmigo, así que la empujé contra la pared y la manoseé, palpándola."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2042
translate spanish d13e2_867f01b1:

    # S "{i}*giggles*{/i} There's no way you didn't go to prison for that."
    S "{i}*risitas*{/i} Es imposible que no fueras a la cárcel por eso."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2045
translate spanish d13e2_edd736b1:

    # Z "Well, it happened inside the prison, so in a way I was already there."
    Z "Bueno, ocurrió dentro de la prisión, así que en cierto modo ya estaba allí."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2046
translate spanish d13e2_fb424e9e:

    # Z "But no, nothing happened because of it. When the guards came in, she kept quiet about it. So she took it out on the prisoner instead."
    Z "Pero no, no pasó nada por ello. Cuando entraron los guardias, se quedó callada. Así que la tomé con el prisionero en su lugar."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2047
translate spanish d13e2_eb09cd3b:

    # Z "Merneith needs someone to look up to, and in a way, I think I can give her that."
    Z "Merneith necesita a alguien a quien admirar y, en cierto modo, creo que puedo dárselo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2050
translate spanish d13e2_79906a93:

    # S "Yeah... maybe... maybe she's just... very lonely."
    S "Sí... quizá... A lo mejor es que... se siente muy sola."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2052
translate spanish d13e2_6de36051:

    # S "I remember when she kissed me. I felt like there could've been more to it, had I allowed it to happen..."
    S "Recuerdo cuando me besó. Sentí que podría haber habido algo más, si hubiera permitido que ocurriera..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2058
translate spanish d13e2_d52abf3c_1:

    # Z "I suppose it is not easy to deal with people when you're supposed to be above them, keep a distance, rule over them."
    Z "Supongo que no es fácil tratar con la gente cuando se supone que debes estar por encima de ellos, mantener una distancia, gobernarlos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2059
translate spanish d13e2_11ceed79_1:

    # Z "Who do you trust, in such a situation?"
    Z "¿En quién confías, en una situación así?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2062
translate spanish d13e2_5e299fe5_1:

    # S "That's true. She must be lonely."
    S "Eso es verdad. Debe de sentirse sola."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2065
translate spanish d13e2_03e13664_1:

    # Z "Be that as it may, she has shown to be capable of standing her ground and make her desires known."
    Z "Sea como fuere, ha demostrado ser capaz de mantenerse firme y dar a conocer sus deseos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2068
translate spanish d13e2_28ebfb18_1:

    # S "Now that sounds just like [A], don't you think?"
    S "Eso suena igual que [A], ¿no crees?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2071
translate spanish d13e2_cc98e841_1:

    # Z "That's a scary thought. Don't let your sister hear that."
    Z "Eso es una idea aterradora. No dejes que tu hermana escuche eso."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2074
translate spanish d13e2_65953b99_1:

    # S "{i}*giggles*{/i} Why? I think she'd make a fine Queen, no?"
    S "{i}*risitas*{/i} ¿Por qué? Creo que sería una buena Reina, ¿no?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2077
translate spanish d13e2_e91a53f4_1:

    # Z "[A] with the power to rule over Zeta? Downright scary, if you ask me."
    Z "¿[A] con el poder de gobernar Zeta? Realmente aterrador, si me lo preguntas."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2078
translate spanish d13e2_141ee192_1:

    # Z "No, Merneith is impulsive, maybe, but she is grown into her role."
    Z "No, Merneith es impulsiva, tal vez, pero ha crecido en su papel."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2081
translate spanish d13e2_23581d02_1:

    # Z "Trained for it and everything."
    Z "Entrenado específicamente para eso y preparado en todo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2089
translate spanish d13e3_67b85e51:

    # S "Do you... think that we can convince her somehow to open up a little more?"
    S "¿Crees... que podemos convencerla de alguna manera para que se abra un poco más?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2092
translate spanish d13e3_d42dfa62:

    # Z "In what sense?"
    Z "¿En qué sentido?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2095
translate spanish d13e3_7a7ff55c:

    # S "You know... she seems to like us..."
    S "Sabes... parece que le gustamos..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2098
translate spanish d13e3_408afc57:

    # S "Imagine if we were closer with the Queen of Zeta... who can say that, right?"
    S "Imagina que estuviéramos más cerca de la Reina de Zeta... ¿quién puede decir eso, verdad?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2102
translate spanish d13e3_ad3ded17:

    # Z "Pretty opportunistic. Like father, like daughter I suppose..."
    Z "Bastante oportunista. De tal palo, tal astilla, supongo..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2103
translate spanish d13e3_a7cd6d4e:

    # Z "Any actual plans?"
    Z "¿Algún plan real?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2106
translate spanish d13e3_4222d929:

    # S "Not yet really. Let's see how things pan out."
    S "En realidad, todavía no. Vamos a ver cómo se desarrollan las cosas."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2113
translate spanish d13e3_15c76686:

    # Z "Let's talk about your glowing find."
    Z "Hablemos de tu hallazgo luminoso."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2116
translate spanish d13e3_0aeed785:

    # S "Alright!"
    S "¡De acuerdo!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2119
translate spanish d13e3_53693d9a:

    # S "So, what do you think about this thing?"
    S "¿Qué opinas de esto?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2120
translate spanish d13e3_d8baaec1:

    # S "Do you really think this is what your mentor meant for me to find?"
    S "¿Realmente crees que esto es lo que tu mentor quería que yo encontrara?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2121
translate spanish d13e3_39efa8e0:

    # S "It was inside that factory I told you about and I didn't see anything else standing out quite this much, but I have also not searched every room, so..."
    S "Estaba dentro de la fábrica de la que te hablé y no vi nada que destacara tanto, pero tampoco registré todas las habitaciones, así que..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2122
translate spanish d13e3_ba9c8674:

    # S "The notes that I found on the path leading to it, all seemed to indicate this being a special item, at least back then."
    S "Las notas que encontré en el camino que conducía a esto parecían indicar que se trataba de un objeto especial, al menos por aquel entonces."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2123
translate spanish d13e3_c129aae7:

    # Z "That's just it... we don't know what it was for, and if it could still be used to that end."
    Z "Eso es... no sabemos para qué servía, y si aún podría utilizarse con ese fin."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2124
translate spanish d13e3_e475868d:

    # Z "We don't know if there are more of them..."
    Z "No sabemos si hay más de estos...."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2125
translate spanish d13e3_5919810a:

    # S "Take a look at this, [persistent.dad]..."
    S "Echa un vistazo a esto, [persistent.dad]..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2128
translate spanish d13e3_f23f553e:

    # "She carefully takes out a note..."
    "Ella saca con cuidado una nota..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2131
translate spanish d13e3_ecd42ae3:

    # S "There were others, but this one was the most specific."
    S "Había otras, pero ésta era la más específica."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2132
translate spanish d13e3_5f278a26:

    # "You take a closer look..."
    "Echas un vistazo más de cerca..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2133
translate spanish d13e3_0e3ef835:

    # nvl clear
    # Nar "{i}Team 5 supervisor personal log: The EPB 11 was made under time constraints. I was made aware that the previous EPB was soon to be discarded.\nNo explanation was given as to why. Faulty fuselage? Defective sealants? Has it simply run its course? The latter seems unlikely.{/i}"
    nvl clear
    Nar "{i}Registro personal del supervisor del Equipo 5: El EPB 11 fue construido bajo fuertes limitaciones de tiempo. Fui informado de que el EPB anterior iba a ser descartado pronto.\nNo se dio ninguna explicación al respecto. ¿Fuselage defectuoso? ¿Selladores defectuosos? ¿Simplemente cumplió su ciclo? Esto último parece poco probable.{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2135
translate spanish d13e3_a055a3e6:

    # Nar "{i}\nI would have liked to have more information to understand the failings of the previous one, in order to avoid repeating them. As it is, we had to make EPB 11 in record time{/i}."
    Nar "{i}\nMe hubiera gustado tener más información para comprender los fallos de la anterior, a fin de evitar repetirlos. Así las cosas, tuvimos que hacer la EPB 11 en un tiempo récord{/i}."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2136
translate spanish d13e3_e98c5a72:

    # Nar "{i}We did the best we could, but I want it officially recorded that we cannot take responsibility for any issues that might arise. The need for secrecy and the slow vetting process of qualified personnel also does not help.{/i}"
    Nar "{i}Hicimos todo lo que pudimos, pero quiero que conste oficialmente que no podemos responsabilizarnos de los problemas que puedan surgir. La necesidad de mantener el secreto y la lentitud del proceso de selección del personal cualificado tampoco ayudan.{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2137
translate spanish d13e3_1f256052:

    # Nar "{i}As it is, I know it will work, it will fully integrate with the Station and run the devices it is supposed to, both the Gate and the Horus System.{/i}"
    Nar "{i}Así como está, sé que funcionará, se integrará plenamente con la Estación y hará funcionar los dispositivos que se supone que debe hacer funcionar, tanto la Puerta como el Sistema Horus.{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2138
translate spanish d13e3_b8195e15:

    # Nar "{i}I trust that with this, the Horus System will perform adequately and defend us from the long term consequences of the chemical fallout from the Scorched Earth Project... durability however remains a potential issue.{/i}"
    Nar "{i}Confío en que, con esto, el Sistema Horus funcionará adecuadamente y nos defenderá de las consecuencias a largo plazo de la lluvia radiactiva química del Proyecto Tierra Quemada.. La durabilidad, sin embargo, sigue siendo un problema potencial.{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2139
translate spanish d13e3_c942be0b:

    # Z "Horus system..."
    Z "Sistema Horus..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2142
translate spanish d13e3_b4e50eb7:

    # Z "This kind of language... I have encountered it before and always in contexts of things related to the military of the times."
    Z "Este tipo de lenguaje.. Me lo he encontrado antes y siempre en contextos de cosas relacionadas con el ejército de la época."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2143
translate spanish d13e3_e99dfd05:

    # Z "It seems this man was concerned for his reputation, but still not explicitly stating anything of use."
    Z "Parece que este hombre se preocupaba por su reputación, pero sin afirmar explícitamente nada de utilidad."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2144
translate spanish d13e3_759cedc8:

    # Z "That's what happens when you find text exchanges between people who already know the subject of their conversation. They don't spend time explaining it to each other."
    Z "Eso es lo que ocurre cuando encuentras intercambios de texto entre personas que ya conocen el tema de su conversación. No dedican tiempo a explicárselo el uno al otro."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2147
translate spanish d13e3_f78a0913:

    # S "I wish I knew more..."
    S "Ojalá supiera más..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2150
translate spanish d13e3_404991d1:

    # Z "We may yet find out."
    Z "Puede que aún lo descubramos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2153
translate spanish d13e3_62485cfa:

    # Z "Regardless. You did what he asked of you, and you did it well. I'm proud of you."
    Z "A pesar de todo. Hiciste lo que te pidió, y lo hiciste bien. Estoy orgulloso de ti."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2156
translate spanish d13e3_00e2f217:

    # "She puts the notes aside and places the battery back in front of you..."
    "Deja las notas a un lado y vuelve a colocar la batería delante de ti..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2159
translate spanish d13e3_6a01ea02:

    # S "Will you bring this to him?"
    S "¿Se lo vas a llevar?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2162
translate spanish d13e3_9dcac0b8:

    # Z "No. This thing will stay with us until I know why he wanted you to fetch it in the first place."
    Z "No. Esta cosa se quedará con nosotros hasta que sepa por qué quería que la trajeras en primer lugar."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2165
translate spanish d13e3_1f7af5a7:

    # Z "After all, he said that I could keep it, and that he only wanted to confirm his theories."
    Z "Después de todo, me dijo que podía quedármelo, y que sólo quería confirmar sus teorías."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2166
translate spanish d13e3_6f94b889:

    # S "Do you believe that? I mean, it makes no sense to have me look for something if he doesn't want it in the first place."
    S "¿Te lo puedes creer? No tiene sentido que me haga buscar algo si él no lo quiere en primer lugar."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2167
translate spanish d13e3_9b898e37:

    # Z "I think there's a good chance that he will change his mind once he knows the thing is actually within reach."
    Z "Creo que es muy probable que cambie de opinión cuando sepa que la cosa está realmente a su alcance."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2168
translate spanish d13e3_64714dfb:

    # Z "I will try to get him to explain its purpose before we come to the point where he asks me for it. He must know more."
    Z "Intentaré que me explique su propósito antes de llegar al punto en que me lo pida. Debe saber más."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2169
translate spanish d13e3_db21df68:

    # Z "Old Master Zosar always knew what he was doing and his plans had plans... and contingencies."
    Z "El Viejo Maestro Zosar siempre sabía lo que hacía y sus planes tenían planes... y contingencias."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2170
translate spanish d13e3_6dd91cbd:

    # Z "I don't know if this new... if Abrax has the same kind of sophisticated mind."
    Z "No sé si este nuevo... si Abrax tiene el mismo tipo de mente sofisticada."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2171
translate spanish d13e3_29918c3c:

    # Z "But I must assume that his physical changes haven't diminished his wits at all."
    Z "Debo suponer que sus cambios físicos no han mermado en absoluto su ingenio."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2172
translate spanish d13e3_b5e48939:

    # Z "Basically, he knows what he is doing."
    Z "Básicamente, sabe lo que hace."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2173
translate spanish d13e3_43ca57be:

    # S "Hm..."
    S "Hm..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2179
translate spanish d13e3_ea825323:

    # S "I remember when you told stories about your old master. You always spoke highly of him, and that he always meant you well."
    S "Recuerdo cuando contabas historias sobre tu antiguo maestro. Siempre hablabas bien de él, y que siempre te trató bien."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2182
translate spanish d13e3_a4411fa6:

    # S "Do you think he would deceive you? Do you trust him at all?"
    S "¿Crees que te engañaría? ¿Confías en él?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2189
translate spanish d13e3_405a1c8a:

    # Z "I did indeed speak highly of him. He was like the father I never had."
    Z "En efecto, hablé muy bien de él. Era como el padre que nunca tuve."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2190
translate spanish d13e3_b737869c:

    # Z "Master Zosar was a patriot, he stood for the city."
    Z "El maestro Zosar era un patriota, defendía la ciudad."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2191
translate spanish d13e3_f8875680:

    # Z "He did his part for years, being a Stalker for the old Queen, and then later, teaching younglings like me to follow in his footsteps."
    Z "Cumplió su parte durante años, como Acechador de la antigua Reina, y más tarde, enseñando a jóvenes como yo a seguir sus pasos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2194
translate spanish d13e3_1ba7c198:

    # Z "Why he would side with the decayed... cannibals... I don't know."
    Z "Por qué se pondría del lado de los Decaídos... caníbales... no lo sé."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2195
translate spanish d13e3_feee1d04:

    # Z "But when I spoke with him, deep in the belly of Old Cairo..."
    Z "Pero cuando hablé con él, en las profundidades del Viejo Cairo..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2196
translate spanish d13e3_12af17c2:

    # Z "He seemed driven, possessed by a calculating anger..."
    Z "Parecía impulsado, poseído por una ira calculadora..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2197
translate spanish d13e3_2b0155f6:

    # Z "What do you think?"
    Z "¿Qué te parece?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2201
translate spanish d13e3_39bb0851:

    # S "Hm... I don't know him at all. But I know who the decayed are..."
    S "Hm... No le conozco de nada. Pero sé quiénes son los Decaídos..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2204
translate spanish d13e3_db5a0a03:

    # S "I see no reason to work with cannibals, [persistent.dad]."
    S "No veo ninguna razón para trabajar con caníbales, [persistent.dad]."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2207
translate spanish d13e3_a7cd2b0b:

    # S "Buying fuel from them is one thing, a necessary evil maybe. But trusting them? No, I wouldn't."
    S "Comprarles combustible es una cosa, tal vez un mal necesario. Pero confiar en ellos, no lo haría."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2211
translate spanish d13e3_5086373e:

    # S "Hm... I don't know him, but as long as he doesn't hurt us, he could bring useful information."
    S "Hm... No le conozco, pero mientras no nos haga daño, podría aportar información útil."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2212
translate spanish d13e3_f2a2862a:

    # S "I would say we see what he wants from us first."
    S "Yo diría que veamos qué es lo que él quiere de nosotros primero."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2215
translate spanish d13e3_001a6380:

    # Z "I want to trust him. But I can't, yet. I will not risk your life again, going in blindly. He may just kill us and take this thing, after all."
    Z "Quiero confiar en él. Pero aún no puedo. No volveré a arriesgar tu vida, entrando a ciegas. Después de todo, puede que nos mate y se lleve esta cosa."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2218
translate spanish d13e3_0755c284:

    # S "So I am not coming with you?"
    S "¿Así que no voy contigo?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2221
translate spanish d13e3_43195a86:

    # Z "No. Not this time, [S]."
    Z "No. Esta vez no, [S]."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2224
translate spanish d13e3_d3de4cc3:

    # Z "I am not inclined to take his word at face value like I used to when he was still... well, himself."
    Z "Ya no confío plenamente en lo que dice como solía hacer cuando aún era... bueno, su verdadero yo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2227
translate spanish d13e3_13da58c3:

    # S "I see. I will wait here, then. Be careful."
    S "Entiendo. Esperaré aquí entonces. Ten cuidado."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2235
translate spanish d13e3_ce665c38:

    # Z "Master Zosar was a patriot, he stood up for the city."
    Z "El maestro Zosar era un patriota, defendía la ciudad."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2236
translate spanish d13e3_f8875680_1:

    # Z "He did his part for years, being a Stalker for the old Queen, and then later, teaching younglings like me to follow in his footsteps."
    Z "Cumplió su parte durante años, como Acechador de la antigua Reina, y más tarde, enseñando a jóvenes como yo a seguir sus pasos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2237
translate spanish d13e3_dddf87fd:

    # Z "I would have trusted him as my old mentor. But now..."
    Z "Habría confiado en él como en mi antiguo mentor. Pero ahora..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2240
translate spanish d13e3_1ba7c198_1:

    # Z "Why he would side with the decayed... cannibals... I don't know."
    Z "Por qué se pondría del lado de los Decaídos... caníbales... no lo sé."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2241
translate spanish d13e3_2b0155f6_1:

    # Z "What do you think?"
    Z "¿Qué te parece?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2245
translate spanish d13e3_39bb0851_1:

    # S "Hm... I don't know him at all. But I know who the decayed are..."
    S "Hm... No le conozco de nada. Pero sé quiénes son los Decaídos..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2248
translate spanish d13e3_db5a0a03_1:

    # S "I see no reason to work with cannibals, [persistent.dad]."
    S "No veo ninguna razón para trabajar con caníbales, [persistent.dad]."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2251
translate spanish d13e3_a7cd2b0b_1:

    # S "Buying fuel from them is one thing, a necessary evil maybe. But trusting them? No, I wouldn't."
    S "Comprarles combustible es una cosa, tal vez un mal necesario. Pero confiar en ellos, ¿yo? No lo haría."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2255
translate spanish d13e3_5086373e_1:

    # S "Hm... I don't know him, but as long as he doesn't hurt us, he could bring useful information."
    S "Hm... No le conozco, pero mientras no nos haga daño, podría aportar información útil."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2256
translate spanish d13e3_f2a2862a_1:

    # S "I would say we see what he wants from us first."
    S "Yo diría que veamos qué es lo que él quiere de nosotros primero."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2259
translate spanish d13e3_28cfb87c:

    # Z "I see. Also, talking about leverage..."
    Z "Entiendo. Además, hablando de ventaja o influencia..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2260
translate spanish d13e3_f8978f0a:

    # Z "We've got what he wanted. Let's see if he can convince me to give it to him. If he wants it at all."
    Z "Ya tenemos lo que quería. A ver si me convence para que se lo dé. Si es que lo quiere."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2263
translate spanish d13e3_d3cc8615:

    # S "So you don't want me to come with you?"
    S "¿Así que no quieres que vaya contigo?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2266
translate spanish d13e3_43195a86_1:

    # Z "No. Not this time, [S]."
    Z "No. Esta vez no, [S]."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2269
translate spanish d13e3_d3de4cc3_1:

    # Z "I am not inclined to take his word at face value like I used to when he was still... well, himself."
    Z "Ya no confío plenamente en lo que dice como solía hacer cuando aún era... bueno, su verdadero yo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2272
translate spanish d13e3_13da58c3_1:

    # S "I see. I will wait here, then. Be careful."
    S "Entiendo. Esperaré aquí entonces. Ten cuidado."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2280
translate spanish d13e3_59858232:

    # Z "I don't, no..."
    Z "No lo hago, no..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2281
translate spanish d13e3_b737869c_1:

    # Z "Master Zosar was a patriot, he stood for the city."
    Z "El maestro Zosar era un patriota, defendía la ciudad."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2282
translate spanish d13e3_ce4f71a9:

    # Z "He did his part for years, as a Stalker for the old Queen, and then later, teaching younglings like me to follow in his footsteps."
    Z "Hizo su parte durante años, como Acechador de la antigua Reina, y más tarde, enseñando a jóvenes como yo a seguir sus pasos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2285
translate spanish d13e3_17752619:

    # Z "But now... this. The decayed, of all groups."
    Z "Pero ahora... esto. El decaído, de todos los grupos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2286
translate spanish d13e3_3836b6b3:

    # Z "I fear that my old master has lost his way. But I have also learned to not judge a character before you hear him out."
    Z "Temo que mi antiguo maestro haya perdido el rumbo. Pero también he aprendido a no juzgar a un personaje antes de escucharlo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2287
translate spanish d13e3_ab46a1d4:

    # Z "And this is why am still willing to hear him out."
    Z "Y por eso sigo dispuesto a escucharle."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2288
translate spanish d13e3_2b0155f6_2:

    # Z "What do you think?"
    Z "¿Qué te parece?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2292
translate spanish d13e3_39bb0851_2:

    # S "Hm... I don't know him at all. But I know who the decayed are..."
    S "Hm... No le conozco de nada. Pero sé quiénes son los Decaídos..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2295
translate spanish d13e3_90667d0f:

    # S "I see no reason why to work with cannibals, [persistent.dad]."
    S "No veo ninguna razón para trabajar con caníbales, [persistent.dad]."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2298
translate spanish d13e3_a7cd2b0b_2:

    # S "Buying fuel from them is one thing, a necessary evil maybe. But trusting them? No, I wouldn't."
    S "Comprarles combustible es una cosa, tal vez un mal necesario. Pero confiar en ellos, ¿yo? No lo haría."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2302
translate spanish d13e3_5086373e_2:

    # S "Hm... I don't know him, but as long as he doesn't hurt us, he could bring useful information."
    S "Hm... No le conozco, pero mientras no nos haga daño, podría aportar información útil."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2303
translate spanish d13e3_f2a2862a_2:

    # S "I would say we see what he wants from us first."
    S "Yo diría que veamos qué es lo que él quiere de nosotros primero."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2306
translate spanish d13e3_0d811bd0:

    # Z "I see. Either way, I will not risk your life in this. There's no point to it."
    Z "Ya veo. En cualquier caso, no arriesgaré tu vida en esto. No tiene sentido."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2309
translate spanish d13e3_0755c284_1:

    # S "So I am not coming with you?"
    S "¿Así que no voy contigo?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2312
translate spanish d13e3_43195a86_2:

    # Z "No. Not this time, [S]."
    Z "No. Esta vez no, [S]."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2315
translate spanish d13e3_d3de4cc3_2:

    # Z "I am not inclined to take his word at face value like I used to when he was still... well, himself."
    Z "Ya no confío plenamente en lo que dice como solía hacer cuando aún era... bueno, su verdadero yo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2318
translate spanish d13e3_13da58c3_2:

    # S "I see. I will wait here, then. Be careful."
    S "Entiendo. Esperaré aquí entonces. Ten cuidado."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2324
translate spanish d13e_end_15434178:

    # Z "Alright, great. That should do it for now."
    Z "Perfecto, genial. Eso será suficiente por ahora."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2325
translate spanish d13e_end_f7511458:

    # Z "I will see what I can do."
    Z "Veré lo que puedo hacer."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2328
translate spanish d13e_end_ad92d16c:

    # S "Got it. Let's head downstairs?"
    S "Entendido. ¿Vamos abajo?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2340
translate spanish d13f_7d55f6be:

    # "Meanwhile, as the day comes to an end, [S] decides to get some rest..."
    "Mientras tanto, a medida que el día llega a su fin, [S] decide descansar un poco..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2343
translate spanish d13f_9ae64167:

    # St "\"The tribes of al Minya cultivated the dried underground caves just like Zeta did, despite the red mist obscuring the sky more often than not.\""
    St "\"Las tribus de al Minya cultivaban las cuevas subterráneas secas igual que Zeta, a pesar de que la niebla roja oscurecía el cielo la mayoría de las veces.\""

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2344
translate spanish d13f_e77f486d:

    # St "\"A complicated system of pulleys and balancing kegs aided with the irrigation of...\""
    St "\"Un complicado sistema de poleas y barriles de equilibrio ayudado con el riego de...\""

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2345
translate spanish d13f_d71125ad:

    # St "Hmm..."
    St "Hmm..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2348
translate spanish d13f_c2704ee9:

    # St "I wonder if the legends are true... I wonder if the path towards the city will ever be safe?"
    St "Me pregunto si las leyendas son ciertas... Me pregunto si el camino hacia la ciudad será seguro alguna vez."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2351
translate spanish d13f_a4eca11a:

    # S "{i}*yawn*{/i}"
    S "{i}*bostezo*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2354
translate spanish d13f_9924b194:

    # S "I think that's enough for today."
    S "Creo que es suficiente por hoy."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2357
translate spanish d13f_d2fc2e08:

    # St "Time to sleep..."
    St "Hora de dormir..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2363
translate spanish d13f_971a98df:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2365
translate spanish d13f_1b9e770c:

    # St "I wonder what that bandit girl is up to now... did she make it out of there...?"
    St "Me pregunto qué estará haciendo ahora esa bandida... ¿habrá conseguido salir de allí?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2366
translate spanish d13f_2dfd8b05:

    # St "Probably not... she was still bleeding when I left her... the wound..."
    St "Probablemente no... seguía sangrando cuando la dejé... la herida..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2368
translate spanish d13f_f03e1d81:

    # St "I really wonder what happened to that boy's mother..."
    St "Realmente me pregunto qué le habrá pasado a la madre de ese chico..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2369
translate spanish d13f_65475e1b:

    # St "...Or where she is even... from..."
    St "... o incluso de dónde es..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2372
translate spanish d13f_971a98df_1:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2373
translate spanish d13f_dbafa452:

    # C "[S]???"
    C "[S]..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2376
translate spanish d13f_4db0d0fd:

    # C "[S], where are you?!"
    C "[S], ¡¿dónde estás?!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2379
translate spanish d13f_c28d46d5:

    # St "What is..."
    St "¿Es que..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2380
translate spanish d13f_58dd19ce:

    # A "Please come see, I haven't seen this before!!"
    A "Por favor, ven a verlo, ¡¡¡no lo había visto antes!!!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2381
translate spanish d13f_495c9b5b:

    # S "[A]?"
    S "¿[A]?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2382
translate spanish d13f_febccfed:

    # A "[S], you need to see this!"
    A "[S], ¡tienes que ver esto!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2385
translate spanish d13f_abb123c2:

    # S "{i}*sigh*{/i}"
    S "{i}*suspiro*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2386
translate spanish d13f_150b6b77:

    # S "It's so late... what does she..."
    S "Es tan tarde... ¿qué hace ella..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2387
translate spanish d13f_e5ac971f:

    # A "[S], I think this is dangerous!"
    A "[S], ¡creo que esto es peligroso!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2391
translate spanish d13f_fc1cd12f:

    # S "Dangerous?"
    S "¿Peligroso?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2394
translate spanish d13f_76e0428b:

    # S "I'm coming, don't do anything!"
    S "Ya voy, ¡no hagas nada!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2395
translate spanish d13f_4f885647:

    # "[S] hurriedly gets up and rushes outside..."
    "[S] se levanta a toda prisa y sale corriendo..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2400
translate spanish d13f_495c9b5b_1:

    # S "[A]?"
    S "¿[A]?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2401
translate spanish d13f_cf7b63f6:

    # A "I'm here, come, fast!"
    A "Estoy aquí, ven, ¡rápido!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2404
translate spanish d13f_d62428f4:

    # A "[S]..."
    A "[S]..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2407
translate spanish d13f_3cd9af68:

    # S "Yes... I heard you."
    S "Sí... Te he oído."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2408
translate spanish d13f_adfd939f:

    # S "What is going on?"
    S "¿Qué está pasando?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2411
translate spanish d13f_37d0288c:

    # "Looking around the corner, [A] is just standing there."
    "Al mirar a la vuelta de la esquina, [A] está ahí de pie."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2412
translate spanish d13f_8995a313:

    # "The urgency in her tone is denied by her relaxed posture."
    "La urgencia de su tono queda desmentida por su postura relajada."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2413
translate spanish d13f_cdb82d69:

    # "Is this meant to be a prank?"
    "¿Se trata de una broma?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2416
translate spanish d13f_93778af8:

    # S "What is it, [A]? I was concerned. Why are you out here anyways?"
    S "¿Qué ocurre, [A]? Estaba preocupada. ¿Por qué estás aquí?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2417
translate spanish d13f_0cea8f25:

    # S "[persistent.mom!c] and [persistent.dad] are probably asleep already. Why aren't you?"
    S "[persistent.mom!c] y [persistent.dad] probablemente ya estén dormidos. ¿Por qué tú no?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2420
translate spanish d13f_f7bded7b:

    # A "[S]... I think we should be careful, it's dangerous."
    A "[S]... Creo que deberíamos tener cuidado, es peligroso."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2423
translate spanish d13f_e77a8ee5:

    # S "What is dangerous, [A]? Are you okay?"
    S "¿Qué es peligroso, [A]? ¿Estás bien?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2424
translate spanish d13f_33de7e0e:

    # S "Will you tell me what's going on, already?"
    S "¿Me dirás de una vez qué está pasando?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2427
translate spanish d13f_fe4e1d2a:

    # A "I told you, I just got here. [S], do you see these people out there?"
    A "Te lo he dicho, acabo de llegar. [S], ¿ves a esa gente de ahí fuera?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2430
translate spanish d13f_d62428f4_1:

    # A "[S]..."
    A "[S]..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2431
translate spanish d13f_0d159f92:

    # A "I think they want to hurt-{w=0.8}{nw}"
    A "Creo que quieren hacernos da-{w=0.8}{nw}"

