translate spanish d13f_8918e7b7:

    # S "What..."
    S "¿Qué..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2491
translate spanish d13f_eb35d789:

    # S "But it felt so..."
    S "Pero me ha parecido tan..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2494
translate spanish d13f_40475518:

    # A "[S]...?!"
    A "¡¿[S]...?!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2495
translate spanish d13f_971a98df_2:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2499
translate spanish d13f_23219497:

    # A "Sis... are you... okay?"
    A "Hermanita... ¿estás... bien?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2500
translate spanish d13f_64050c9c:

    # A "I heard you shouting... it was scary."
    A "Te oí gritar... daba miedo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2503
translate spanish d13f_56451c30:

    # A "You... had a nightmare..."
    A "Tú... has tenido una pesadilla..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2504
translate spanish d13f_293e19f3:

    # A "[S]... it's okay."
    A "[S]... está bien."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2507
translate spanish d13f_971a98df_3:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2508
translate spanish d13f_a415de86:

    # S "I... guess..."
    S "Yo... supongo..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2511
translate spanish d13f_f3c5a1d1:

    # A "I'm here..."
    A "Estoy aquí..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2514
translate spanish d13f_ec811841:

    # A "So... um... was it about your adventure?"
    A "Entonces... um... ¿se trataba de tu aventura?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2515
translate spanish d13f_1267eb05:

    # S "...Yeah."
    S "... Sí."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2516
translate spanish d13f_cc78c508:

    # S "I mean... sort of."
    S "Quiero decir... más o menos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2517
translate spanish d13f_11cf3a24:

    # S "I don't really want to talk about it..."
    S "No quiero hablar de ello..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2520
translate spanish d13f_17f3b4d6:

    # A "About your adventure, or the dream?"
    A "¿Sobre tu aventura, o sobre el sueño?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2521
translate spanish d13f_bcd975fb:

    # S "Both really..."
    S "Ambas realmente..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2524
translate spanish d13f_567e2ef1:

    # A "I never ask [persistent.dad] anything either, you know? Sometimes he will tell me, but mostly he... he stays quiet."
    A "Yo tampoco le pregunto nunca nada a [persistent.dad], ¿sabes? A veces me lo cuenta, pero la mayoría de las veces... se queda callado."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2527
translate spanish d13f_a7fff95d:

    # "[A] settles in a comfortable silence."
    "[A] se instala en un cómodo silencio."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2530
translate spanish d13f_b81d74ba:

    # S "It's ok really, I'm just happy you're fine."
    S "No pasa nada, de verdad, me alegro de que estés bien."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2533
translate spanish d13f_aa8bcf5a:

    # A "{i}I'm{/i} fine? Why, what could happen to me?"
    A "{i}¿Estoy{/i} bien? ¿Por qué? ¿Qué podría pasarme?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2534
translate spanish d13f_3ae38ced:

    # A "Was it the dream?"
    A "¿Fue por el sueño?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2537
translate spanish d13f_30afb66d:

    # S "Well, yeah... in the dream you got hurt..."
    S "Bueno, sí... en el sueño te hacían daño..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2538
translate spanish d13f_30bcbe22:

    # A "That's... scary. But I am really ok, you see?"
    A "Eso... da miedo. Pero realmente estoy bien, ¿lo ves?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2541
translate spanish d13f_26ae68aa:

    # S "I know, I know... you were right. It was just a dream."
    S "Lo sé, lo sé... tenías razón. Sólo era un sueño."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2544
translate spanish d13f_4891c01d:

    # "As [S] shifts from a placating smile to a more pensive state of mind, [A] picks up on it and sits for a few seconds, looking for words to comfort her elder sister."
    "Cuando [S] pasa de una sonrisa apaciguadora a un estado de ánimo más pensativo, [A] lo capta y se sienta durante unos segundos, buscando palabras para consolar a su hermana mayor."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2547
translate spanish d13f_d8654138_1:

    # A "..."
    A "..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2548
translate spanish d13f_41c51200:

    # "[A] looks concerned, not sure how to console her sister..."
    "[A] parece preocupada, no sabe cómo consolar a su hermana..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2551
translate spanish d13f_ee640b3f:

    # A "I guess you really did see a lot of bad things in that place..."
    A "Supongo que realmente viste muchas cosas malas en ese lugar..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2552
translate spanish d13f_d10108b0:

    # S "Just... that's the strange thing actually. Things were different, but the bad things... the violence... those came from outside the Zone."
    S "En realidad... eso es lo extraño. Las cosas eran diferentes, pero lo malo... la violencia... Esas vinieron de fuera de la Zona."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2553
translate spanish d13f_96f2fa22:

    # S "I could have met those walking a little ways away from our home."
    S "Podría haberme encontrado con esos caminantes a poca distancia de nuestra casa."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:2556
