    # "You sense she is being rather more formal than when you last spoke, which is possibly because of the presence of her personal guard, Sharifa."
    "Percibes que está más formal que la última vez que hablasteis, posiblemente debido a la presencia de su guardia personal, Sharifa."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3482
translate spanish d13i_0fa0a7f2:

    # "Her tone is neither cocky, nor pretentious, but serious, and sincere."
    "Su tono no es arrogante ni pretencioso, sino serio y sincero."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3485
translate spanish d13i_2dcaf675:

    # "Despite that, you remind yourself of the dangerous task she has given to your [persistent.da], and you feel the urge to respond."
    "A pesar de ello, te acuerdas de la peligrosa tarea que ha encomendado a tu [persistent.da], y sientes el impulso de responder."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3488
translate spanish d13i_944395b9:

    # Z "The mission you gave my [persistent.da] was almost a fatal one."
    Z "La misión que le diste a mi [persistent.da] fue casi fatal."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3489
translate spanish d13i_6756b7a1:

    # Z "It turned out that that scout of yours was actually spying on you to try and put his hands on anything that he could use to his benefit."
    Z "Resultó que ese explorador tuyo en realidad te estaba espiando para intentar poner sus manos sobre cualquier cosa que pudiera utilizar en su beneficio."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3492
translate spanish d13i_4fbed853:

    # Z "And he wasn't operating alone."
    Z "Y no estaba operando solo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3495
translate spanish d13i_ddf72b55:

    # Z "[S] had to fight against multiple bandits."
    Z "[S] tuvo que luchar contra múltiples bandidos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3498
translate spanish d13i_09e57a4b:

    # "The Queen stays silent for a moment, evaluating this information."
    "La Reina permanece en silencio un momento, evaluando esa información."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3501
translate spanish d13i_a029ffb1:

    # Q "I am sorry to hear that. I was led to believe that you would be rescuing a loyal servant, not confronting a dangerous traitor."
    Q "Lamento oír eso. Me hicieron creer que rescatarías a un leal servidor, no que te enfrentarías a un peligroso traidor."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3504
translate spanish d13i_e7a60857:

    # Q "[S], I am happy that you managed to survive the ordeal and rid me of a potential danger at the same time."
    Q "[S], me alegro de que hayas conseguido sobrevivir a la prueba y librarme al mismo tiempo de un peligro potencial."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3505
translate spanish d13i_8059d8ab:

    # Q "I will... let my people know they should be more careful about who they let join their numbers."
    Q "Haré... saber a mi gente que deben tener más cuidado con quién dejan que se una a sus filas."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3510
translate spanish d13i_8d4f0ebd:

    # Z "You almost sent my [persistent.da] to her death."
    Z "Casi mandas a mi [persistent.da] a la muerte."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3512
translate spanish d13i_e3e34772:

    # Z "You almost sent [S] to her death."
    Z "Casi mandas a [S] a la muerte."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3513
translate spanish d13i_57386886:

    # Z "put her on sent her straight towards a group of bandits."
    Z "La misión que le diste la llevó directamente hacia un grupo de bandidos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3514
translate spanish d13i_1b036360:

    # Z "The man she was supposed to rescue? He turned out to be a traitor who, together with his companions, was almost the end of [S]."
    Z "¿El hombre al que se suponía que iba a rescatar? Resultó ser un traidor que, junto con sus compañeros, fue casi el fin de [S]."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3515
translate spanish d13i_1440421d:

    # Z "Tell me you didn't know about it..."
    Z "Dime que no lo sabías..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3518
translate spanish d13i_9b494f45:

    # Sh "[persistent.player_name], watch your tone!"
    Sh "[persistent.player_name], ¡cuidado con el tono!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3521
translate spanish d13i_230cabac:

    # Z "The life of my [persistent.da] is more important to me than formalities, Sharifa."
    Z "La vida de mi [persistent.da] es más importante para mí que las formalidades, Sharifa."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3524
translate spanish d13i_4e1a47de:

    # Q "Leave it, Sharifa... I understand his anger."
    Q "Déjalo, Sharifa... Comprendo su ira."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3527
translate spanish d13i_e672c476:

    # Q "Even so, [persistent.player_name] you should not throw around accusations. You were willing to send [S] into the Zone well before I asked you to give her an additional task."
    Q "Aun así, [persistent.player_name] no deberías lanzar acusaciones. Estabas dispuesto a enviar a [S] a la Zona mucho antes de que te pidiera que le dieras una tarea adicional."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3528
translate spanish d13i_f4741f81:

    # Q "I asked a Stalker to do me a service. Do you think she wasn't ready? Have I overestimated you both?"
    Q "Le pedí a un Acechador que me hiciera un servicio. ¿Crees que no estaba preparada? ¿Os he sobrevalorado a los dos?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3531
translate spanish d13i_c69f98b1:

    # Q "Don't get me wrong, [S], I don't send people into danger on purpose, but this had to be done."
    Q "No me malinterpretes, [S], yo no envío a la gente al peligro a propósito, pero esto había que hacerlo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3532
translate spanish d13i_d6003426:

    # Q "That said, no, I did not know that my scout was a wolf in sheep's clothing."
    Q "Dicho esto, no, no sabía que mi explorador era un lobo con piel de cordero."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3533
translate spanish d13i_36b5ecba:

    # Q "However, I am happy that you managed to survive the ordeal and rid me of a potential danger at the same time."
    Q "Sin embargo, me alegro de que hayas conseguido sobrevivir a la prueba y librarme al mismo tiempo de un peligro potencial."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3534
translate spanish d13i_aa867498:

    # Q "I will let my people know they should've known better."
    Q "Haré saber a mi gente que deberían haberlo sabido mejor."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3540
translate spanish d13i10_3c156a99:

    # Q "[persistent.player_name], I'm sure there were other complications during [S]'s mission as well as your settlement ordeal."
    Q "[persistent.player_name], seguro que hubo otras complicaciones durante la misión de [S], además de tu calvario en el asentamiento."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3541
translate spanish d13i10_84c975e5:

    # Q "I think it would be best if we talk about it one issue at a time."
    Q "Creo que lo mejor sería que habláramos de una cuestión cada vez."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3545
translate spanish d13i10_33195f3f:

    # Q "So... which one would you like to discuss first?"
    Q "Entonces... ¿de qué quieres hablar primero?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3558
translate spanish d13i_discussions_84251a6b:

    # Z "Regarding the Overpass settlement, I have news."
    Z "En cuanto al asentamiento del Paso Elevado, tengo noticias."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3559
translate spanish d13i_discussions_090df21f:

    # Z "The settlement's former leader, some buffoon who called himself the \"General\", was refusing to align himself any further with Zetan interests."
    Z "El antiguo líder del asentamiento, un bufón que se hacía llamar el \"General\", se negaba a alinearse más con los intereses zetanos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3560
translate spanish d13i_discussions_4d175b0e:

    # Z "Despite my attempts at negotiation, he was unwilling to trade with, or get help from, your soldiers."
    Z "A pesar de mis intentos de negociación, se negaba a comerciar con tus soldados o a recibir ayuda de ellos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3564
translate spanish d13i_discussions_4ca6a824:

    # Z "He kicked me out almost immediately, sending his regards."
    Z "Me echó casi inmediatamente, enviándome sus saludos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3565
translate spanish d13i_discussions_9d10e26e:

    # Z "I don't like to say this... but words won't make a difference to that guy."
    Z "No me gusta decir esto... pero las palabras no harán ninguna diferencia para ese tipo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3568
translate spanish d13i_discussions_bdc61a01:

    # Q "..."
    Q "..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3569
translate spanish d13i_discussions_2166a1f3:

    # Z "He's as thick as can be. His settlement is barely protected..."
    Z "Es de lo más grueso. Su asentamiento apenas está protegido..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3572
translate spanish d13i_discussions_0f4aae3d:

    # Z "I say it's a matter of time before it will be overrun."
    Z "Yo digo que es cuestión de tiempo que sea invadido."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3575
translate spanish d13i_discussions_391a937d:

    # Q "Then he shall get what's coming for him."
    Q "Entonces recibirá su merecido."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3576
translate spanish d13i_discussions_fa91a8e1:

    # Q "We will wait and see what happens for now. I will send a scout in the near future to see if the settlement is still standing."
    Q "De momento, esperaremos a ver qué ocurre. Enviaré un explorador en un futuro próximo para ver si el asentamiento sigue en pie."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3580
translate spanish d13i_discussions_03cabea2:

    # Q "[Sh], let the council know that I am considering to take that settlement should it still stand by next week."
    Q "[Sh], informa al consejo de que estoy considerando tomar ese asentamiento si sigue en pie la semana que viene."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3581
translate spanish d13i_discussions_bd745186:

    # Q "I want an evaluation about the expected losses."
    Q "Quiero una evaluación sobre las pérdidas previstas."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3584
translate spanish d13i_discussions_8e5b1659:

    # Sh "Yes, my Queen. I will report back to you about this."
    Sh "Sí, mi Reina. Te informaré al respecto."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3591
translate spanish d13i_discussions_e2eed665:

    # Z "On top of that, I intercepted a group of Raiders about to attack the settlement."
    Z "Además, intercepté a un grupo de Asaltantes a punto de atacar el asentamiento."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3594
translate spanish d13i_discussions_63763403:

    # Q "So you are saying that the Overpass has been overrun by Raiders? Why has this news not reached me until now?"
    Q "¿Estás diciendo que el Paso Elevado ha sido invadido por los Asaltantes? ¿Por qué no me ha llegado esta noticia hasta ahora?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3597
translate spanish d13i_discussions_88311778:

    # Z "Well, you see... the reason may be because I have struck a deal with them."
    Z "Bueno, verás... la razón puede ser que he hecho un trato con ellos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3600
translate spanish d13i_discussions_6dff14df:

    # Q "A Deal?!"
    Q "¡¿Un trato?!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3607
translate spanish d13i_discussions_ac1a068a:

    # Z "Let me explain... No, there's too much. Let me sum up."
    Z "Déjame explicarte... No, son demasiadas cosas. Déjame resumirte."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3608
translate spanish d13i_discussions_37c76a4a:

    # Z "As you know, raiders are divided into factions, war bands, call them what you like. This particular group, I actually know well enough."
    Z "Como sabes, los asaltantes se dividen en facciones, bandas de guerra, llámalas como quieras. A este grupo en concreto lo conozco bastante bien."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3609
translate spanish d13i_discussions_f4c60e43:

    # Z "On my suggestion, instead of burning it to the ground, they stuck around and they are now in command of the Overpass."
    Z "Por sugerencia mía, en lugar de quemarlo hasta los cimientos, se quedaron y ahora están al mando del Paso Elevado."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3611
translate spanish d13i_discussions_bdbe198c:

    # Sh "Are you seriously telling me that you helped the Raiders gain a significant foothold within a short distance of Zeta and subjugate Zetan citizens?"
    Sh "¿En serio me estás diciendo que ayudaste a los Asaltantes a conseguir un punto de apoyo significativo a poca distancia de Zeta y a subyugar a los ciudadanos zetanos?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3612
translate spanish d13i_discussions_0f5ba803:

    # Z "A settlement that is not going to be raided into oblivion, and a faction of Raiders who are, for once, not hell bent on fighting us."
    Z "Un asentamiento que no va a ser asaltado hasta el olvido, y una facción de Asaltantes que, por una vez, no están empeñados en luchar contra nosotros."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3613
translate spanish d13i_discussions_15afe497:

    # Z "And those were never really Zetans to begin with."
    Z "Y, para empezar, esos nunca fueron realmente zetanos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3614
translate spanish d13i_discussions_6c00909c:

    # Q "And now, those wasteland savages are running the settlement?"
    Q "Y ahora, ¿esos salvajes del páramo dirigen el asentamiento?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3615
translate spanish d13i_discussions_5e15a983:

    # Z "They are, and I have the trust of their leaders. They will listen to me."
    Z "Lo hacen, y tengo la confianza de sus líderes. Me escucharán."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3622
translate spanish d13i_discussions_ad1b8db9:

    # Z "You could've sent your army and taken the place, but you told me that you like an ally better than an occupation, especially this deep in the desert."
    Z "Podrías haber enviado a tu ejército y tomar el lugar, pero me dijiste que te gusta más un aliado que una ocupación, sobre todo tan profundo en el desierto."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3623
translate spanish d13i_discussions_28974e3e:

    # Z "I think they will mostly let the place be, use it for shelter and occasionally take a chunk of the profits and goods for themselves, but they'll leave it standing."
    Z "Creo que en su mayor parte dejarán el lugar en paz, lo utilizarán como refugio y ocasionalmente se llevarán una parte de los beneficios y los bienes, pero lo dejarán en pie."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3624
translate spanish d13i_discussions_f06baee3:

    # Q "How is that supposed to help us exactly?"
    Q "¿Cómo se supone que eso nos va a ayudar exactamente?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3625
translate spanish d13i_discussions_e95bb390:

    # Z "Well, they will leave the caravans alone if they can get some of the goods almost without effort, by letting them use the Overpass as a safe haven along the road."
    Z "Bueno, dejarán en paz a las caravanas si pueden conseguir parte de la mercancía casi sin esfuerzo, dejándoles utilizar el Paso Elevado como refugio seguro a lo largo de la carretera."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3627
translate spanish d13i_discussions_f3ef0653:

    # Q "But... they're wastelanders. How do I know they're not attacking my troops on sight?"
    Q "Pero... son baldíos. ¿Cómo sé que no atacarán a mis tropas nada más verlas?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3629
translate spanish d13i_discussions_2c543645:

    # Sh "How are our troops supposed to find shelter in the Overpass if the Raiders are there?"
    Sh "¿Cómo se supone que nuestras tropas van a encontrar refugio en el Paso Elevado si los Asaltantes están allí?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3630
translate spanish d13i_discussions_d66f3371:

    # Z "I've made a deal with them. We keep up the trade with them, in return they let our troops rest and pass through on expeditions."
    Z "He hecho un trato con ellos. Nosotros mantenemos el comercio con ellos, a cambio ellos dejan que nuestras tropas descansen y pasen en expediciones."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3631
translate spanish d13i_discussions_7b9439bc:

    # Z "Troops that won't actually need to go that way, on account of the raiders doing their work for us."
    Z "Tropas que en realidad no necesitarán ir por ahí, ya que los asaltantes harán su trabajo por nosotros."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3632
translate spanish d13i_discussions_6d9cfa84:

    # Z "You have your ally, your extended arm in the desert, as well as a connection to one of the gangs fighting for power in and around Adira."
    Z "Tienes a tu aliado, tu brazo extendido en el desierto, así como una conexión con una de las bandas que luchan por el poder en Adira y sus alrededores."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3635
translate spanish d13i_discussions_31acdad0:

    # Z "The enemy of your enemies is now your friend, my Queen. To a point, at least."
    Z "El enemigo de tus enemigos es ahora tu amigo, mi Reina. Hasta cierto punto, al menos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3638
translate spanish d13i_discussions_8ce9501c:

    # Q "What makes you think that the Raiders won't just destroy everything and will keep their word?"
    Q "¿Qué te hace pensar que los Asaltantes no lo destruirán todo y cumplirán su palabra?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3641
translate spanish d13i_discussions_9954c1df:

    # S "He knows the leader of this gang personally. I have seen her myself briefly. Isn't that right?"
    S "Él conoce personalmente a la líder de esta banda. Yo misma la he visto brevemente. ¿No es cierto?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3644
translate spanish d13i_discussions_8338f5bd:

    # "You wink at [S], remembering how she confronted you when you were about to escort Kyra back to Adira..."
    "Le guiñas un ojo a [S], recordando cómo se enfrentó a ti cuando ibas a escoltar a Kyra de vuelta a Adira..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3645
translate spanish d13i_discussions_982a6a04:

    # Z "Leaders, actually. But yes, she is right. They will listen to me for now. A loose friend is better than no friend."
    Z "Las líderes, en realidad. Pero sí, ella tiene razón. Me escucharán por ahora. Un amigo suelto es mejor que ningún amigo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3652
translate spanish d13i_discussions_6bbcdaa4:

    # Z "The General would not have complied either way. Your option would have been to take over the settlement or leave it."
    Z "El General no habría accedido de ninguna de las maneras. Su opción habría sido hacerse cargo del asentamiento o abandonarlo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3653
translate spanish d13i_discussions_aa9390cd:

    # Q "I did in fact not aim to take that place over... it's of no relevance on its own."
    Q "De hecho, no pretendía apoderarme de ese lugar... no tiene relevancia por sí mismo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3654
translate spanish d13i_discussions_f2a4d177:

    # Q "But with this raider gang controlling it... we could play around some more."
    Q "Pero con esta banda de asaltantes controlándolo... podríamos jugar un poco más."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3655
translate spanish d13i_discussions_f0f1fd2f:

    # Q "Say... [persistent.player_name], how do you plan to influence them in the future?"
    Q "Di... [persistent.player_name], ¿cómo piensas influir en ellos en el futuro?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3656
translate spanish d13i_discussions_2cb1fd81:

    # Q "Raiders can be decent mercenaries for our city, but you could also try to assimilate them over time."
    Q "Los asaltantes pueden ser mercenarios decentes para nuestra ciudad, pero también podrías intentar asimilarlos con el tiempo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3657
translate spanish d13i_discussions_3a8d4399:

    # Q "Zeta has made some attempts over the centuries to assimilate some of the savage tribes."
    Q "Zeta ha hecho algunos intentos a lo largo de los siglos para asimilar a algunas de las tribus salvajes."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3658
translate spanish d13i_discussions_af290365:

    # Z "I will have to see what opportunities arise. I don't know enough of their clan yet to go into specifics, but I will come back to you."
    Z "Tendré que ver qué oportunidades surgen. Aún no sé lo suficiente de su clan como para entrar en detalles, pero volveré a hablar contigo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3661
translate spanish d13i_discussions_2503d269:

    # Q "That's an interesting notion. You took things in your own hands and adapted when circumstances made my task irrelevant. I don't dislike that."
    Q "Es una idea interesante. Tomaste las cosas en tus manos y te adaptaste cuando las circunstancias hicieron que mi tarea fuera irrelevante. Eso no me disgusta."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3664
translate spanish d13i_discussions_65740d84:

    # Q "We have fought against the gangs of Adira for so long... the idea of initiating diplomatic efforts with them is..."
    Q "Llevamos tanto tiempo luchando contra las bandas de Adira... que la idea de iniciar gestiones diplomáticas con ellos es..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3667
translate spanish d13i_discussions_4568a06a:

    # Q "...very intriguing."
    Q "... muy intrigante."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3671
translate spanish d13i_discussions_bed8c849:

    # Q "We will observe what happens. I will send a few men I trust to keep an eye on events from a distance. For now, I am satisfied."
    Q "Observaremos qué pasa. Enviaré a unos pocos hombres de confianza para que vigilen los eventos desde lejos. Por ahora, estoy satisfecha."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3675
translate spanish d13i_discussions_228f1636:

    # Q "We will observe what happens. Sharifa, send a few men you trust to keep an eye on events from a distance. For now, I am satisfied."
    Q "Observaremos lo que ocurre. Sharifa, envía a algunos hombres de tu confianza para que vigilen los acontecimientos a distancia. Por ahora, estoy satisfecha."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3678
translate spanish d13i_discussions_c3d92301:

    # Sh "Understood, my Queen."
    Sh "Entendido, mi Reina."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3685
translate spanish d13i_discussions_44bbd129:

    # Z "Let us discuss more about the Scout's findings. Also, I have something that you need to lay your eyes on."
    Z "Discutamos más sobre los hallazgos del Explorador. Además, tengo algo sobre lo que debes poner tus ojos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3688
translate spanish d13i_discussions_537cedb3:

    # "As you let [S] explain the details of how she came upon the traitorous scout, you lay out the old parchment she found in front of the Queen who scans the content for a few seconds."
    "Mientras dejas que [S] te explique los detalles de cómo dio con el explorador traidor, extiendes el viejo pergamino que encontró delante de la Reina, que escruta el contenido durante unos segundos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3691
translate spanish d13i_discussions_46ca1d74:

    # Q "Mh..."
    Q "Mh..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3694
translate spanish d13i_discussions_09208ab9:

    # "When she picks up on some of the content, her focus shifts entirely towards the text."
    "Cuando capta parte del contenido, su atención se desplaza por completo hacia el texto."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3695
translate spanish d13i_discussions_1259d62d:

    # Q "This..."
    Q "Esto..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3698
translate spanish d13i_discussions_e1498a91:

    # "She is absorbed for a moment, then seems to make a decision."
    "Se queda absorta un momento, luego parece tomar una decisión."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3701
translate spanish d13i_discussions_521fcf9e:

    # Q "Sharifa, I would like to confer with the High Priestess before the day is over."
    Q "Sharifa, me gustaría hablar con la Gran Sacerdotisa antes de que acabe el día."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3704
translate spanish d13i_discussions_4ec2e041:

    # Sh "I will send someone to summon her."
    Sh "Enviaré a alguien para que la convoque."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3707
translate spanish d13i_discussions_fe137d68:

    # Q "No, Sharifa. This... is the High Priestess, I will not shame her by sending an errand boy."
    Q "No, Sharifa. Esta... es la Gran Sacerdotisa, no la avergonzaré enviándole a un recadero."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3708
translate spanish d13i_discussions_9e084c50:

    # Q "I am going to need you to go yourself, to invite her to join me at her earliest convenience."
    Q "Voy a necesitar que vayas tú, que la invites a venir conmigo cuando le venga bien."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3711
translate spanish d13i_discussions_e29ab1db:

    # Sh "Understood, my Queen. I will make sure that she understands the urgency."
    Sh "Entendido, mi Reina. Me aseguraré de que comprenda la urgencia."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3714
translate spanish d13i_discussions_66ee7377:

    # Q "Thank you but... be gentle with her."
    Q "Gracias, pero... sé amable con ella."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3717
translate spanish d13i_discussions_145e6fc3:

    # "[Sh] looks at you..."
    "[Sh] te mira..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3720
translate spanish d13i_discussions_9eb4cee4:

    # Sh "I will call a few guards to attend to you and go immediately."
    Sh "Llamaré a unos guardias para que os atiendan y me marcharé inmediatamente."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3723
translate spanish d13i_discussions_9ea9a2ef:

    # Q "That will not be necessary. I am sure I am perfectly safe with these two Stalkers."
    Q "Eso no será necesario. Estoy segura de que estoy perfectamente a salvo con estos dos Acechadores."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3726
translate spanish d13i_discussions_74946e74:

    # Sh "My Queen, your station demands an honour guard, in my absence."
    Sh "Mi Reina, tu puesto exige una guardia de honor, en mi ausencia."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3729
translate spanish d13i_discussions_c2724fb8:

    # Q "Captain, you have your orders."
    Q "Capitana, ya tienes tus órdenes."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3732
translate spanish d13i_discussions_a9c5e69f:

    # Sh "I apologise, my Queen."
    Sh "Te pido disculpas, mi Reina."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3735
translate spanish d13i_discussions_5da396af:

    # "Somewhat frustrated, Sharifa bows her head in obedience and leaves the three of you alone in the room."
    "Algo frustrada, Sharifa inclina la cabeza en señal de obediencia y os deja a los tres solos en la habitación."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3736
translate spanish d13i_discussions_f152a93a:

    # "A moment of silence passes, as the Queen waits to hear the doors slam shut behind the exiting captain."
    "Transcurre un momento de silencio, mientras la Reina espera oír cómo se cierran las puertas tras la salida de su Capitana."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3739
translate spanish d13i_discussions_10c854d8:

    # Q "Have you read this through?"
    Q "¿Habéis leído todo esto por completo?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3740
translate spanish d13i_discussions_f155036a:

    # "The Queen's tone is sharp and pointed, as she addresses both you and [S]."
    "El tono de la Reina es agudo y punzante, mientras se dirige tanto a ti como a [S]."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3741
translate spanish d13i_discussions_c98cbe25:

    # S "We have."
    S "Lo hemos hecho."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3742
translate spanish d13i_discussions_ae0ff28b:

    # "You confirm with a silent nod."
    "Confirmas con un gesto silencioso de la cabeza."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3743
translate spanish d13i_discussions_b4e84278:

    # Q "Whether this is true or not is... It doesn't actually matter."
    Q "Que esto sea cierto o no... En realidad, no importa."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3744
translate spanish d13i_discussions_54c8d56a:

    # Q "I am under no illusion that the entire populace of my kingdom thinks of me as of a divine being."
    Q "No me hago ilusiones de que toda la población de mi reino piense en mí como en un ser divino."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3747
translate spanish d13i_discussions_9afc12bf:

    # "Looking at you pointedly, she keeps talking."
    "Te mira fijamente y sigue hablando."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3750
translate spanish d13i_discussions_ba0cb129:

    # Q "I know {i}you{/i} don't."
    Q "Sé que {i}tú{/i} no."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3753
translate spanish d13i_discussions_2073448a:

    # Q "And I also know, that those who resist this notion, have been... tamed... for centuries."
    Q "Y también sé, que aquellos que se resisten a esta noción, han sido... domesticados... durante siglos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3754
translate spanish d13i_discussions_e31d3f6e:

    # Q "Documents like these are harmless on their own. Anyone could write this and claim for it to be historical evidence."
    Q "Documentos como estos son inofensivos por sí solos. Cualquiera podría escribir esto y pretender que sea una prueba histórica."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3755
translate spanish d13i_discussions_b26b9152:

    # Q "What is more... concerning, is that there appear to be more hidden records belonging to said Elder somewhere out there."
    Q "Lo que es más... preocupante, es que parece haber más registros ocultos pertenecientes a dicho Anciano en algún lugar ahí fuera."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3756
translate spanish d13i_discussions_381595e1:

    # Q "Underneath a ruin maybe, somewhere inside the walls of this city... who knows."
    Q "Debajo de una ruina quizá, en algún lugar dentro de las murallas de esta ciudad... quién sabe."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3757
translate spanish d13i_discussions_57432a93:

    # S "Are you worried that people will question your authority?"
    S "¿Te preocupa que la gente cuestione tu autoridad?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3758
translate spanish d13i_discussions_656bafa3:

    # Q "This is not about me. I am worried that people will start doubting the fundamental structures of the society they live in, should more evidence of this Elder's words come out."
    Q "No se trata de mí. Me preocupa que la gente empiece a dudar de las estructuras fundamentales de la sociedad en la que vive, si salen a la luz más pruebas de las palabras de este Anciano."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3759
translate spanish d13i_discussions_b861e8fc:

    # Z "Are you going to destroy this parchment?"
    Z "¿Vas a destruir este pergamino?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3760
translate spanish d13i_discussions_2812c293:

    # Q "No... at least not yet. I will have to research this document first; and its author."
    Q "No... al menos todavía no. Primero tendré que investigar este documento y a su autor."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3761
translate spanish d13i_discussions_070200bb:

    # Q "I will personally look into this matter."
    Q "Me ocuparé personalmente de este asunto."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3764
translate spanish d13i_discussions_a1fbc88a:

    # "She keeps looking at the parchment. You had anticipated that she would react like this; she was quick to grasp the political and cultural implications of such inflammatory words."
    "Sigue mirando el pergamino. Habías previsto que reaccionaría así; ha captado rápidamente las implicaciones políticas y culturales de unas palabras tan incendiarias."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3765
translate spanish d13i_discussions_d541927d:

    # Q "This could all turn out to be the ramblings of an embittered old man, but I will have to check."
    Q "Todo esto podrían ser las divagaciones de un viejo amargado, pero tendré que comprobarlo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3766
translate spanish d13i_discussions_43c94e37:

    # "She remains pensive for another handful of seconds, before she concludes..."
    "Permanece pensativa durante otro puñado de segundos, antes de concluir..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3769
translate spanish d13i_discussions_96c6eeef:

    # Q "You have done well, [S]...and... regarding this piece, let me think about it for now."
    Q "Lo has hecho bien, [S]... y... respecto a este asunto, déjame pensarlo por ahora."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3770
translate spanish d13i_discussions_a4925536:

    # Q "I trust you both can keep the secret. This is important."
    Q "Confío en que ambos podáis guardar el secreto. Esto es importante."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3773
translate spanish d13i_discussions_af6c20df:

    # S "Discretion is one of the traits of our profession."
    S "La discreción es uno de los rasgos de nuestra profesión."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3776
translate spanish d13i_discussions_bdc61a01_1:

    # Q "..."
    Q "..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3782
translate spanish d13i24_317663c3:

    # Q "Okay... Now that both matters have been discussed, and [Sh] is gone... I want to say this."
    Q "Vale... Ahora que ambos asuntos se han discutido, y [Sh] se ha ido... Quiero decir lo siguiente."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3783
translate spanish d13i24_f0a97e3e:

    # Q "The palace expects a certain etiquette from me, and from you when you are within these walls. I can not be as open with you two as I'd like to."
    Q "El palacio espera cierta etiqueta de mí y de vosotros cuando os encontréis entre estos muros. No puedo ser tan abierta con vosotros como me gustaría."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3786
translate spanish d13i24_3769f2e5:

    # Q "I have gotten to know you a little bit more, [S], as well as you, [persistent.player_name]."
    Q "He llegado a conocerte un poco más, [S], así como a ti, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3790
translate spanish d13i24_00dd3472:

    # "She looks at you..."
    "Te mira..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3793
translate spanish d13i24_43c21f7e:

    # Q "I remember the agreement we made last time, [persistent.player_name], and..."
    Q "Recuerdo el acuerdo que hicimos la última vez, [persistent.player_name], y..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3796
translate spanish d13i24_e01741f1:

    # Q "I want to dispense with the formalities and court rules from now on."
    Q "A partir de ahora quiero prescindir de las formalidades y de las normas judiciales."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3799
translate spanish d13i24_853981ad:

    # Q "You have been... a strong ally, so far."
    Q "Has sido... un aliado fuerte, hasta ahora."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3802
translate spanish d13i24_04c64fcb:

    # "You notice her carefully weighing her words, her gaze focused on you..."
    "Notas que sopesa cuidadosamente sus palabras, con la mirada fija en ti..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3805
translate spanish d13i24_20d5e858:

    # Q "Anyways..."
    Q "De todos modos..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3811
translate spanish d13i24_2f7f5e9f:

    # "She pauses..."
    "Ella hace una pausa..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3814
translate spanish d13i24_765b8140:

    # Q "Even if... we had a few disagreements."
    Q "Aunque... hayamos tenido algunos desacuerdos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3817
translate spanish d13i24_35386184:

    # "She blushes. Those past instances left an impression on her."
    "Se sonroja. Aquellos momentos pasados la dejaron huella."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3820
translate spanish d13i24_01851af7:

    # Q "What I am saying is..."
    Q "Lo que estoy diciendo es que..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3826
translate spanish d13i24x_1b8cd151:

    # Q "There are going to be a few things I will need your services for, in the near future."
    Q "... habrá algunas cosas para las que necesitaré tus servicios, en un futuro próximo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3827
translate spanish d13i24x_99b99260:

    # Q "So... visit the palace at any time, [persistent.player_name]."
    Q "Así que... visita el palacio cuando quieras, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3832
translate spanish d13i24x_eebfa43d:

    # Q "The same goes for you, [S]... in fact, I'd like to invite you both to spend some time in the thermae."
    Q "Lo mismo digo, [S]... de hecho, me gustaría invitaros a los dos a pasar un rato en las termas."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3834
translate spanish d13i24x_1c82e73b:

    # Q "You both know how relaxing it can be, and it's a fairly private place to talk."
    Q "Ambos sabéis lo relajante que puede ser, y es un lugar bastante privado para hablar."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3835
translate spanish d13i24x_fcf73504:

    # Q "I may have some new information regarding the Elder's parchment by then that we can discuss."
    Q "Puede que para entonces tenga nueva información sobre el pergamino del Anciano que podamos discutir."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3837
translate spanish d13i24x_a79968d3:

    # Q "You already know how relaxing it can be, [S], and it's a fairly private place to talk."
    Q "Ya sabes lo relajante que puede ser, [S], y es un lugar bastante privado para hablar."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3838
translate spanish d13i24x_d1b54f9e:

    # Q "I may have some new information regarding the Elder's parchment by then that we can discuss.."
    Q "Puede que para entonces tenga nueva información sobre el pergamino del Anciano que podamos discutir..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3839
translate spanish d13i24x_26fbe156:

    # Q "What do you think of it?"
    Q "¿Qué te parece?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3844
translate spanish d13i24x_49a7a725:

    # S "I would be honoured."
    S "Me sentiría honrada."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3847
translate spanish d13i24x_8dca206d:

    # Z "We will visit you again, then."
    Z "Entonces, volveremos a visitarte."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3848
translate spanish d13i24x_f2412963:

    # Q "Great! I mean... ahem... {i}that is acceptable{/i}."
    Q "¡Genial!. Quiero decir... ejem... {i}eso es aceptable{/i}."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3854
translate spanish d13i24x_d059f56c:

    # Q "Guards! This meeting is concluded. Escort out these people and call for my private secretary."
    Q "¡Guardias! Esta reunión ha concluido. Escoltad fuera a estas personas y llamad a mi secretario privado."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3858
translate spanish d13i24x_2b4da159:

    # "The Queen picks up the parchment and hides it away."
    "La Reina coge el pergamino y lo esconde."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3859
translate spanish d13i24x_a370f5f1:

    # "Quickly flanked by guards and servants who scuttle around you, you are led out of the palace."
    "Rápidamente flanqueado por guardias y sirvientes que corretean a vuestro alrededor, sois conducidos fuera del palacio."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3868
translate spanish d13j_78b60001:

    # "Entering the remains of the once very populated building was easy, but navigating around inside was harder than assumed."
    "Entrar en los restos del edificio, antaño muy poblado, fue fácil, pero moverse por el interior fue más difícil de lo que se suponía."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3869
translate spanish d13j_0fc6483e:

    # "The mysterious knocking had its source on a high floor. Luckily, the stairs were still sufficiently intact..."
    "El misterioso golpe tenía su origen en un piso alto. Por suerte, las escaleras aún estaban suficientemente intactas..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3873
translate spanish d13j_971a98df:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3874
translate spanish d13j_a6f6023c:

    # "Darkness floods the floors..."
    "La oscuridad inunda los suelos..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3879
translate spanish d13j_0f82c41f:

    # "...but the knocking is closer, now."
    "... pero los golpes están más cerca, ahora."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3883
translate spanish d13j_9bff2a37:

    # St "Lights..."
    St "Luces..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3884
translate spanish d13j_9dabfa9b:

    # St "I don't like this. Reminds me of the burning torches in the pyramid."
    St "Esto no me gusta. Me recuerda a las antorchas encendidas de la pirámide."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3889
translate spanish d13j_aaa7257b:

    # St "The knocking... it stopped?"
    St "El golpeteo... ¿se ha detenido?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3892
translate spanish d13j_f39d2e37:

    # "While the knocking has stopped, the lights keep flickering. Good, otherwise this floor would be pitch dark."
    "Aunque los golpes han cesado, las luces siguen parpadeando. Bien, de lo contrario este piso estaría a oscuras."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3893
translate spanish d13j_f66c602c:

    # St "The door isn't as covered in rubble as the others. Maybe it's still open...?"
    St "La puerta no está tan cubierta de escombros como las otras. ¿Quizá siga abierta?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3899
translate spanish d13j7_9968e066:

    # St "...do I really want to go in there?"
    St "... ¿de verdad quiero entrar ahí?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3900
translate spanish d13j7_5d428a19:

    # St "Maybe it's best to just turn around..."
    St "Tal vez lo mejor sea darse la vuelta..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3903
translate spanish d13j7_e30ee7b9:

    # St "Screw it. I am curious."
    St "Que le den. Tengo curiosidad."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3907
translate spanish d13j7_26f0d73d:

    # St "I have a bad feeling about this."
    St "Tengo un mal presentimiento."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3908
translate spanish d13j7_c1ecd9a9:

    # St "I should go back to the bunker and finish what I came here for in the first place."
    St "Debería volver al búnker y terminar lo que vine a hacer en primer lugar."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3912
translate spanish d13j7_a09b24dd:

    # "On the way back to the bunker, the drumming against the door resumes..."
    "De vuelta al búnker, se reanuda el tamborileo contra la puerta..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3929
translate spanish d13j_kitchen_b8293a6e:

    # St "He's dead..."
    St "Está muerto..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3930
translate spanish d13j_kitchen_8e15871c:

    # St "Breathe, girl... don't let this place..."
    St "Respira, chica... no dejes que este lugar..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3940
translate spanish d13j_kitchen_f55c8076:

    # St "A parchment...? How..."
    St "¿Un pergamino...? Cómo..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3951
translate spanish d13j_kitchen_fa0a3271:

    # St "Everything looks burned..."
    St "Todo parece quemado..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3959
translate spanish d13j_kitchen_ed4efdd4:

    # "{i}\"We stocked up the pantry, but time is passing and our resources are dwindling. Running water is unusable, and we're down to canned beans and little else.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Abastecimos la despensa, pero el tiempo pasa y nuestros recursos disminuyen. El agua corriente es inutilizable, y sólo nos quedan judías enlatadas y poco más.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3960
translate spanish d13j_kitchen_c4c3d130:

    # "{i}\"I pray that you come back soon, my dear. The children are crying in their sleep, calling for you.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Te ruego que vuelvas pronto, querido. Los niños lloran dormidos, llamándote.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3961
translate spanish d13j_kitchen_a0d39e90:

    # "{i}\"Yesterday I have had to shoot at our downstairs neighbour. He tried to get in. I don't even know what he wanted.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Ayer tuve que disparar a nuestro vecino de abajo. Intentó entrar. Ni siquiera sé lo que quería.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3962
translate spanish d13j_kitchen_40617e22:

    # "{i}\"I managed to scavenge some more food from his place.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Me las arreglé para buscar algo más de comida en su casa.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3963
translate spanish d13j_kitchen_693ca808:

    # "{i}\"I will do whatever it takes for our children, but please... come home.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Haré lo que haga falta por nuestros hijos, pero por favor... vuelve a casa.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3964
translate spanish d13j_kitchen_3b03722c:

    # St "Who... wrote this?"
    St "¿Quién... escribió esto?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3994
translate spanish d13j_s8_radio_971a98df:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:3995
translate spanish d13j_s8_radio_b12128df:

    # St "It turned off on its own?"
    St "¿Se apagó sola?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4007
translate spanish d13j_kitchen_radio_26cb956c:

    # "{i}\"What is there left? How can I face myself and look in the mirror every day, after what I have done?\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"¿Qué nos queda? ¿Cómo puedo enfrentarme a mí misma y mirarme en el espejo cada día, después de lo que he hecho?\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4008
translate spanish d13j_kitchen_radio_7aa9a290:

    # "{i}\"No mother should ever be suffered to live after doing the unspeakable. No human being.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"A ninguna madre debería permitírsele vivir después de hacer lo indecible. Ningún ser humano.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4009
translate spanish d13j_kitchen_radio_a7496ea4:

    # "{i}\"This war however... it has made us all beasts.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Sin embargo, esta guerra nos ha convertido a todos en bestias.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4010
translate spanish d13j_kitchen_radio_624cfb9b:

    # "{i}\"Still, I can tell myself that I did it for the right reasons, that I spared them further suffering, but the thought of what I did sickens me.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Aún así, puedo decirme a mí misma que lo hice por las razones correctas, que les evité más sufrimiento, pero la idea de lo que hice me enferma.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4011
translate spanish d13j_kitchen_radio_13d80159:

    # "{i}\"God damn me... the pain and the starvation are tearing at me. I've even considered for a second to feed... I can't even write it.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Joder... el dolor y la inanición me están desgarrando. Incluso he considerado por un segundo alimentarme... Ni siquiera puedo escribirlo\".{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4012
translate spanish d13j_kitchen_radio_f0fb85b2:

    # "{i}\"No, this must end. I must pay for what I have done, no matter the reason.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"No, esto debe terminar. Debo pagar por lo que he hecho, no importa el motivo.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4013
translate spanish d13j_kitchen_radio_ea2aa655:

    # "{i}\"I am sorry, my love. When you read this, if you read this... if you survived, I hope you can forgive me.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Lo siento, amor mío. Cuando leas esto, si lees esto... si has sobrevivido, espero que puedas perdonarme\".{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4014
translate spanish d13j_kitchen_radio_971a98df:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4019
translate spanish d13j_kitchen_radio_a8c61387:

    # "{i}\"I must have gone crazy. What have I done?\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Debo de haberme vuelto loca. ¿Qué he hecho?\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4020
translate spanish d13j_kitchen_radio_fd77db5b:

    # "{i}\"I tried leaving, I swear. We left the building and roamed around for more than a day, sleeping under a bridge, in the fumes and the wreckage.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Intenté marcharme, lo juro. Abandonamos el edificio y estuvimos vagando durante más de un día, durmiendo bajo un puente, entre los humos y los restos.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4021
translate spanish d13j_kitchen_radio_1ac466c2:

    # "{i}\"We scavenged for food. The closest thing to food we saw, was a rat scurrying away, out of our reach.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Buscamos comida. Lo más parecido a comida que vimos, fue una rata escabulléndose, fuera de nuestro alcance.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4022
translate spanish d13j_kitchen_radio_a47db20d:

    # "{i}\"There's nothing left. The bombings have killed or destroyed everything.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"No queda nada. Los bombardeos lo han matado o destruido todo.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4023
translate spanish d13j_kitchen_radio_63f627c5:

    # "{i}\"I tried making some tea using leaves off of random trees. We got sick, and weaker still.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Intenté hacer té con hojas de árboles al azar. Nos pusimos enfermos, y aún más débiles.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4024
translate spanish d13j_kitchen_radio_dbd13aef:

    # "{i}\"I could not listen to their cries, their suffering and their pain any longer.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"No podía seguir escuchando sus gritos, su sufrimiento y su dolor.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4025
translate spanish d13j_kitchen_radio_dd02b9c6:

    # "{i}\"I ended it. I put them to sleep, and then used the gun you left behind.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Acabé con ellos. Los dormí y luego utilicé el arma que dejaste.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4026
translate spanish d13j_kitchen_radio_7ed2a201:

    # "{i}\"I didn't have the courage to use it on myself.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"No tuve el valor de usarla conmigo misma.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4027
translate spanish d13j_kitchen_radio_687c72c4:

    # "{i}\"I am damned forever.\"{/i}"
    "{i}\"Estoy condenada para siempre.\"{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4028
translate spanish d13j_kitchen_radio_971a98df_1:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4058
translate spanish d13j_living_room_45e710eb:

    # St "I've got enough... how do I get out."
    St "Ya he tenido bastante... ¿cómo salgo?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4059
translate spanish d13j_living_room_fb12974a:

    # St "This is scaring me."
    St "Esto me asusta."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4065
translate spanish d13j_living_room_55142faa:

    # Sw "Oh... fuck off."
    Sw "Oh... joder."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4079
translate spanish d13j_living_room_fa19fdcd:

    # St "What on earth...?!"
    St "¡¿Qué demonios...?!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4080
translate spanish d13j_living_room_0ea29282:

    # S "Hey... can you hear me?"
    S "Oye, ¿puedes oírme?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4081
translate spanish d13j_living_room_63e62a54:

    # St "...is that... a corpse?"
    St "... ¿eso es... un cadáver?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4098
translate spanish d13j_living_room_d12b0793:

    # St "What do I do now?!"
    St "¿Qué hago ahora?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4099
translate spanish d13j_living_room_3f730507:

    # St "There is something on the kitchen table..."
    St "Hay algo en la mesa de la cocina..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4111
translate spanish d13j_living_room_f9a3ad9f:

    # St "That came from the entrance."
    St "Eso vino de la entrada."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4122
translate spanish d13j_living_room_807f12c1:

    # St "The noise is coming from the radio..."
    St "El ruido procede de la radio..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4127
translate spanish d13j_living_room_6931d67a:

    # "The room remains silent upon stepping inside..."
    "La habitación se queda en silencio al entrar..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4160
translate spanish d13j_bedroom_df170bf5:

    # St "What is going on..."
    St "¿Qué está pasando?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4164
translate spanish d13j_bedroom_bda65203:

    # St "Oh, this must be the children."
    St "Oh, deben de ser los hijos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4165
translate spanish d13j_bedroom_7c0edb17:

    # St "That's just sad..."
    St "Eso es triste..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4171
translate spanish d13j_bedroom_971a98df:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4179
translate spanish d13j_bedroom_1abe5308:

    # St "What the fuck...!"
    St "¡Qué joder... !"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4182
translate spanish d13j_bedroom_ac6b2747:

    # St "I need to go."
    St "Tengo que irme."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4183
translate spanish d13j_bedroom_10dfd6c4:

    # Sw "I am not doing anything... leave me alone, okay..."
    Sw "No estoy haciendo nada... déjame en paz, vale..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4189
translate spanish d13j_bedroom_dc8020fe:

    # S "Leave me..."
    S "Déjame..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4195
translate spanish d13j_bedroom_df3a78f5:

    # S "...alone, you... whatever you are!"
    S "... en paz, tú... ¡lo que quiera que seas!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4198
translate spanish d13j_bedroom_1edb9678:

    # "Shock runs through the body as the creature lays motionless on the floor..."
    "El shock recorre su cuerpo mientras la criatura yace inmóvil en el suelo..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4199
translate spanish d13j_bedroom_ac85858b:

    # Sw "Ngh... fuck, I need to get out of here."
    Sw "Ngh... joder, tengo que salir de aquí."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4200
translate spanish d13j_bedroom_ae6f95cd:

    # Sw "I can't take this terror anymore."
    Sw "No puedo soportar más este terror."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4217
translate spanish d13j_bedroom_94fccc73:

    # "The noise comes from a radio nearby..."
    "El ruido procede de una radio cercana..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4232
translate spanish d13j_bedroom_0013f390:

    # St "Fuck that..."
    St "Joder..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4257
translate spanish d13j_bedroom_836f12b8:

    # St "There is nothing here."
    St "Aquí no hay nada."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4259
translate spanish d13j_bedroom_ab0e14ef:

    # St "There is still nothing here."
    St "Aquí sigue sin haber nada."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4274
translate spanish d13j_entrance_ffc3a191:

    # St "Footsteps... they came towards me?!"
    St "Pasos... ¿venían hacia mí?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4295
translate spanish d13j_entrance_231293ff:

    # St "Still shut. Solid metal, too."
    St "Sigue cerrada. Metal sólido, también."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4296
translate spanish d13j_entrance_25ac33fd:

    # St "No way I can pry this open."
    St "No hay forma de que pueda abrir esto."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4299
translate spanish d13j_entrance_76bcdf80:

    # St "I've got enough of this..."
    St "Ya tengo bastante..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4306
translate spanish d13j_entrance_8f6878fb:

    # St "No way..."
    St "De ninguna manera..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4307
translate spanish d13j_entrance_62557992:

    # St "It's shut."
    St "Está cerrado."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4308
translate spanish d13j_entrance_1223e1ee:

    # St "There must be another way out..."
    St "Tiene que haber otra salida..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4312
translate spanish d13j_entrance_cee1bc89:

    # St "I'm not going to waste any more time in here. I have a bad feeling about this."
    St "No voy a perder más tiempo aquí. Tengo un mal presentimiento."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4320
translate spanish d13j_entrance_a09b24dd:

    # "On the way back to the bunker, the drumming against the door resumes..."
    "De vuelta al búnker, se reanuda el tamborileo contra la puerta..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4327
translate spanish d13j_ending_e11ba295:

    # St "That didn't sound right..."
    St "Eso no sonaba bien..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4345
translate spanish d13j_ending_ae2d742d:

    # "[S] died; her body rests along with those souls that died in this apartment."
    "[S] murió; su cuerpo descansa junto con las almas que murieron en este apartamento."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4346
translate spanish d13j_ending_16eff73c:

    # "She will relive this moment again, and again, and again..."
    "Revivirá este momento una y otra vez..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4347
translate spanish d13j_ending_a7751eb2:

    # "Had she remembered her teachers' teachings, she would have known to not disturb the dead souls of those long passed away."
    "Si hubiera recordado las enseñanzas de sus maestros, habría sabido que no debía molestar a las almas muertas de aquellos que hace tiempo que fallecieron."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4378
translate spanish d13j_ending_a3c68a48:

    # S "...!"
    S "¡...!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4394
translate spanish d13j_ending_f4df0125:

    # St "The... door... it's open!!"
    St "La... puerta... ¡está abierta!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4400
translate spanish d13j_ending_c719e83d:

    # S "Nnah..-"
    S "Nnah..-"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4401
translate spanish d13j_ending_0e72faad:

    # S "{i}*pant*{/i}"
    S "{i}*jadeo*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4405
translate spanish d13j_ending_845ea9d8:

    # S "I will... {i}*cough*{/i}... never go back... in there..."
    S "Yo... {i}*tos*{/i}... nunca volveré... ahí dentro..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4406
translate spanish d13j_ending_99d1a520:

    # S "What was that even..."
    S "¿Qué ha sido eso...?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4407
translate spanish d13j_ending_29c47b10:

    # St "Damn, [S], you idiot!"
    St "¡Joder, [S], idiota!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4408
translate spanish d13j_ending_4cb6132c:

    # St "Screw this."
    St "Que le den."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4413
translate spanish d13j_ending_0af36e20:

    # "As the distance to the door grows further, something starts again..."
    "A medida que aumenta la distancia hasta la puerta, algo vuelve a empezar..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4415
translate spanish d13j_ending_e42a5c18:

    # St "This... felt like some sort of cycle."
    St "Esto... parecía una especie de ciclo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4416
translate spanish d13j_ending_267ede31:

    # St "Are they still... reliving their memories?"
    St "¿Siguen... reviviendo sus recuerdos?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4417
translate spanish d13j_ending_4240e807:

    # S "{i}*sigh*{/i}..."
    S "{i}*suspiro*{/i}..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4418
translate spanish d13j_ending_beed7a3c:

    # St "...Or maybe the air is just making my mind play tricks on me."
    St "... o tal vez el aire está haciendo que mi mente me juegue malas pasadas."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4419
translate spanish d13j_ending_82736085:

    # St "I need to get back to the bunker."
    St "Tengo que volver al búnker."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4427
translate spanish d13j_ending_f78f6d4c:

    # "The way back to the bunker is quiet."
    "El camino de vuelta al búnker es tranquilo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4428
translate spanish d13j_ending_85a79b25:

    # "The oppressive thoughts and the dark mood that came into existence in the apartment, leave a mark, and only gradually does the soft sound of steps, and wind resurface from the background. "
    "Los pensamientos opresivos y el ambiente oscuro que se respira en el apartamento, dejan huella, y sólo gradualmente resurge del fondo el suave sonido de los pasos y el viento."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4436
translate spanish d13k_5d8c52dd:

    # "As you were going to visit [S] in her room, you spot her standing in front of her wall mirror from the outside..."
    "Cuando vas a visitar a [S] a su habitación, la ves de pie frente al espejo de la pared desde el exterior..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4439
translate spanish d13k_d07539a7:

    # S "{i}*humming*{/i}"
    S "{i}*tarareando*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4440
translate spanish d13k_7118381a:

    # Sw "I guess that works..."
    Sw "Supongo que funcionará..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4443
translate spanish d13k_b733caed:

    # Sw "Worth the price, I hope..."
    Sw "Espero que merezca la pena..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4444
translate spanish d13k_195958c9:

    # Sw "I wonder about the neck area, though."
    Sw "Aunque me pregunto por la zona del cuello."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4448
translate spanish d13k_e246992d:

    # S "...?"
    S "¿...?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4449
translate spanish d13k_15090bf3:

    # Z "Where's my girl?"
    Z "¿Dónde está mi chica?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4452
translate spanish d13k_af281edf:

    # "You come inside and walk up to her..."
    "Entras y te acercas a ella..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4455
translate spanish d13k_bd9aef97:

    # Z "Hey [S], so I was wondering if you want to take a look at..."
    Z "Ey [S], me preguntaba si querrías echar un vistazo a..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4458
translate spanish d13k_0231cc65:

    # Z "...that motorcycle..."
    Z "... esa moto..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4462
translate spanish d13k_2ac832da:

    # "You check her out before finishing your sentence."
    "La examinas antes de terminar la frase."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4463
translate spanish d13k_612286c9:

    # "She's wearing a dress you haven't seen before, with flowery patterns in burgundy hues."
    "Lleva un vestido que no habías visto antes, con motivos florales en tonos burdeos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4466
translate spanish d13k_863cf971:

    # "It hugs her figure in a very complimentary fashion."
    "Se ciñe a su figura de forma muy favorecedora."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4469
translate spanish d13k_f64a9462:

    # Z "Your dress... is it new?"
    Z "Tu vestido... ¿es nuevo?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4470
translate spanish d13k_fd6a545a:

    # Z "I don't remember seeing it before."
    Z "No recuerdo haberlo visto antes."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4473
translate spanish d13k_8b4bc7cd:

    # S "That's right. I bought it just today. Do you like it?"
    S "Así es. Lo he comprado hoy mismo. ¿Te gusta?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4476
translate spanish d13k_c17e2be5:

    # Z "I really do."
    Z "De verdad que sí."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4479
translate spanish d13k_994eed50:

    # S "You know, to be honest, it was a bit expensive."
    S "Para ser sincera, fue un poco caro."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4480
translate spanish d13k_3c83428f:

    # S "Remember when we talked about that creepy apartment I encountered? It's been on my mind, lately, and not in a good way."
    S "¿Recuerdas cuando hablamos del apartamento espeluznante que encontré? Últimamente lo tengo en mente, y no en el buen sentido."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4483
translate spanish d13k_cd21c851:

    # S "So today, I have taken a page from [A]'s book and decided to go to the city for a little shopping therapy..."
    S "Hoy he seguido el ejemplo de [A] y he decidido ir a la ciudad para una pequeña terapia de compras..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4486
translate spanish d13k_d3aca464:

    # S "...and... well..."
    S "... y... bueno..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4489
translate spanish d13k_f390cf21:

    # Z "You? Going shopping without being dragged into it? That's new."
    Z "¿Tú? ¿Ir de compras sin que te arrastren a ello? Eso es nuevo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4490
translate spanish d13k_6c549e2c:

    # Z "It looks very pretty. Give me a twirl, will you?"
    Z "Estás muy guapa. Date una vuelta, ¿quieres?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4493
translate spanish d13k_0d69f943:

    # "She smiles and quickly turns around..."
    "Sonríe y se da la vuelta rápidamente..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4501
translate spanish re_d13k13_b4de6f47:

    # S "I don't know why, but I really liked the colors, [persistent.dad]."
    S "No sé por qué, pero me gustaron mucho los colores, [persistent.dad]."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4502
translate spanish re_d13k13_bc45afdc:

    # S "Sorry for spending your gold..."
    S "Siento haber gastado tu oro..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4505
translate spanish re_d13k13_6be7fcc8:

    # S "Also, I like that it doesn't cover my back entirely unlike the other dresses that I have."
    S "Además, me gusta que no me cubra totalmente la espalda, a diferencia de los otros vestidos que tengo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4509
translate spanish re_d13k13_f8a8145a:

    # "She turns around, revealing her toned back..."
    "Se da la vuelta, mostrando su tonificada espalda..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4510
translate spanish re_d13k13_4d17972a:

    # S "What do you think?"
    S "¿Qué te parece?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4515
translate spanish re_d13k13_f7ce6d3e:

    # Z "Yeah, you see..."
    Z "Sí, verás..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4518
translate spanish re_d13k13_9037fde8:

    # "You walk up to her..."
    "Te acercas a ella..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4519
translate spanish re_d13k13_e6b4a9aa:

    # Z "I do like it, but I am not sure about the quality yet."
    Z "Me gusta, pero aún no estoy seguro de su calidad."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4522
translate spanish re_d13k13_18cf5bac:

    # S "{i}*giggles*{/i}... really... is that so?"
    S "{i}*risitas*{/i}... de verdad... ¿es eso así?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4523
translate spanish re_d13k13_cc5092d8:

    # S "You've got to feel the material, huh?"
    S "Tienes que sentir el material, ¿eh?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4526
translate spanish re_d13k13_6529d3c9:

    # Z "Exactly..."
    Z "Exacto..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4527
translate spanish re_d13k13_f957e359:

    # "You feel up her waist..."
    "Tanteas su cintura..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4528
translate spanish re_d13k13_6d5c90b3:

    # Z "Now, for instance, I can tell that the craftmanship in sewing this dress is exquisite."
    Z "Ahora, por ejemplo, puedo decir que la artesanía en la costura de este vestido es exquisita."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4529
translate spanish re_d13k13_418f9827:

    # S "Craftsmanship, huh?"
    S "Artesanía, ¿eh?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4530
translate spanish re_d13k13_dca6f8a1:

    # S "I see... but..."
    S "Ya veo... pero..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4533
translate spanish re_d13k13_0197d27a:

    # "She steps away from your embrace and slowly walks over to the wall, leaning forward..."
    "Se separa de tu abrazo y se acerca lentamente a la pared, inclinándose hacia delante..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4536
translate spanish re_d13k13_f0652c25:

    # S "Do you think it compliments my figure adequately?"
    S "¿Crees que complementa adecuadamente mi figura?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4540
translate spanish re_d13k13_900f0148:

    # Z "Hm..."
    Z "Hm..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4543
translate spanish re_d13k13_9037fde8_1:

    # "You walk up to her..."
    "Te acercas a ella..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4546
translate spanish re_d13k13_7f891691:

    # Z "That looks expensive. A lot of gold. My gold, you say."
    Z "Parece caro. Mucho oro. Mi oro, dices."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4547
translate spanish re_d13k13_b0f79853:

    # Z "I think I should have a say in how you use it."
    Z "Creo que debería poder opinar sobre cómo la utilizas."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4548
translate spanish re_d13k13_00f3dcc5:

    # S "Oh... um..."
    S "Oh... um..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4552
translate spanish re_d13k13_c0f1065a:

    # S "[persistent.dad!c]..."
    S "[persistent.dad!c]..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4553
translate spanish re_d13k13_421170de:

    # "You start feeling her up aggressively..."
    "Empiezas a tocarla agresivamente..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4554
translate spanish re_d13k13_1f7c0499:

    # S "{i}*giggles*{/i}... maybe it was a little expensive..."
    S "{i}*risitas*{/i}... Quizá fuera un poco caro..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4555
translate spanish re_d13k13_3fc57677:

    # "Her voice sounds sultry, cute and teasing at the same time..."
    "Su voz suena sensual, tierna y burlona al mismo tiempo..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4558
translate spanish re_d13k13_14229b0f:

    # "Your hands aggressively roam her body. Your right hand lifts up her full breast as your left greedily goes to her neck..."
    "Tus manos recorren agresivamente su cuerpo. Tu mano derecha le levanta el pecho mientras la izquierda se dirige ávidamente a su cuello..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4559
translate spanish re_d13k13_e2e29aa9:

    # S "[persistent.dad!c]... what has gotten into you..."
    S "[persistent.dad!c]... ¿qué se te ha metido...?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4560
translate spanish re_d13k13_1675880d:

    # Z "I guess the dress has an effect on me, after all."
    Z "Supongo que el vestido tiene un efecto sobre mí, después de todo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4563
translate spanish re_d13k13_c59458ce:

    # S "So... I guess that means you like it?"
    S "Entonces... ¿supongo que eso significa que te gusta?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4566
translate spanish re_d13k13_36160084:

    # S "{i}*gulp*{/i}"
    S "{i}*tragando*{/i}"

