    "Tanto tú como [S] habéis tenido vuestros momentos íntimos con la reina, pero éste podría ser el rompehielos que necesitáis."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4877
translate spanish d13l17x_49904979:

    # "You've had your intimate moments with the Queen, but this could be the icebreaker you need."
    "Tú has tenido tus momentos íntimos con la Reina, pero éste podría ser el rompehielos que necesitas."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4883
translate spanish d13l17x_fcbc5652:

    # "You step closer..."
    "Te acercas más..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4886
translate spanish d13l17x_76e6eab1:

    # Z "You know..."
    Z "Sabes..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4887
translate spanish d13l17x_88e5c4e2:

    # Z "That might be a good idea after all."
    Z "Después de todo, podría ser una buena idea."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4890
translate spanish d13l17x_4ba2219b:

    # S "Let's show her what we do?"
    S "¿Vamos a enseñarle lo que hacemos?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4893
translate spanish d13l17x_bb1666ac:

    # Z "Let's show her what we do."
    Z "Vamos a enseñarle lo que hacemos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4894
translate spanish d13l17x_d9fcce3e:

    # Z "Now, I think she's waiting for us already."
    Z "Creo que ya nos está esperando."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4895
translate spanish d13l17x_628df5db:

    # Z "Let's finish changing, you can take your time, but I need to get out there."
    Z "Vamos a terminar de cambiarnos, puedes tomarte tu tiempo, pero yo tengo que salir."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4898
translate spanish d13l17x_71d190fc:

    # S "Oh...and... [persistent.dad]?"
    S "Oh... y... ¿[persistent.dad]?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4901
translate spanish d13l17x_9609918a:

    # S "Just so you know. Once we're out there..."
    S "Para que lo sepas. Una vez que estemos ahí fuera..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4904
translate spanish d13l17x_fb086d78:

    # S "...I might not hold myself back for once."
    S "...puede que no me contenga por una vez."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4914
translate spanish d13l17x_7fa93db7:

    # Z "You know... this isn't a bad idea, at all."
    Z "Sabes... no es mala idea, en absoluto."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4917
translate spanish d13l17x_16bda134:

    # Z "But I think I will find another to open up a little more."
    Z "Pero creo que encontraré otro modo de abrirme un poco más."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4920
translate spanish d13l17x_6859c878:

    # Z "Let's have some patience. I don't think this is the right time."
    Z "Tengamos un poco de paciencia. No creo que sea el momento adecuado."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4923
translate spanish d13l17x_cfe3cef4:

    # S "Up to you, [persistent.dad]. You know her better than me."
    S "Depende de ti, [persistent.dad]. Tú la conoces mejor que yo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4926
translate spanish d13l17x_d9fcce3e_1:

    # Z "Now, I think she's waiting for us already."
    Z "Creo que ya nos está esperando."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4927
translate spanish d13l17x_628df5db_1:

    # Z "Let's finish changing, you can take your time, but I need to get out there."
    Z "Vamos a terminar de cambiarnos, puedes tomarte tu tiempo, pero yo tengo que salir."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4932
translate spanish d13l18_7dc772c1:

    # "You change quickly, then leave [S] for the thermae, where Queen Merneith is waiting for you."
    "Os cambiáis rápidamente y salís [S] hacia las termas, donde os espera la reina Merneith."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4937
translate spanish d13l18_37b86516:

    # "You enter the royal thermae. A place that maintains its grandiose impact even though you have been here before."
    "Entráis en las termas reales. Un lugar que mantiene su grandiosidad a pesar de que ya has estado aquí antes."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4939
translate spanish d13l18_24157b9a:

    # "You enter the famed royal thermae..."
    "Entráis en las famosas termas reales..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4940
translate spanish d13l18_3595d1d4:

    # "A subtle cloud of steam rises from the water in front of you. As you approach the steps leading to it, you hear someone splashing around, already in it."
    "Una sutil nube de vapor se eleva desde el agua frente a ti. Al acercarte a los escalones que conducen a ella, oyes a alguien chapoteando, ya en ella."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4943
translate spanish d13l18_9c7c86b0:

    # "The temperature is a fair bit fresher here in the depth of the palace than outside under the scorching sun."
    "La temperatura es bastante más fresca aquí, en las profundidades del palacio, que en el exterior, bajo el sol abrasador."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4946
translate spanish d13l18_7df1cfe5:

    # "As you step closer towards the bathing area, you hear a familiar voice humming..."
    "Mientras te acercas a la zona de baño, oyes una voz familiar que tararea..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4949
translate spanish d13l18_7bc371e6:

    # Sl "..."
    Sl "..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4950
translate spanish d13l18_f0e8f4ad:

    # Q "{i}*humming*{/i}"
    Q "{i}*tarareando*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4953
translate spanish d13l18_d59b6df2:

    # "One of the royal attendants is standing to the side of the pool ."
    "Una de las asistentes reales está de pie a un lado de la piscina."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4955
translate spanish d13l18_04fde537:

    # "Despite the mask you recognise her from your previous visit..."
    "A pesar de la máscara, la reconoces de tu anterior visita..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4958
translate spanish d13l18_f0e8f4ad_1:

    # Q "{i}*humming*{/i}"
    Q "{i}*tarareando*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4962
translate spanish d13l18_46ca1d74:

    # Q "Mh..."
    Q "Mh..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4965
translate spanish d13l18_c81dd608:

    # Q "Slave..."
    Q "Esclava..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4968
translate spanish d13l18_20cbf211:

    # Q "...tell the master of the Thermae that I am satisfied with the temperature of the water, today. It is adequate..."
    Q "... dile al responsable de las Termas que hoy estoy satisfecha con la temperatura del agua. Es adecuada..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4971
translate spanish d13l18_c31a50f9:

    # "The Queen's glistening body shimmers in the light of the torches. The way she moves her hands over her glossy skin captures your attention for a few long seconds..."
    "El cuerpo reluciente de la Reina brilla a la luz de las antorchas. La forma en que mueve las manos sobre su piel brillante capta tu atención durante unos largos segundos..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4974
translate spanish d13l18_b63a6147:

    # "She moves with poised elegance and you wonder how much of that is her natural gait and how much has been ingrained by years of training."
    "Se mueve con aplomada elegancia y te preguntas hasta qué punto se trata de su forma natural de andar y hasta qué punto está arraigada por años de entrenamiento."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4975
translate spanish d13l18_9fe7658c:

    # "Whether intentional or not, her appearance in this more intimate setting does stir familiar urges in your body."
    "Intencionadamente o no, su aparición en este ambiente más íntimo despierta en tu cuerpo impulsos familiares."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4978
translate spanish d13l18_a77b08c0:

    # "You've been staring at her for a good time now, so you think to make your presence known..."
    "Llevas un buen rato mirándola fijamente, así que piensas en hacer notar tu presencia..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4980
translate spanish d13l18_c81dd608_1:

    # Q "Slave..."
    Q "Esclava..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4981
translate spanish d13l18_20cbf211_1:

    # Q "...tell the master of the Thermae that I am satisfied with the temperature of the water, today. It is adequate..."
    Q "... dile al responsable de las Termas que hoy estoy satisfecha con la temperatura del agua. Es adecuada..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4984
translate spanish d13l18_4b8bce05:

    # "You make your presence known..."
    "Te haces presente..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4985
translate spanish d13l18_544dc398:

    # Z "{i}*ahem*{/i}"
    Z "{i}ejem{/i}"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4988
translate spanish d13l18_bdc61a01:

    # Q "..."
    Q "..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4991
translate spanish d13l18_b4a1cf04:

    # Q "[persistent.player_name]?"
    Q "¿[persistent.player_name]?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4994
translate spanish d13l18_bdc61a01_1:

    # Q "..."
    Q "..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4995
translate spanish d13l18_5f178e4b:

    # "You see the hint of a smile on her face..."
    "Ves el atisbo de una sonrisa en su rostro..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:4998
translate spanish d13l18_a4c68fcd:

    # Q "Uhm... Slave, you can go now. Join your sisters until I call for you again."
    Q "Uhm... Esclava, ya puedes irte. Únete a tus hermanas hasta que vuelva a llamarte."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5004
translate spanish d13l18_0ed16780:

    # "As you approach the Queen, you sit on the steps in her proximity..."
    "Mientras te acercas a la Reina, te sientas en los escalones cerca de ella..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5007
translate spanish d13l18_f70cb776:

    # Q "You come alone, [persistent.player_name]?"
    Q "¿Vienes solo, [persistent.player_name]?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5009
translate spanish d13l18_b23cbd3c:

    # Z "My [persistent.da] will join us soon. She's still changing clothes."
    Z "Mi [persistent.da] se unirá pronto a nosotros. Todavía se está cambiando de ropa."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5011
translate spanish d13l18_91cbcb7d:

    # Z "[S] will join us soon. She's still changing clothes."
    Z "[S] se unirá pronto a nosotros. Todavía se está cambiando de ropa."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5014
translate spanish d13l18_351bd169:

    # "She moves closer..."
    "Ella se acerca..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5015
translate spanish d13l18_397956f3:

    # Q "Ah... I am glad. I was hoping for you both to join me here."
    Q "Ah... me alegro. Esperaba que los dos os unierais a mí aquí."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5019
translate spanish d13l18_153106af:

    # Z "Anything new regarding the Elder's hideout?"
    Z "¿Alguna novedad sobre el escondite del Anciano?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5022
translate spanish d13l18_0fdca3fa:

    # Q "Unfortunately... not yet."
    Q "Por desgracia... todavía no."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5025
translate spanish d13l18_729cfdb7:

    # Q "I have to research this matter personally, and it's not always easy for me to get rid of my retinue, the guards, the slaves..."
    Q "Tengo que investigar ese asunto personalmente, y no siempre me resulta fácil deshacerme de mi séquito, los guardias, los esclavos..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5028
translate spanish d13l18_41d7ddd9:

    # Q "You'd be surprised to know how little of my day I can spend in solitude without arousing suspicion or acting out of the boundaries of my role."
    Q "Te sorprendería saber la poca parte del día que puedo pasar en soledad sin levantar sospechas o actuar fuera de los límites de mi función."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5029
translate spanish d13l18_e4d04c8a:

    # Q "But this is too important to confide in one of the Elders or even my most trusted guards and advisors."
    Q "Pero esto es demasiado importante para confiárselo a uno de los Ancianos o incluso a mis guardias y consejeros de mayor confianza."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5032
translate spanish d13l18_0f2b4b26:

    # Q "In their zeal to protect me or the realm, they might act rashly before I can stop them."
    Q "En su celo por protegerme a mí o al reino, podrían actuar precipitadamente antes de que pudiera detenerlos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5035
translate spanish d13l18_a469062e:

    # Z "I see. Then I guess it will take some time until we have anything we can work with."
    Z "Ya veo. Entonces supongo que pasará algún tiempo hasta que tengamos algo con lo que podamos trabajar."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5038
translate spanish d13l18_bdc61a01_2:

    # Q "..."
    Q "..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5042
translate spanish d13l18_0e2e6614:

    # "You both hear footsteps that come from the direction of the entrance. You don't have to guess who that could be..."
    "Ambos oís pasos que vienen de la dirección de la entrada. No tenéis que adivinar quién puede ser..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5045
translate spanish d13l18_9f46420f:

    # S "Aww... you two started without me?"
    S "Ohh... ¿habéis empezado sin mí?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5048
translate spanish d13l18_66ba41e1:

    # S "Sorry, I took a bit longer. That servant kept giving me clothing options..."
    S "Perdona, he tardado un poco más. Esa sirvienta no paraba de darme opciones de ropa..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5055
translate spanish d13l18_7b89397f:

    # "...and what a dress she chose."
    "... y menudo vestido eligió."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5056
translate spanish d13l18_f1d64f86:

    # "She rests against a pillar, knowing full well that you both are staring at her."
    "Se apoya en una columna, sabiendo perfectamente que ambos la estáis mirando."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5059
translate spanish d13l18_d4c39f5a:

    # "Her breasts are wrapped inside a pristine white bra and her hips are complemented by a soft skirt."
    "Sus pechos están envueltos en un sujetador blanco inmaculado y sus caderas se complementan con una falda suave."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5062
translate spanish d13l18_145b4bea:

    # "A long moment of silence settles in the thermae."
    "Un largo momento de silencio se instala en las termas."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5063
translate spanish d13l18_6b90b513:

    # "For a moment you sense the Queen's breath quicken, then she composes herself again."
    "Por un momento sientes que la respiración de la Reina se acelera, pero luego vuelve a serenarse."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5066
translate spanish d13l18_b307f440:

    # Z "Why don't you join us?"
    Z "¿Por qué no te unes a nosotros?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5067
translate spanish d13l18_9fa51bcd:

    # Z "We just sat down actually."
    Z "De hecho, acabamos de sentarnos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5070
translate spanish d13l18_63869a51:

    # Q "Yeah, I mean. We were just about to start discussing things..."
    Q "Sí. Estábamos a punto de empezar a discutir las cosas..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5073
translate spanish d13l18_7cde45a6:

    # Q "...but I'm glad you're joining us."
    Q "... pero me alegro de que te unas a nosotros."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5076
translate spanish d13l18_654a5bcb:

    # "She takes off her skirt and descends into the water..."
    "Se quita la falda y desciende al agua..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5079
translate spanish d13l18_96cd080d:

    # S "Hey guys. So, what are we doing?"
    S "Oye, chicos. Entonces, ¿qué estamos haciendo?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5082
translate spanish d13l18_9a948479:

    # Z "You should come and sit next to me."
    Z "Deberías venir y sentarte a mi lado."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5085
translate spanish d13l18_4237633e:

    # S "I should, huh? Alright, as you wish."
    S "Debería, ¿eh? De acuerdo, como quieras."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5089
translate spanish d13l18_d14fba2a:

    # "She sits next to you as the conversation resumes..."
    "Ella se sienta a tu lado mientras se reanuda la conversación..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5092
translate spanish d13l18_52745dbd:

    # Q "So... as I was saying..."
    Q "Entonces... como te estaba diciendo..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5095
translate spanish d13l18_ba866611:

    # Q "Researching the source of the paper you found and the name of the Elder in the old records is slow work."
    Q "Investigar la fuente del papel que encontraste y el nombre del Anciano en los registros antiguos es un trabajo lento."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5098
translate spanish d13l18_0a987102:

    # Q "I will get to it though. Once I have found what I need, I will have work for both of you."
    Q "No obstante, me pondré a ello. Cuando haya encontrado lo que necesito, tendré trabajo para los dos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5101
translate spanish d13l18_ab26d12a:

    # Q "Aside from that, though..."
    Q "Aparte de eso, sin embargo..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5102
translate spanish d13l18_2eaf0028:

    # Q "But...I would still like you to be around the palace, [persistent.player_name]. We don't yet know the extent of this."
    Q "Pero... me gustaría que sigas cerca del palacio, [persistent.player_name]. Aún no sabemos la magnitud de esto."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5103
translate spanish d13l18_237fe96f:

    # "She seems to think of her words for a moment, mumbling..."
    "Por un momento, parece reflexionar sobre sus palabras, murmurando..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5106
translate spanish d13l18_4bf24c32:

    # Q "I guess it would make sense, the palace guards would not question your regular presence..."
    Q "Supongo que tendría sentido, los guardias del palacio no cuestionarían tu presencia habitual..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5107
translate spanish d13l18_68e28e1d:

    # Q "I could use your help around the palace. Menial tasks, if anything."
    Q "Podría necesitar tu ayuda en el palacio. Tareas simples, si es necesario."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5110
translate spanish d13l18_5c03cb62:

    # Q "Yeah, let's do that. I will instruct the guards to give you access to the inner courtyard and the Thermae when you want to make use of them."
    Q "Sí, hagamos eso. Instruiré a los guardias para que te den acceso al patio interior y las Termas cuando desees usarlos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5111
translate spanish d13l18_c667b737:

    # Q "You will be free to come as you please without me summoning you explicitly."
    Q "Serás libre de venir cuando quieras sin que yo te convoque explícitamente."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5116
translate spanish d13l18_9f37eaef:

    # S "Okay, that's between you two I think. Just let me know next time when you have a lead to the hideout."
    S "Vale, creo que esto queda entre vosotros dos. Avísame la próxima vez cuando tengas una pista sobre el escondite."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5119
translate spanish d13l18_bdd9be27:

    # Q "Definitely. I am looking forward to that. I will make sure to..."
    Q "Sin duda. Lo estoy deseando. Me aseguraré de..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5123
translate spanish d13l18_821e0d93:

    # "As the Queen goes more into detail, [S] gently moves her hand, stroking against your blanket..."
    "Mientras la Reina entra en detalles, [S] mueve suavemente la mano, acariciando tu manta..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5127
translate spanish re_d13l63_bf080b9a:

    # Sw "[persistent.dad!c]... Now would be a good time, I think."
    Sw "[persistent.dad!c]... Ahora sería un buen momento, creo."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5128
translate spanish re_d13l63_8e48cc58:

    # Sw "Let's make her a little jealous...?"
    Sw "¿Vamos a ponerla un poco celosa?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5131
translate spanish re_d13l63_a32b56ce:

    # Zw "Don't get us into trouble, [S]..."
    Zw "No nos metas en líos, [S]..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5132
translate spanish re_d13l63_93ce3df4:

    # "You wink at her..."
    "La guiñas un ojo..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5135
translate spanish re_d13l63_1e3211d2:

    # Sw "Would I ever?"
    Sw "¿Alguna vez lo haría?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5137
translate spanish re_d13l63_a9425f87:

    # Sw "Just follow my lead."
    Sw "Sólo sígueme la corriente."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5140
translate spanish re_d13l63_f3dc0b2d:

    # Zw "After you..."
    Zw "Después de ti..."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5151
translate spanish d13l55_cd00168e:

    # Q "So, anyway... As I said, the guards will know that you and those of your House are allowed to enjoy the Thermae at your discretion.."
    Q "En fin... Como ya te he dicho, los guardias sabrán que tú y los de tu Casa podéis disfrutar de las Termas a vuestra discreción.."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5152
translate spanish d13l55_701a4184:

    # Q "I will be going back to my duties for now. You two keep enjoying the time here, okay?"
    Q "Por ahora volveré a mis obligaciones. Vosotros dos seguid disfrutando del tiempo que paséis aquí, ¿de acuerdo?"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5153
translate spanish d13l55_54b1879d:

    # Q "Visit the palace again if you're up for some extra work, [persistent.player_name]."
    Q "Visita el palacio de nuevo si estás dispuesto a hacer un poco de trabajo adicional, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5154
translate spanish d13l55_c4f3242d:

    # S "Thank you!"
    S "¡Gracias!"

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5155
translate spanish d13l55_56f91ed6:

    # Z "We will rest a little and then leave as well. I will see to visit you again in the future."
    Z "Descansaremos un poco y luego nos iremos también. Veré de volver a visitaros en el futuro."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5156
translate spanish d13l55_20d46187:

    # Q "Great! Um... goodbye for now, then, you two."
    Q "¡Genial! Um... adiós por ahora, entonces, a los dos."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5159
translate spanish d13l55_910acd21:

    # "You share in the luxurious opulence of the Queen's residence some more with [S]."
    "Compartes un poco más con [S] la lujosa opulencia de la residencia de la Reina."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5160
translate spanish d13l55_80a6a7cf:

    # "Your mind goes to the many people of Zeta who have only limited access to such a vital thing as a water supply, and you consider that your hard work has given you many privileges."
    "Tu mente se dirige a las muchas personas de Zeta que sólo tienen un acceso limitado a algo tan vital como el suministro de agua, y consideras que tu duro trabajo te ha dado muchos privilegios."

# game/scripts/day13.rpy:5161
translate spanish d13l55_a8a7dfaf:

